quran[1606]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,“Qaf. Ndikulumbira Qur’an yolemekezeka
  50,2,"“Koma akudabwa chifukwa chowadzera Mchenjezi wochokera mwa iwo. Ndipo osakhulupirira adanena: “Ichi nchinthu chodabwitsa.”"
  50,3,"“Kodi tikadzafa ndi kukhala fumbi (tidzaukanso?) Kubwerera kumeneko nkwakutali kwambiri, (nkosatheka).”"
  50,4,“Ndithu tikudziwa chimene nthaka ikuchepetsa m’matupi mwawo (akalowa m’manda). Ndipo kwa Ife kuli kaundula wosungidwa
  50,5,“Koma adatsutsa choona pamene chidawadzera. Ndipo iwo ali m’chinthu chosokonezeka
  50,6,“Kodi sawona thambo pamwamba pawo m’mene tidalimangira ndi kulikongoletsa? Ndipo lilibe ming’alu
  50,7,“Ndipo nthaka tidaiyala; ndi kuika mapiri m’menemo ndi kumeretsamo m’mera Wokongola wamtundu uliwonse
  50,8,“(Kuti zimenezi zikhale) chotsekula maso ndi chikumbutso kwa munthu aliyense wotembenukira (kwa Allah)
  50,9,"“Ndipo tatsitsa madzi odalitsidwa kuchokera ku mitambo, ndipo kupyolera m’madziwo, tameretsa (mmera) m’minda ndi mbewu zokololedwa"
  50,10,“Ndi mitengo italiitali ya kanjedza yokhala ndi mikoko yazipatso zothothana
  50,11,“(Kuti chikhale) chakudya cha akapolo (a Allah); ndi madziwo taukitsa dziko lakufa (louma). Momwemo ndimmene kudzakhalira kutuluka m’manda (muli moyo)
  50,12,"“Kale, iwo kulibe, adatsutsa anthu a Nuh ndi eni chitsime ndi Asamudu"
  50,13,"“Ndi Âdi, ndi Farawo ndi Abale a Luti"
  50,14,"“Ndi anthu a m’mitengo (ya Aika), ndi anthu a Tubba; onsewo adatsutsa Aneneri; choncho chenjezo Langa lidatsimikizika (pa iwo)"
  50,15,“Kodi tidatopa nkulenga koyamba? Koma iwo ali m’maganizo osokonezeka m’zakalengedwe katsopano
  50,16,"“Ndithu tidamulenga munthu, ndipo Ife tikudziwa zimene mtima wake ukumunong’oneza; ndipo Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa mtsempha wam’khosi mwake (wolumikizana ndi mtima)"
  50,17,"“Ndipo pamene amalandira olandira awiri (angelo), wina amakhala kudzanja lamanja, wina kudzanja lamanzere"
  50,18,“Palibe chilichonse chimene amayankhula koma pafupi ndi iye pali mlonda amene wakonzekera (kulemba)
  50,19,"“Ndipo kuledzera kwa imfa kukam’dzera mwa choona, (pamenepo adzauzidwa): “Ichi ndi chomwe mumachithawa chija.”"
  50,20,“Ndipo lipenga lidzaimbidwa; limenelo ndilo tsiku lamavuto (tsiku lachiweruziro)
  50,21,“Ndipo udzadza mzimu uliwonse pamodzi ndi m’busa (wake) ndi mboni (yake)
  50,22,"“(Adzauzidwa): “Ndithu udali wosalabadira zinthu izi; basi takuvundukulira (chomwe) chimakuphimba, ndipo kuyang’ana kwako lero nkwakuthwa!”"
  50,23,"“Ndipo (Mngelo) yemwe adali naye (pamodzi ndikumalemba zochita zake) adzanena (kwa Mngelo wachilango): “Izi ndizimene zidakonzedwa ndi ine.”"
  50,24,"“Mponyeni ku Moto aliyense wokanira, wamakani,”"
  50,25,"““Wotsekereza zabwino, wolumpha malire, wokaika.”"
  50,26,““Amene adampangira Allah mulungu wina. Chomwecho mponyeni ku chilango chaukali.”
  50,27,"“Mnzake (satana) adzanena: “E Mbuye wathu! Sindidamsokeretse, koma iye mwini adali wosokera kutali kwambiri ndi choonadi”"
  50,28,"“(Allah) adzanena: “Musakangane kwa Ine; ndidakutsogozerani kale chenjezo (Langa).”"
  50,29,"“Liwu Langa silisinthidwa kwa Ine, ndipo Ine siwopondereza akapolo (Anga)"
  50,30,"“Tsiku limene tidzaifunsa Jahannam: “Kodi wadzaza?” Iyo idzanena: “Kodi kuli zoonjezera?”"
  50,31,“Ndipo Munda wamtendere udzayandikitsidwa pafupi kwa oopa (Allah)
  50,32,"““Izi ndizimene mumalonjezedwa, za aliyense wotembenukira kwa Allah, Wosunga (malamulo Ake)"
  50,33,"“Amene adaopa (Allah), Wachifundo chambiri, pomwe samamuona ndi maso, ndipo adadza ndi mtima wotembenukira (kwa Iye).”"
  50,34,"“(Adzauzidwa): “Uloweni mwamtendere.” Limeneli ndi tsiku lokhazikika mpaka muyaya"
  50,35,"“M’menemo adzapeza chilichonse (chimene) adzafune, ndipo kwa Ife kuli zoonjezera"
  50,36,"“Ndipo kodi ndi mibadwo ingati tidainonga kale iwo kulibe, yamphamvu kuposa iwo? Adayendayenda padziko. Kodi padalipo pothawira"
  50,37,“Ndithu m’zimenezi muli chikumbutso kwa yemwe ali ndi mtima ndi yemwe akutchelera khutu (uku) iye ali pompo (ndi maganizo ake)
  50,38,"“Ndithu tidalenga thambo ndi nthaka ndi zapakati pake m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi, ndipo sikudatikhuze kutopa kulikonse"
  50,39,"“Choncho, pirira nazo zomwe akunenazo, ndipo lemekeza Mbuye wako pomutamanda dzuwa lisadatuluke, (Swala ya Subh), ndi (dzuwa) lisadalowe, (Swala ya Asr)"
  50,40,"“Ndi gawo lausiku, (Swala ya Maghrib ndi Isha); ndiponso (mulemekeze) pambuyo pa mapemphero (popemphera Swala za Sunna)"
  50,41,“Ndipo mvetsera (za) tsiku limene woitana adzaitana kuchokera pamalo apafupi
  50,42,"“Tsiku limene adzamva phokoso mwa choonadi: limenelo ndilo tsiku lodzatuluka (m’manda)"
  50,43,“Ndithu Ife ndi amene timapereka moyo ndi kupereka imfa; ndipo kobwerera Nkwathu
  50,44,“(Akumbutse za) tsiku limene nthaka idzang’ambike kwa iwo mwachangu; kusonkhanitsa kumeneko nkosavuta kwa Ife
  50,45,“Ife tikudziwa bwino zimene akunena; iwe siuli wowakakamiza. Choncho mukumbutse ndi Qur’an yemwe akuopa chilango Changa
  51,1,“. Ndikulumbilira mphepo imene ikubalalitsa mitambo ya mvula
  51,2,“Ndi imene imasenza mitolo yolemera (ya madzi)
  51,3,“Ndi kuyenda (nawo madziwo) mwaubwino
  51,4,“Ndi awo amene amagawa rizq (limene Allah amalipereka kwa amene wamfuna)
  51,5,"“Ndithu zimene mukulonjezedwa nzoonadi, (zidzachitika)"
  51,6,"“Ndipo, ndithu malipiro (pa zochita zanu) adzapezekadi"
  51,7,“Ndikulumbilira thambo lomwe njira zake zambiri nzoikidwa mwaluso
  51,8,"“Ndithu inu muli m’mau otsutsana, (pa zimene mukunena)"
  51,9,“(Kupyolera m’mawu amenewa) akuchotsedwa ku icho (chikhulupiliro chalonjezo loona) amene adachotsedwa (ku chikhulupilirocho)
  51,10,“Aonongeka abodza (amene akunena za tsiku lachiweruziro mongoganizira)
  51,11,"“Iwo amene akubira mu umbuli, osalabadira (za tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  51,12,“Akufunsa (mwachipongwe ponena kuti) “Lidzakhala liti tsiku lamalipiro?”
  51,13,“(Limenelo ndi) tsiku lomwe iwo adzalangidwa ku Moto
  51,14,"“(Adzawauza kuti): “Lawani chilango chanu ichi chimene munkachifulumizitsa (kuti chikufikeni).”"
  51,15,“Ndithu oopa (Allah) adzakhala (akusangalala) m’minda ndi mu akasupe okongola
  51,16,“Uku akulandira zimene wawapatsa Mbuye wawo (malipiro aulemu); ndithu iwo ankachita zabwino asanapeze izi
  51,17,“Nthawi yausiku amagona pang’ono. (Amadzuka nachita mapemphero mochulukitsa)
  51,18,"“Ndipo kum’bandakucha, iwo amapempha chikhululuko"
  51,19,“Ndipo m’chuma chawo mudali gawo (lodziwika) la opempha ndi osapempha (mwa osauka)
  51,20,"“M’nthaka muli zizindikiro kwa otsimikiza, (zosonyeza kuti Allah alipo)"
  51,21,“Ndi mwa inu nomwe; kodi simuona
  51,22,"“Ndipo kumwamba kuli zokuthandizani (pa moyo wanu), ndi zimene mukulonjezedwa"
  51,23,"“Ndikulumbilira Mbuye wa kumwamba ndi pansi, ndithu zimenezo ndi zoona monga kulili kuyankhula kwanu"
  51,24,“Kodi yakufika nkhani ya alendo a Ibrahim; (angelo) olemekezeka
  51,25,"“Pamene adalowa kwa iye ndi kunena kuti: “Salaam,” (“Mtendere”)! Iye adayankha: “Salaam,” (“Mtendere) inu ndinu anthu osadziwika (achilendo).”"
  51,26,"“Adatembenukira kwa akunyumba ake (mwakachetechete), ndipo adadza ndi nyama ya mwana wa ng’ombe yonona (yowotcha)"
  51,27,"“Naipereka kwa iwo (koma sadadye); iye adanena (modabwa): “Kodi bwanji simukudya?”"
  51,28,"“Mumtima mwake adadzazidwa mantha ndi iwo. Iwo adati: “Usaope,” ndipo adamuuza nkhani yabwino ya kubala mwana wodziwa"
  51,29,"“Adadza mkazi wake ndi mkuwe (pamene adamva nkhani yabwino ija). Adadzimenya kunkhope (ndi dzanja lake kusonyeza kudabwa ndi kusatheka). Ndipo adati: (“Ine ndine) nkhalamba (ndiponso) chumba; (ndingabereke bwanji)?”"
  51,30,"“Iwo adati: “Momwemo, Mbuye wako wanena. Iye Ngwanzeru zakuya (pa chilichonse chimene akulamula); Ngodziwa; (palibe chimene chingabisike kwa Iye)"
  51,31,"“۞ (Ibrahim) adati: “Kodi nkhani yanu ndiyotani E inu otumidwa?”"
  51,32,"“Iwo adati: “Tatumizidwa kwa anthu oipa.”"
  51,33,““Kuti tiwagende ndi miyala yotenthedwa kuchokera kudongo.”
  51,34,““Yoikidwa chizindikiro cha aliyense wochimwa kuchokera kwa Mbuye wako.”
  51,35,“Tidawatulutsa okhulupirira omwe adali m’mudzimo
  51,36,“Sitidapeze mmenemo (okhulupirira ambiri) kupatula mnyumba imodzi ya Asilamu
  51,37,“Ndipo tidasiya pamenepo chizindikiro (chosonyeza kuonongeka kwa eni mudziwo kuti chikhale lingaliro) kwa amene akuopa chilango chopweteka
  51,38,“M’nkhani ya Mûsa (muli phunziro) pamene tidamtuma kwa Farawo uku atalimbikitsidwa ndi chisonyezo choonekera
  51,39,"“Koma Farawo adanyoza (kukhulupirira Mûsa) chifukwa chotama nyonga zake, ndipo adati: “Uyu ndi wamatsenga kapena wamisala.”"
  51,40,“Tidamlanga pamodzi ndi khamu lake la nkhondo ndi kuwaponya mnyanja; iye ali wodzudzulidwa
  51,41,“Ndipo m’nkhani ya Âdi (muli phunziro) pamene tidawatumizira chimphepo (chamkuntho) chopanda chabwino mkati mwake
  51,42,“Chomwe sichisiya chinthu chimene chachidutsa koma kuchichita monga chofumbwa
  51,43,"“Ndipo m’nkhani ya Samudu (muli chisonyezo) pamene kudanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Sangalalani (mnyumba zanu) mpaka nthawi yaikika.”"
  51,44,“Koma adadzikweza (ponyozera) lamulo la Mbuye wawo. Choncho chiphokoso chidawaononga uku akupenya
  51,45,“Sadathe kuimilira ndi (kuthawa) ndiponso sadali wodzipulumutsa
  51,46,“Naonso anthu a Nuh (tidawaononga) kale chifukwa iwo adali anthu otuluka mchilamulo (cha Allah)
  51,47,“Thambo tidalimanga mwamphamvu (ndi luntha); ndipo tingathe kuchita zochuluka (kuposa zimenezi)
  51,48,“Ndipo nthaka tidaiyala; taonani kukonza bwino Ife amene tidakonza nthaka
  51,49,“Ndipo m’chinthu chilichonse talenga ziwiriziwiri kuti inu mulingalire (ndi kukhulupirira mphamvu Zathu)
  51,50,“Thawirani kwa Allah. Ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,“Ndipo musadzipangire mulungu wina wompembedza ndi kumuphatikiza ndi Allah. Ndithu ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera poyera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"“Momwemo (ndimo idalili mibadwo yakale pamodzi ndi aneneri awo); palibe Mthenga amene adawadzera anthu akale, anthu akowa kulibe, popanda kumnena kuti: “Ndiwamatsenga kapena wamisala.”"
  51,53,"“Kodi adalangizana za mawuwa pakati pawo? Iyayi, koma iwo ndianthu opyola malire"
  51,54,"“Choncho apatukire iwo (amakani), iwe suli wodzudzulidwa (pakuleka kwawo kuyankha kuitana)"
  51,55,“Kumbutsa. Ndithu kukumbutsa kumawathandiza okhulupirira
  51,56,“Sindidalenge ziwanda (majini) ndi anthu koma kuti azindipembedza
  51,57,“Sindifuna kwa iwo chithandizo ndiponso sindifuna kuti azindidyetsa
  51,58,"“Ndithu Allah ndi Amene amapereka rizq; Iye ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wolimba, (salaphera kanthu)"
  51,59,“Ndithu amene adzichitira okha chinyengo (pokana ndi kutsutsa) ali nalo gawo la chilango monga gawo la anzawo (a mibadwo yakale); choncho asandifulumizitse (kutsitsa chilango nthawi yake isanafike)
  51,60,“Kuonongeka kuli pa amene atsutsa za tsiku lawo limene alonjezedwa
  52,1,“Ndikulumbilira phiri la Turi (ku Sinai pamene Mûsa adalankhulana ndi Allah)
  52,2,“Ndi buku lolembedwa
  52,3,“M’mipukutu yazikopa zotambasuka (zosavuta kuwerenga)
  52,4,“Ndi nyumba yopitako kawirikawiri (pochitamo mapemphero)
  52,5,“Ndi thambo limene latukulidwa (popanda mzati)
  52,6,“Ndi nyanja yodzadza ndi madzi
  52,7,“Ndithu chilango cha Mbuye wako (chimene wawalonjeza nacho osakhulupirira) chiwapeza (popanda chipeneko)
  52,8,“Palibe wochichotsa (pa iwo)
  52,9,“Pa tsikulo thambo lidzagwedezeka; kugwedezeka kwamphamvu
  52,10,“Ndipo mapiri adzayenda mwamphavu (kuchoka m’malo mwake)
  52,11,“Kuonongeka koopsa pa tsiku limenelo kuzakhala pa otsutsa choonadi
  52,12,“Iwo amene akungosewera mzinthu zopanda pake
  52,13,“Tsiku limene adzakankhidwira mwamphamvu ku Jahannam (ku Moto Woopsa)
  52,14,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa iwo): “Uwu ndi Moto uja umene mudali kuutsutsa (pa dziko lapansi)"
  52,15,“Kodi awa ndi matsenga kapena inu simukuona
  52,16,"“Lowanimo, (mulawe kupsereza kwake) pirirani (ndi mavuto ake) kapena musapirire, ndichimodzimodzi kwa inu. Ndithu mulipidwa pazimene munkachita.”"
  52,17,“Ndithu oopa Allah adzakhala m’Minda yamtendere ndi chisangalalo chachikulu
  52,18,“Uku akukondwelera pazimene wawapatsa Mbuye wawo ndipo Mbuye wawo azawatchinjiriza ku chilango cha Jahena
  52,19,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa iwo): “Idyani (chakudya chamtendere); ndipo imwani mosangalala kukhala malipiro pazimene munkachita (pa dziko lapansi).”"
  52,20,“Uku atakhala moyadzamira pa makama ondandika bwino ndi kuyalidwa bwino; ndipo tidzawakwatitsa akazi ophanuka maso mokongola
  52,21,“Ndipo amene akhulupirira ndipo ana awo nkuwatsatira pa chikhulupiliro tidzawakumanitsa iwo ndi ana awowo ndipo sitikawachepetsera kalikonse m’mphoto za ntchito zawo; munthu aliyense adzakoledwa ndi zochita zake
  52,22,“Ndipo tidzawaonjezera zipatso ndi nyama imene adzakhala akuilakalaka
  52,23,“Azikalandirana m’menemo (mwachikondi wina ndi mnzake) chikho chodzaza ndi zakumwa; sipakakhala kwa iwo zolankhula zachabe ngakhale zochita zamachimo
  52,24,“Ndipo azikawazungulira anyamata owatumikira onga ngale yosungidwa m’chigoba chake (kukongola kwawo)
  52,25,“Azidzatembenukirana wina ndi mnzake uku akufunsana (za kukula kwa mtendere umene adzakhala nawo ndi kuti adaupeza chotani)
  52,26,"“Adzanena: “Ife tidali oopa chilango cha Allah pakati pa maanja athu (tisadalandire mtenderewu)"
  52,27,“Ndipo Allah watidalitsa ndipo watitchinjiriza ku chilango cha Moto
  52,28,"“Ndithu ife timampembedza (kalero pa dziko lapansi) ndithu Iye Yekha Ngwabwino, Ngwachifundo.”"
  52,29,"“Choncho kumbutsa, iwe suli mlosi kapena wamisala pamtendere wa Mbuye wako"
  52,30,"“Kapena akunena kuti ndiwe mlakatuli, tikumuyembekezera imfa impeze"
  52,31,"“Nena: “Yembekezerani! Ndithu ine ndili nanu mwa mmodzi woyembekezera.”"
  52,32,“Kapena nzeru zawo ndizo zikuwauza izi kapena iwo ndi anthu opyola malire
  52,33,"“Kodi akunena kuti: “Wadzipekera (Mtumiki {s.a.w} Qur’an)?” Iyayi, koma iwo sakukhulupirira"
  52,34,"“Tero abwere ndi nkhani yofanana ndi iyo (Qur’an) ngati ali owona m’kuyankhula kwawo (koti Mtumiki{s.a.w} wapeka Qur’an"
  52,35,“Kapena adalengedwa popanda Mlengi kapena iwo adadzilenga okha (nchifukwa sakuvomereza za Mlengi Wopembedzedwayo)
  52,36,“Kapena ndiwo adalenga thambo ndi nthaka? Koma satsimikiza (zoyenera kumchitira Mlengi)
  52,37,“Kapena nkhokwe (za zabwino) za Mbuye wako zili ndi iwo (kotero kuti akuzigwiritsa ntchito mmene angafunire?) Kapena iwo ngopambana
  52,38,"“Nanga kapena ali nawo makwelero (amene akukwelera kumwamba) kotero kuti akumvetsera zimene Allah akulamula? Choncho, omvetsera awo abwere nawo umboni owonekera (osonyeza kuona kwawo pa zimene akunenazi)"
  52,39,“Kapena Iye (Allah) ndiye ali ndi ana akazi ndipo inu muli ndi ana amuna
  52,40,“Kapena ukuwapempha malipiro alionse (pofikitsa uthenga); kotero kuti iwo akulemedwa ndi kulipira (uthengawu)
  52,41,“Kapena iwo amadziwa zamseri kotero kuti iwo akumalemba (zimene afuna)
  52,42,“Kapena akufuna kukuchitira chiwembu (ndikuononga uthenga wako?) Koma amene sadakhulupirire ndiwo omwe chiwabwelere chiwembu (chawo)
  52,43,"“Kodi ali naye wompembedza, osati Allah (amene angawateteze ku chilango cha Allah)? Allah wapatukana ndi zimene akumuphatikiza nazo"
  52,44,"“Koma akaona gawo lathambo likugwa (kuti liwalange) akunena (mwamakani ndi kunyada): “Uwu ndi mtambo umene wasonkhanitsa madzi a mvula.”"
  52,45,“Choncho asiye; (usalabadire za iwo) mpaka pomwe adzakumana ndi tsiku lawo limene adzaonongedwa
  52,46,“Tsiku lomwe chiwembu chawo sichidzawathandiza chilichonse; ndipo iwo sadzapulumutsidwa
  52,47,“Ndipo ndithu amene achita zosalungama ali nacho chilango china chosakhala chimenecho (chisanawapeze chilango cha ku Âkhira)! Koma ambiri a iwo sadziwa (zimenezi)
  52,48,“Ndipo pirira ndi lamulo la Mbuye wako ndithu iwe ndiwe wosungidwa ndi kuyang’aniridwa ndi Ife; ndipo lemekeza ndi kumuyamika Mbuye ako pamene ukuimilira (kupemphera)
  52,49,“Ndipo m’gawo la usiku mlemekeze Iye ndi nthawi yolowa nyenyezi
  53,1,“Ndikulumbira nyenyezi pamene zikulowa
  53,2,“Sadasokere m’bale wanu (Mtumiki panjira ya choonadi) ndipo sadakhulupirire zonama
  53,3,“Ndipo sayankhula zofuna za mtima wake
  53,4,"“Iyoyi (Qur’an imene akuinena), sichina, koma ndichivumbulutso chovumbulutsidwa"
  53,5,“Adamphunzitsa (chivumbulutsochi) (Jibril) wanyonga zambiri
  53,6,“Wanzeru zakuya; ndipo adakhazikika (m’maonekedwe ake)
  53,7,“Ali m’chizimezime kumwamba
  53,8,"“Kenako (Jibril) adamuyandikira (Mtumiki {s.a.w}) ndikuonjezera kumuyandikira"
  53,9,"“(Kumuyandikira kwake) kudali ngati (mpata wa) nsonga ziwiri za uta, kapena kuyandikira kuposa apo"
  53,10,“(Choncho Jibril) adavumbulutsira kapolo wake (wa Allah) zimene adazivumbulutsa
  53,11,“Sudaname mtima (wa Mtumiki) pazimene adaziona
  53,12,“Kodi mukutsutsana naye (Mthenga wa Allah) pazimene adaziona
  53,13,“Ndipo ndithu adamuona (Jibril) m’kuona kachiwiri mkaonekedwe kake
  53,14,“Pa ‘Sidratil Muntaha’ (mtengo wamasawu pothera zinthu zonse)
  53,15,"“Pafupi pake pali Janatu Ma’awa, (munda wokhalamo)"
  53,16,“Pomwe chophimba chidaphimba msawuwo
  53,17,“Maso ake sadaphonye kapena kupyola malire (oikidwa)
  53,18,"“Ndithu (Mneneri Muhammad {s.a.w}) adaona zina mwa zizindikiro zikuluzikulu za Mbuye wake (zosonyeza mphamvu Zake)"
  53,19,“Kodi mwamuona Laat ndi Uzza
  53,20,"“Ndi Manata; (fano lanu) lina lachitatu, (kuti iwowa ndi milungu)"
  53,21,"“Kodi mwadzisankhira ana aamuna (kukhala anu), ndi aakazi nkukhala a Iye (Allah)"
  53,22,“Choncho kugawa kumeneko nkopanda chilungamo (pompatsa Allah zimene mumazida)
  53,23,"“Sali (mafanowo) chilichonse koma ndi maina basi omwe mudawatcha inu ndi makolo anu, (molingana ndi zilakolako zanu zachabe); Allah sadatsitse umboni pazimenezo (wotsimikiza pamawu anuwo). Sakutsatira koma zoganizira basi ndi zimene ikufuna mitima (yawo yopotoka). Ndithu chidawadzera chiongoko kuchokera kwa Mbuye wawo (chomwe m’kati mwake mudali kuongoka kwawo akadachitsatira)"
  53,24,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti adzapeza chilichonse chimene akuchilakalaka
  53,25,“Moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro ndi wadziko lapansi ngwa Allah Yekha
  53,26,“Ndipo kuli angelo ambiri kumwamba omwe kuchondelera kwawo sikungathandize china chilichonse pokhapokha Allah ataloleza kwa amene wamfuna ndi kumuyanja
  53,27,"“Ndithu amene sakhulupirira za (Moyo wa) tsiku lachimaliziro, amawatcha angelo kuti ndiakazi"
  53,28,“Ndipo alibe kudziwa kulikonse pa zimenezo sakutsata china koma maganizo. Ndipo ndithu kuganizira sikuthandiza chilichonse pofuna kupeza choonadi
  53,29,“Choncho apewe (osakhulupirirawa) amene anyozera chikumbutso Chathu (Qur’an); ndipo palibe chimene akufuna koma moyo wa padziko lapansi basi
  53,30,“Zimenezo ndiwo mapeto a kudziwa kwawo. Ndithu Mbuye wako Ngodziwa kwambiri za amene akusokera njira Yake ndiponso akudziwa bwino za yemwe wawongoka
  53,31,"“Ndipo zonse za kumwamba ndi zadziko lapansi nza Allah Yekha, (pozilenga ndi kuziyang’anira), kuti adzawalipire amene adaipitsa pa zimene adachita ndi kutinso adzawalipire zabwino amene adachita zabwino"
  53,32,"“Amene akuwapewa machimo akuluakulu ndi zadama, kupatula timachimo tating’onoting’ono (timene Allah amatikhululuka); ndithu Mbuye wako ndiwokhululuka kwakukulu. Iye akudziwa chikhalidwe chanu kuyambira pomwe adakulengani kuchokera m’nthaka ndi pamene inu mudali makanda m’mimba mwa amayi anu (mosinthasintha; mosiyanasiyana). Choncho musadzitame nokha kuyera mtima; Iye Ngodziwa kwambiri za yemwe akumuopa (Allah)"
  53,33,“Kodi wamuona yemwe wadzipatula (pakusiya kutsatira choonadi)
  53,34,“Ndipo wapereka (chuma) chochepa nasiyanso kuperekako
  53,35,"“Kodi akudziwa zamseri, kotero kuti akuziwona (zomwe wadza nazo (Mtumiki {s.a.w) kuti sizoona"
  53,36,“Kapena sadauzidwe zomwe zidali m’mabuku a Mûsa
  53,37,“Ndi Ibrahim amene adakwaniritsa (lonjezo la Allah)
  53,38,“Kuti mzimu wamachimo sungasenze machimo a mzimu wina
  53,39,“Ndi kutinso munthu sakalipidwa koma zimene adachita
  53,40,“Ndipo ndithu ntchito zake zidzaonekera
  53,41,“Kenako (munthu) adzalipidwa malipiro okwanira (pa ntchito zake zimene amachita)
  53,42,“Ndipo ndithu kwa Mbuye wako yekha ndiwo malekezero (a chilichonse)
  53,43,“Ndithu Iye ndiAmene amapereka chisangalalo ndi zoliritsa
  53,44,“Ndipo Iye yekha ndi Amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene adalenga mitundu iwiri: chachimuna ndi chachikazi, (anthu ndi zamoyo zina)"
  53,46,“Kuchokera m’mbewu ya moyo pamene imafwamphukira (m’chiberekero)
  53,47,“Ndipo ndithu ndi udindo Wake kuukitsa kwina (pambuyo pa imfa)
  53,48,“Ndipo Iye ndiAmene amapatsa chokwanira ndipo ndi amene amapatsa chosunga
  53,49,“Ndipo ndithu Iye ndi Mbuye wa nyenyezi yotchedwa Shiira
  53,50,“Ndipo Iye ndi amene adaononga Âdi oyamba; (anthu a Mneneri Hûd)
  53,51,“Ndi Samudu; (anthu a Mneneri Swaleh;) choncho sadasiye (ndi mmodzi yemwe wa iwo)
  53,52,"“Ndipo (adawaononganso) anthu a Nuh, kale (asadaononge Âdi ndi Samudu). Ndithu iwo adali osalungama ndi olumpha malire kwambiri (kuposa Âdi ndi Samudu)"
  53,53,"“Ndi midzi yotembenuzidwa kumwamba kukhala pansi, pansi kukhala kumwamba, (ya anthu a Luti) adaigwetsa"
  53,54,“Tero chidaivindikira (midziyo) chomwe chidaivindikira (chilango)
  53,55,“Kodi ndimtendere uti (mumtendere) wa Mbuye wako umene ukuukaikira
  53,56,“Uyu (Mtumiki) ndimchenjezi mwa achenjezi oyamba (amene adachenjezedwa nawo anthu a mibadwo yakale)
  53,57,“Chayandikira choyandikira (Qiyâma)
  53,58,“Palibe amene angachionetse koma Allah Yekha
  53,59,“Kodi mukuidabwa nkhaniyi (ya Qur’an moikana)
  53,60,“Mungoseka (mwachipongwe) ndipo simukulira (pamene mukuimva monga momwe akuchitira okhulupirira)
  53,61,“Ndipo mukunyozera
  53,62,“Mlambireni ndi kumpembedza Allah (amene wavumbulutsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chiongoko cha anthu)
  54,1,“Nthawi ya chimaliziro (Qiyâma) yayandikira ndipo mwezi wagawikana
  54,2,"“Koma akaona chozizwitsa akunyoza ndi kunena kuti: “Awa ndi matsenga womkeramkera patsogolo.”"
  54,3,“Ndipo adatsutsa (choonadi) ndi kutsatira zilakolako (zawo zoipa) koma chinthu chilichonse (cha Allah) nchokhazikika
  54,4,“Ndipo ndithu zidawafika nkhani zomwe zili zokwanira kuwaopseza
  54,5,“Nzeru zokwana koma machenjezo (kwa iwo) sanawathandize
  54,6,"“Choncho, apewe (iwe Mtumiki) osakhulupirira, (yembekezani) tsiku loitana woitana (wa Allah) ku chinthu chovuta kwambiri, (chodedwa ndi mitima)"
  54,7,“Maso awo ali zyoli chifukwa chakuopsa; adzatuluka m’manda uku ali ngati dzombe lobalalika (chifukwa cha kuchuluka)
  54,8,"“Akuthamangira kwa woitana (uku atatukula mitu yawo, osatha kucheukira kwina). Adzanena osakhulupirira (tsiku lachiweruziro): “Ili nditsiku lovuta kwambiri.”"
  54,9,"“Patsogolo pawo (Aquraishi) anthu a Nuh nawo adatsutsa, adamtsutsa kapolo Wathu nanena kuti: “Uyu ngwamisala!” Ndipo adaopsezedwa (ndi kuzunzidwa ndi mazunzo osiyanasiyana)"
  54,10,"“(Nuh) adaitana Mbuye wake (nati): “Ine ndagonjetsedwa (ndi anthu anga); choncho ndipulumutseni (kwa iwo).”"
  54,11,"“Tero tidatsekula makomo akumwamba ndi madzi otsika mopitiriza, mwamphamvu"
  54,12,“Ndipo tidaing’amba nthaka kukhala ndi akasupe (ofwamphuka madzi mwamphamvu). Choncho adakumana madzi (akumwamba ndi am’nthaka kuti awaononge) pamuyeso wopimidwa ndi kulamulidwa (ndi Allah)
  54,13,“Ndipo tidamnyamula Nuh pa chombo chamatabwa chokhomedwa ndi misomali (yamitengo)
  54,14,“Chinkayandama pamadzi ndi kuyang’aniridwa ndi Ife. Iyi ndi mphoto ya (Nuh) yemwe adakanidwa ndi anthu ake
  54,15,“Ndipo ndithu tidachisiya (chigumula) kukhala phunziro (pakuonongeka kwa osakhulupirira ndi kupulumuka kwa okhulupirira). Kodi alipo wolikumbukira (ndi kupeza nalo malango abwino)
  54,16,“Kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)
  54,17,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chikumbutso. Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)
  54,18,"“Âdi adamtsutsa (mneneri wawo Hud), kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)"
  54,19,"“Ndithu Ife tidawatumizira mphepo yozizira, yaphokoso, m’tsiku latsoka lopitilira"
  54,20,“Idawazula anthu (kuchoka m’malo mwawo ndi kuwaponya panthaka ali akufa) ngati matsinde a mitengo yakanjedza ozulidwa m’malo mwake
  54,21,“Kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa onyoza)
  54,22,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chikumbutso. Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)
  54,23,“Asamudu adatsutsa machenjezo
  54,24,"“Ndipo adati: “Kodi titsatire munthu mmodzi wochokera mwa ife? Ndithu ife ngati titamtsatira ndiye kuti tili nkusokera ndiponso misala.”"
  54,25,"“Kodi am’vumbulutsira iye chikumbutso pakati pathu, (pomwe tili nawo oposa iye pa ulemelero)? Koma iye ndiwabodza ndi wodzitukumu.”"
  54,26,"“Mawa lino adzadziwa (tsiku lakuwatsikira chilango,) kuti ndiyani wabodza wodzitukumula (iwo kapena Swaleh)"
  54,27,"“(Tidamuuza mneneriyo kuti) ndithu Ife titumiza ngamira yaikazi kuti ikhale mayeso kwa iwo. Choncho adikire, ndipo pirira"
  54,28,“Ndipo auze kuti madzi agawidwa pakati pawo (ndi ngamira). Aliyense ali ndi tsiku lopita kukatunga
  54,29,“Koma adaitana mnzawo (wa mphulupulu). Choncho adakonzeka kupha ngamirayo ndipo adaipha
  54,30,“Kodi chidali bwanji chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga (kwa anthu otsutsa)
  54,31,“Ndithu tidawatumizira nkuwe umodzi choncho adakhala ngati udzu ndi mitengo youma yaomanga khola
  54,32,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an kuti ikhale chikumbutso. Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)
  54,33,“Anthu a Luti adatsutsa machenjezo (a mneneri wawo)
  54,34,"“Ndithu Ife tidawatumizira chimphepo champhamvu choulutsa miyala (ndi kuwagenda), kupatula akubanja la Luti; tidawapulumutsa (ku chilangocho) m’bandakucha"
  54,35,“(Choncho kupulumukako kudali) chisomo chochokera kwa Ife (pa iwo). Momwemo ndimo timamlipirira wothokoza
  54,36,“Ndipo ndithu (Luti) adawachenjeza anthu ake za kulanga Kwathu koopsa. Koma adakaikira machenjezo (ake ndi kumtsutsa)
  54,37,"“Ndipo ndithu adafuna kwa iye kuti awapatse alendo ake (kuti achite nawo zauve), koma tidafafaniza maso awo (kuti ikhale mphoto pa zimene adafunazo). (Ndipo tidawauza): “Choncho lawani chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga.”"
  54,38,"“Ndipo ndithu chidawadzera mwadzidzidzi chilango chokhazikika, nthawi yam’mamawa"
  54,39,“Choncho (kudanenedwa kwa iwo) “Lawani chilango Changa ndi machenjezo Anga.”
  54,40,“Ndipo ndithu taifewetsa Qur’an (kuti ikhale chikumbutso). Kodi alipo woikumbukira (ndi kupeza nayo malangizo abwino)
  54,41,“Ndipo ndithu machenjezo (ondondozana) adawadzera anthu a Farawo (ndi iye mwini)
  54,42,"“Adatsutsa zozizwitsa Zathu zonse (zimene zidadza kupyolera m’manja mwa aneneri Athu). Choncho tidawalanga, kulanga kwa Wamphamvu (Wosapambanidwa), Wokhoza"
  54,43,“Kodi osakhulupirira anuwa ndi abwino kuposa iwo (kotero kuti sadzaonongedwa)? Kapena zalembedwa m’mabuku kuti inu mdzasiyidwa (sadzakuonongani monga momwe adawaonongera akale)
  54,44,"“Kapena akunena kuti: “Ife ndiochuluka titha kudziteteza (palibe angatipambane)?”"
  54,45,"“(Auze): Gululo ligonjetsedwa ndipo athawa ndi kutembenuza misana"
  54,46,"“Koma lonjezo la chilango chawo ndi tsiku la chiweruziro, ndipo tsiku la chiweruziro ndi latsoka lalikulu, lowawa kwabasi (kwa osakhulupirira)"
  54,47,“Ndithu oipa (mwa awa ndi aja) ali nkusokera ndi misala
  54,48,"“Tsiku limene adzakokedwera ku Moto ndi nkhope zawo, (kudzanenedwa kwa iwo:) “Lawani zowawa za Jahena (ndi kutentha kwake)"
  54,49,“Ndithu Ife tachilenga chinthu chilichonse ndi muyeso (kulingana ndi zolinga)
  54,50,"“Ndipo silili lamulo Lathu (pa chinthu tikachifuna) koma liwu limodzi, (timangoti kwa chinthucho: “Chitika.” Ndipo chimachitika mwachangu) ngati kuphethira kwa diso"
  54,51,"“Ndipo ndithu tidawaononga anzanu (onga inu osakhulupirira): Kodi alipo wokumbuka"
  54,52,“Ndipo chinthu chilichonse adachichita iwowo (pa dziko lapansi) chili mkaundula
  54,53,"“Ndipo ntchito iliyonse, yaing’ono kapena yaikulu, idalembedwa; (palibe chimene chingamsowe)"
  54,54,“Ndithu oopa Allah adzakhala m’Minda ya ulemelero waukulu ndi Mitsinje (yosiyanasiyana)
  54,55,"“Pokhala pabwino pachoonadi, (popanda mawu achabe ndi machimo), kwa Mfumu yokhoza chilichonse"
  55,1,“(Allah) Wachifundo chochuluka
  55,2,“Waphunzitsa Qur’an
  55,3,“Adalenga munthu
  55,4,“Adamphunzitsa kuyankhula
  55,5,“Dzuwa ndi mwezi zikuyenda mwachiwerengero
  55,6,"“Zomera zopanda tsinde ndi mitengo, zikulambira (Allah pachilichonse chimene wafuna mwa izo)"
  55,7,“Ndipo thambo adalitukula kumwamba ndipo adakhazikitsa sikelo (ya chilungamo)
  55,8,“Kuti musapyole malire ndi kuchita chinyengo poyesa
  55,9,“Choncho yesani sikelo mwachilungamo ndipo musapungule muyeso
  55,10,“Ndipo nthaka adaiyala (ndi kuikonza) kuti ikhale ya zolengedwa
  55,11,“M’menemo muli zipatso ndi mitengo ya kanjedza yokhala ndi mapava (a zipatso)
  55,12,"“Ndi mbewu zamakoko (kuti chikhale chakudya cha inu ndi ziweto zanu), ndipo mulinso m’menemo mmera wafungo labwino"
  55,13,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,14,“Adalenga munthu kuchokera ku dongo lolira monga ziwiya zadongo
  55,15,“Ndipo adalenga ziwanda kuchokera ku malawi a moto (wopanda utsi)
  55,16,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,17,“Mbuye wa kuvuma kuwiri ndiponso Mbuye wa kuzambwe kuwiri
  55,18,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,19,"“Adaika nyanja ziwiri zokumana (yamadzi amchere, ndi yamadzi ozizira)"
  55,20,"“Pakati pake pali chitsekerezo, sizilowana"
  55,21,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,22,“M’menemo mumatuluka ngale zing’onozing’ono ndi ngale zikuluzikulu
  55,23,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,24,"“Ndipo (Iye) ali nazo zombo (zimene zapangidwa ndi manja anu), zoyenda panyanja, zazikuluzikulu ngati mapiri"
  55,25,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,26,“Zonse zili pamenepo (pa dziko) nzakutha
  55,27,“Ndipo idzatsala nkhope ya Mbuye wako yaulemelero ndi mtendere
  55,28,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,29,"“(Onse) akumwamba ndi pansi akupempha Iye (zofuna zawo)! Tsiku lililonse Iye ali ndi zochita (monga kupatsa uyu ulemelero, ndi kutsitsa uyu)"
  55,30,"“(Inu zolengedwa zamitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,31,"“Posachedwapa (patsiku la chiweruziro), tidzaikapo mtima pa chiwerengero chanu (cha zochita zanu) inu anthu ndi ziwanda"
  55,32,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,33,"“E inu ziwanda ndi anthu! Ngati mungathe kutuluka m’mphepete mwa thambo ndi nthaka (pothawa Allah), tulukani! Simungathe kutuluka pokhapokha ndi mphamvu. (Koma inu simungathe kutero)"
  55,34,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,35,“Mudzathiridwa malawi a moto ndi mtovu wa moto wosungunuka ndipo simungathe kupulumuka (ku chilango chimenechi)
  55,36,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,37,“(Kumbuka) pamene thambo lidzang’ambika ndi kukhala lofiira ngati chikopa chofiira (kapena ngati mafuta oyaka)
  55,38,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,39,"“Ndipo patsikulo munthu ndi chiwanda, sadzafunsidwa (aliyense) za tchimo lake"
  55,40,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,41,“Adzadziwika oipa (pakati pa anthu ndi ziwanda) ndi zizindikiro zawo (zowazindikiritsa). Ndipo adzagwidwa maliombo awo ndi mapazi awo (ndi kuponyedwa ku Jahena)
  55,42,"“((Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,43,"“(Kudzanenedwa mowadandaulitsa): Iyi ndi Jahannam yomwe adali kuitsutsa oipa"
  55,44,"“Adzakhala akuyenda pakati pa moto ndi pakati pa madzi owira, otentha kwambiri"
  55,45,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,46,"“Koma amene waopa kuti adzaimitsidwa kwa Mbuye wake (pa nthawi ya chiweruziro), adzalandira minda iwiri (yaikulu yamtendere)"
  55,47,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,48,“(Minda ya mitengo) yanthambi zofwanthamuka
  55,49,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,50,"“M’menemo muli akasupe awiri, omwe akuyenda"
  55,51,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,52,"“M’menemo muli zipatso za mtundu uliwonse, mitundu iwiri iwiri"
  55,53,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,54,"“Atatsamira pa zoyala, mkati mwake mosokelera veleveti wochindikala; ndipo zipatso zam’minda iwiriyi nzapafupi (kuzithyola)"
  55,55,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,56,"“M’mindamo muli akazi oyang’ana amuna awo okha basi, (mawuthu) omwe sadakhalepo malo amodzi ndi munthu kapena chiwanda asadakumane ndi iwo"
  55,57,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,58,“Kukongola kwake (akaziwo) kuli ngati ngale zikuluzikulu ndi zing’onozing’ono
  55,59,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,60,“Malipiro a ntchito zabwino ndikulandira zabwino basi
  55,61,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,62,“Ndipo kuonjezera paminda iwiri (ija) palinso minda ina iwiri
  55,63,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,64,"“Yobiriwira, kwambiri"
  55,65,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,66,“M’menemo muli akasupe awiri ofwamphuka madzi mwaphamvu
  55,67,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,68,"“Mmenemo muli zipatso, mitengo yakanjedza ndi yamikangaza"
  55,69,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,70,"“M’menemo muli akazi amakhalidwe abwino, owala nkhope"
  55,71,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,72,"“Okongola maso, achikhalire m’mahema (m’matenti) awo"
  55,73,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,74,“Amene sadakhalepo malo amodzi ndi munthu kapena chiwanda asadakumane ndi iwo
  55,75,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,76,"“Uku atatsamira misamiro yawofuwofu yokutidwa ndi zobiriwira; ndi zoyala zokongola, zakapangidwe kabwino"
  55,77,"“(Inu zolengedwa za mitundu iwiri, anthu ndi ziwanda), kodi ndi mtendere uti wa Mbuye wanu umene mukuukana (kuti si Wake)"
  55,78,“Latukuka ndi kudalitsika dzina la Mbuye wako Mwini ulemelero ndi ufulu
  56,1,“Chikadzachitika chochitikacho (Qiyâma)
  56,2,“Palibe wotsutsa za kuchitika kwake
  56,3,“Chidzatsitsa (oipa) ndi kutukula (abwino)
  56,4,“Nthaka ikadzagwedezeka kwamphamvu
  56,5,“Ndipo mapiri akadzaperedwaperedwa
  56,6,“Nkukhala fumbi longouluka
  56,7,"“Choncho, inu mudzakhala m’magulu atatu (kulingana ndi zochita zanu)"
  56,8,“Anthu akumanja (abwino;) taonani kukula kwa ulemelero wa anthu akumanja
  56,9,“Ndi anthu akumanzere (oipa;) taonani kuipa khalidwe la anthu akumanzere
  56,10,“Ndipo otsogola (pochita zabwino pa dziko) adzakhalanso otsogola (polandira ulemu tsiku lachimaliziro)
  56,11,“Iwowo ndioyandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,12,“M’minda yamtendere
  56,13,"“(Iwowo oyandikitsidwawo), gulu lalikulu lochokera kumibadwo yakale"
  56,14,“Ndipo ochepa ochokera ku mbadwo wotsirizira
  56,15,“Uku ali m’makama (m’mabedi) olukidwa ndi zingwe zagolide
  56,16,“Atatsamira m’makamawo uku akuyang’anizana (mwachikondi)
  56,17,“Anyamata osasintha adzakhala akuwazungulira iwo (ndi kuwatumikira)
  56,18,"“Uku atatenga matambula ndi maketulo (odzaza ndi zakumwa za ku Jannah), ndi zipanda zodzaza ndi zakumwa zochokera mu akasupe oyenda"
  56,19,“(Zakumwa zake) zosapweteketsa mutu ndiponso zosaledzeretsa
  56,20,“Ndi zipatso (zamitundumitundu) zimene azikazisankha
  56,21,“Ndi nyama yambalame imene mitima yawo izikafuna
  56,22,“Ndi akazi ophanuka maso mokongola
  56,23,“(Kukongola kwawo) ndiye ngati ngale zosungidwa bwino mzigoba zake
  56,24,“Kukhala mphoto chifukwa cha zimene amachita (zabwino padziko lapansi)
  56,25,“M’menemo sakamva mawu achabe ngakhale (mawu a) machimo
  56,26,"“Koma mawu oti: “Mtendere! Mtendere!”"
  56,27,“Anthu akudzanja lamanja. Taonani kukula malipiro a anthu akudzanja lamanja
  56,28,“(Adzakhala m’mithunzi ya) mitengo ya masawu yopanda minga
  56,29,“Ndi mitengo ya nthochi yobereka kwambiri
  56,30,"“Ndi m’mithunzi yotambasuka kwambiri, yosachoka"
  56,31,“Ndi madzi oyenda mosalekeza
  56,32,“Ndi zipatso zambiri
  56,33,"“Zopezeka mnyengo zonse, ndiponso zosaletsedwa (kwa amene akuzifuna)"
  56,34,“Ndi zoyala zapamwamba (zawofuwofu)
  56,35,“Ndithu tidzawalenga (akazi okhulupirira) m’kalengedwe kapamwamba
  56,36,“Tidzawapanga kukhala anamwali
  56,37,“Okondedwa ndi amuna awo; ofanana misinkhu
  56,38,“A anthu akudzanja la manja
  56,39,“Gulu lalikulu lochokera ku m’badwo woyamba
  56,40,“Ndiponso gulu lalikulu lochokera ku mibadwo yotsiriza
  56,41,“Anthu akudzanja lakumanzere. Taonani chilango choopsa kwa anthu akudzanja lakumanzere
  56,42,“Adzakhala mu mvuchi wamoto ndi m’madzi owira
  56,43,“Ndi mumthunzi wa utsi wakuda
  56,44,“Siwoziziritsa ndiponso siwosangalatsa
  56,45,“Ndithu iwo amakhala kalelo mosangalala (samalabadira kumvera Allah)
  56,46,“Ndipo amapitiriza kuchita machimo aakulu (polinga kuti palibe kuuka ku imfa)
  56,47,"“Ndipo amanena (motsutsa); “Kodi tikadzafa nkusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa ofumbwa, tidzaukitsidwanso?”"
  56,48,““Kodi ndi makolo athu akale (adzaukitsidwanso!)”
  56,49,"“Nena kwa iwo (poyankha kutsutsa kwawo). Ndithudi, amibadwo yoyamba ndi mibadwo yomaliza (omwe inu muli m’gulu lawo)"
  56,50,“Adzasonkhanitsidwa m’nthawi ya tsiku lomwe lakhazikitsidwa
  56,51,"“Kenako inu osokera (njira yachilungamo), otsutsa (za kuuka)"
  56,52,"“Mudzadya (ku Jahannam) mtengo wa Zakkum, (mtengo wowawa wopezeka mu Jahannam)"
  56,53,“Mudzakhutitsa mimba zanu ndi umenewu (chifukwa cha njala yadzaoneni)
  56,54,“(Mkhuto wa mtengowo) adzamwera madzi owira
  56,55,“Adzamwa monga mmene imamwera ngamira yodwala matenda aludzu
  56,56,“Ili ndi phwando lawo tsiku lamalipiro
  56,57,“Ife tidakulengani kodi nchifukwa ninji simukukhulupirira
  56,58,“Tandiuzani za madzi (ambewu ya munthu) amene mumawathira m’chiberekero
  56,59,“Kodi inu ndiamene mumawalenga (madziwo ndi kumayang’anira mkusinthasintha kwake kuti akhale cholengedwa) kapena Ife ndiamene timawalenga
  56,60,“Ife tidalamula imfa pakati panu ndipo Ife sitili wolephera
  56,61,“Kubweretsa ena m’malo mwanu ndi kukulengani mwamaonekedwe ena omwe simumawadziwa
  56,62,“Ndipo ndithu mukdziwa kalengedwe koyamba; nanga bwanji simukukumbukira
  56,63,“Tandiuzani za zimene mukubzala
  56,64,“Kodi ndinu amene mukuzimeretsa kapena ndife Amene tikuzimeretsa
  56,65,“Tikadafuna tikadazitembenuza (mbewu zimenezo kukhala zouma isanakwane nthawi yake yozithyola) choncho mukadakhala mukudandaula
  56,66,"“(Uku mukunena:) “Ndithu ife tangotaya chuma chathu (padera);”"
  56,67,““Koma ife tamanidwa (phindu la khama lathu).”
  56,68,“Kodi mukuwaona madzi amene mukumwa
  56,69,“Kodi ndinu amene mudawatsitsa ku mitambo kapena ndife Amene timawatsitsa
  56,70,“Tikadafuna tikadawapanga kukhala amchere; nanga nchifukwa ninji simuthokoza
  56,71,“Kodi mukuwuona moto umene mumaukoleza
  56,72,“Kodi ndinu amene mudameretsa mitengo yake kapena Ndife tidaipanga
  56,73,"“Ife taupanga kuti ukhale chikumbutso (cha Moto watsiku lachimaliziro akauona), ndikuti ukhale chothandiza kwa anthu apaulendo (amene akuyenda m’chipululu)"
  56,74,"“Choncho, pitiriza kulemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wamkulu"
  56,75,"“Ndikulumbilira motsimikiza, mmene mumatsikira nyenyezi (pomwe zikulowa)"
  56,76,"“Ndithu kulumbira uku, mukadakhala olingalira, nkwakukulu kwabasi (pazimene kukusonya)"
  56,77,“Ndithu iyi ndi Qur’an yolemekezeka (ndipo mkati mwake muli zithandizo zambiri)
  56,78,“Idachokera mu buku lotetezedwa
  56,79,“Salikhudza kupatula okhawo oyeretsedwa (angelo)
  56,80,“Chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  56,81,“Kodi nkhani iyi (ya Qur’an) ndiyomwe inu mukuinyozera
  56,82,“Kodi mwakuchita kukanira kukhala kuthokoza kwanu pa zimene wakupatsani
  56,83,“Mmaona bwanji (mzimu wa mmodzi wa inu) ukafika kummero (panthawi ya imfa)
  56,84,“Uku inu panthawi imeneyo mukuona zimenezo
  56,85,"“Pomwe Ife tili pafupi ndi iye kuposa inu, koma inu simuona"
  56,86,“Mukadakhala kuti simuzalipidwa (pa zomwe mukuchita)
  56,87,“Bwenzi mukuubweza (mzimuwo) ngati mukunena zoona
  56,88,“Ngati (amene yamfikira imfayo) adali mmodzi wa woyandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  56,89,“Kobwerera kwake ndi kumpumulo ndi mtendere ndi kupatsidwa zonunkhira ndiponso Munda wamtendere
  56,90,“Ndipo ngati adali mmodzi wa anthu akudzanja lamanja
  56,91,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa iye:) “Mtendere ukhale pa iwe, amene udali m’gulu la anthu akudzanja lakumanja (anthu abwino).”"
  56,92,"“Koma ngati adali mmodzi wa anthu otsutsa, osokera"
  56,93,“Phwando lamadzi owira (ndilake)
  56,94,“Ndi kupsa m’moto wa Jahena
  56,95,"“Ndithu izi ndizoona, zotsimikizika"
  56,96,“Choncho lemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wamkulu
  57,1,"“Chilichonse chakumwamba ndi chapansi chikulemekeza Allah (ndi kumuyeretsa kumakhalidwe opunguka) ndipo Iye ndi Mwini Mphamvu, Wanzeru zakuya"
  57,2,"“Ufumu wakumwamba ndi pansi, Ngwake amapereka moyo ndi imfa. ndipo Iye Ngwamphamvu pa chilichonse"
  57,3,"“Iye ndi Oyamba (adalipo chilichonse chisadayambe); Wamuyaya (zonse zikadzatha); Woonekera (mzisonyezo pa chinthu chilichonse), Wobisika mkati kwambiri (saonedwa ndi maso pamoyo uno), Iye Ngodziwa chilichonse (kunja ndi mkati mwake)"
  57,4,"“Iye ndi Amene adalenga kumwamba ndi pansi (ndi zonse zammenemo) m’masiku asanu ndi limodzi kenako adakhazikika pa Arsh (Mpando Wake wachifumu monga momwe Iye adziwira polongosola ufumu Wake). Akudziwa chilichonse cholowa m’nthaka ndi chimene chikutuluka m’menemo; ndi chilichonse chimene chikutsika kuchokera kumwamba ndi chimene chikukwera kumeneko. Ndipo Iye ali nanu paliponse pamene muli. Ndithu Allah amaona chilichonse chimene mukuchita, (sichibisika chilichonse kwa Iye)"
  57,5,“Ufumu wakumwamba ndi pansi Ngwake ndipo kwa Allah nkobwerera zinthu (zonse)
  57,6,"“Usiku amawulowetsa mu usana, ndipo usana amawulowetsa mu usiku. (Choncho kumasiyana kutalika kwake); ndipo Iye Ngodziwa zobisika za m’zifuwa (ndi zoganiza za m’mitima)"
  57,7,"“Khulupirirani Allah ndi Mthenga Wake, ndipo perekani (pa njira ya Allah m’chuma chimene Allah wakupatsani uchiyang’anira. Choncho mwa inu amene akhulupirira (mwa Allah ndi mthenga Wake) ndikupereka (zimene awapatsa) iwo ali ndi malipiro aakulu (kwa Allah)"
  57,8,"“Kodi nchifukwa ninji simukhulupirira Allah pomwe Mtumiki akukuitanani kuti mukhulupirire Mbuye wanu (ndi kukulimbitsani pa zimenezo) chikhalirecho (Iye) adalandira lonjezo lanu, (muli mumsana wa tate wanu Adam kuti mdzakhulupirira,) ngati mulidi okhulupirira"
  57,9,"“Iye ndi Amene akuvumbulutsa kwa kapolo Wake Ayah (ndime) zofotokoza mwatsatanetsatane kuti akutulutseni mum’dima (wa kusokera) ndi kukuikani ku chiongoko cha kuunika. Ndipo ndithu Allah Ngoleza kwa inu, Ngwachisoni"
  57,10,"“Kodi ndichifukwa chiani simukupereka pa njira ya Allah (chuma chanu) pamene Allah Ndimwini wa zosiyidwa zonse za kumwamba ndi za m’dziko lapansi. Sali ofanana mwa inu amene adapereka chuma (panjira ya Allah) pamodzi ndi kumenya nkhondo usadagonjetsedwe (mzinda wa Makka), iwowo ndiomwe ali ndi ulemelero waukulu kuposa amene apereka chuma chawo ndi kumenya nkhondo pambuyo. Koma onsewo Allah wawalonjeza zabwino (ngakhale ali osiyana ulemelero wawo); ndipo Allah akudziwa zonse zimene muchita. (Choncho aliyense adzalipidwa molingana ndi zimene amachita)"
  57,11,“Kodi ndani (okhulupirira) amene angamkongoze Allah ngongole yabwino kuti amuchulukitsire malipiro ake? Ndipo iye adzalandira malipiro aulemu (pa tsiku la chiweruziro)
  57,12,"“Tsiku limene udzaona okhulupirira aamuna ndi aakazi dangalira lawo likuyenda patsogolo pawo ndi mbali ya kumanja kwao (uku angelo akunena kwa iwo): “Chisangalalo chanu lero ndi minda imene pansi pake pakuyenda mitsinje. Mukhala m’menemo nthawi yaitali! Kumeneku ndiko kupambana kwakukulu (kwa inu)"
  57,13,"“Tsiku limene achinyengo aamuna ndi achinyengo aakazi adzauza okhulupirira (kuti:) “Tidikireni kuti tipeze kuunika kwanu!” Kudzanenedwa (mwachipongwe): “Bwererani pambuyo panu mukafune kuunika kumeneko!” Choncho padzaikidwa mpanda pakati pawo (okhulupirira ndi achinyengo) umene udzakhala ndi khomo, mkati mwake muli chifundo ndi mtendere; kunja kwake kuli mazunzo ndi chilango"
  57,14,"“(Achinyengo) adzaitana okhulupirira ponena kuti: “Kodi sitidali nanu limodzi (pa dziko ndi kumatsagana nanu?” (Okhulupirira) adzati: “Inde! (Mudali nafe monga momwe mukunenera). Koma inu munadziononga nokha ndipo mumayembekezera (kuti okhulupirira awapeze mavuto ndi kuonongeka); mudakaikira (zinthu za chilengedwe chanu); choncho zikhulupiliro zanu zonama zidakunyengani pomwe mudali angwiro mpaka lamulo la Allah (imfa) lidakupezani, komanso adakunyengani onyenga (satana) za Allah"
  57,15,“Basi lero sililandiridwa dipo lochokera kwa inu (limene mungalipereke kuti mudzipulumutse ku chilango ngakhale likhale lamtengo wotani). Ndiponso sililandiridwa dipo lochokera kwa osakhulupirira (amene adalingana nanu n’kusakhulupirira kwawo Allah) malo anu nonsenu ndi ku Moto basi. Amenewa ndi malo okuyenerani. Kumeneko ndiko kobwerera koipa kwabasi
  57,16,“Kodi siidakwane nthawi kwa okhulupirira kuti mitima yawo idzichepetse pokumbukira Allah ndi zomwe zidavumbulutsidwa za chowonadi (Qur’an yolemekezeka)? Ndi kuti asakhale monga omwe adapatsidwa buku kale (Ayuda ndi Akhrisitu) amene nthawi yawo yosiyana ndi aneneri awo idali yaitali. Choncho mitima yawo idauma ndipo ambiri a iwo adatuluka m’chilamulo (cha Allah)
  57,17,“Dziwani kuti ndithu Allah amaukitsa nthaka itauma (poitsitsira mvula kuti mmera umere). Choncho takulongosolerani zisonyezo kuti inu mukhale ndi nzeru
  57,18,"“Ndithu amene akupereka sadaka amuna ndi akazi, ndi kumamkongoza Allah ngongole yabwino (Allah) adzawaonjezera malipiro pa zimenezi. Ndipo ali ndi malipiro aulemu"
  57,19,"“Ndipo amene akhulupirira Allah ndi aneneri Ake, iwowo ndiwo owona (pa chikhulupiliro); ndi ofera pa njira ya Allah (onsewo) azapeza malipiro awo ndi kuwala kwawo kwa Mbuye wawo. Koma amene sadakhulupirire ndi kutsutsa zisonyezo zathu iwowo ndi eni a ku Jahena"
  57,20,"“Dziwani kuti ndithu moyo wa pa dziko lapansi ndimasewera, chibwana, chokometsera chabe, chonyadiritsana pakati panu (pa ulemelero) ndi kuchulukitsa chuma ndi ana (pomwe zonsezo sizikhala nthawi yayitali;) fanizo lake lili ngati mvula yomwe mmera wake umakondweretsa alimi; kenako umafota, ndipo uuona uli wachikasu; kenako nkukhala odukaduka (oonongeka). Koma tsiku lachimaliziro kuli chilango cha ukali; ndi chikhululuko komanso chikondi chochokera kwa Allah. Moyo wa pa dziko lapansi suli kanthu, koma ndichisangalalo chonyenga basi"
  57,21,“Chitani changu (pa zinthu zokupatitsani) chikhululuko chochokera kwa Mbuye wanu ndi Munda wamtendere womwe mulifupi mwake muli ngati kutambasuka kwa kumwamba ndi pansi; wakonzedwera amene akhulupirira Allah ndi aneneri Ake; umenewo ndi ubwino wa Allah womwe akuupereka kwa amene wamfuna. Allah ndi Mwini ubwino waukulu
  57,22,“Silipezeka tsoka lililonse panthaka (monga chilala) ngakhale pamatupi anu koma lidalembedwa kale m’buku (la Allah) tisadalilenge ndi kulipereka. Ndithu zimenezo kwa Allah nzofewa
  57,23,"“(Takudziwitsani zimenezi) kuti musadandaule ndi chimene chakudutsani, ndi kutinso musakondwere monyada ndi chimene wakupatsani. Allah sakonda aliyense wodzitama, wonyada"
  57,24,"“Amene akuchita umbombo (ndi chuma chawo; ndipo osapereka pa njira ya Allah) ndi kumalamula anthu ena kuchita umbombo. Ndipo amene atembenuke (adzalandira chilango chachikulu), ndithu Allah Ngolemera, (sasaukira chilichonse kwa wina), Ngotamandidwa"
  57,25,"“Ndithu tidatuma atumiki Athu pamodzi ndi zozizwitsa. Ndipo tidavumbulutsa pamodzi ndi iwo mabuku ndi muyeso wa choonadi kuti anthu achite chilungamo. Ndipo tidalenga chitsulo momwe muli mphamvu zambiri (pa nkhondo) ndiponso chithandizo kwa anthu (akakhala pa mtendere ndi kupindula nacho pochita zowathandiza pa moyo wawo). Ndi kuti Allah amuonetsere poyera, amene angachiteteze (chipembedzo Chake) ndi atumiki Ake (kupyolera m’chitsulocho) pomwe Iye sakumuona. Ndithu Allah Ngwamphamvu (pa chilichonse) Ngopambana"
  57,26,"“Ndipo ndithu tidatuma Nuh ndi Ibrahim ndi kukhazikitsa uneneri m’mbumba yawo ndi mabuku (achiongoko). Ena mwa iwo adayenda pa njira yolungama, koma ambiri a iwo adapatuka pa njira yolungamayo"
  57,27,"“Kenako tidatsatiza pambuyo pawo ndi atumiki Athu ndipo tidasatiza ndi Isa (Yesu) mwana wa Mariya, ndipo tidampatsa Injili ndipo tidaika kufatsa ndi chifundo m’mitima ya omwe adamtsatira. Koma kusakwatira, adakuyambitsa okha; sitidawalamule zimenezo koma (adayambitsa zimenezo) chifukwa chofuna chikondi cha Allah; koma sadazisunge moyenera. Choncho amene adakhulupirira pakati pawo tidawapatsa malipiro awo, koma ambiri a iwo ngopandukira malamulo"
  57,28,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Opani Allah, ndipo khulupirirani mthenga Wake, akupatsani zigawo ziwiri za chifundo Chake. Ndipo akupangirani kuunika koongoka nako (poyenda patsiku la chiweruziro.) Ndiponso akukhululukirani ndipo Allah Ngokhululuka mochuluka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  57,29,"“(Allah akupatsani zonsezi) kuti adziwe amene adapatsidwa buku (omwe sadamkhulupirire Mtumiki{s.a.w}) kuti iwo sangathe kudzisankhira okha chilichonse mu mtendere wa Allah. Ndipo ndithu ubwino wonse uli m’manja mwa Allah Yekha. Amapatsa amene wamfuna mwa akapolo Ake. Ndipo Allah ndi Mwini ubwino wochuluka"
  58,1,"“۞ Ndithu Allah wamva mawu a (mkazi) amene akubwezeranabwezerana nawe (mawu) pa za mwamuna wake (amene adamsala); ndipo akusuma kwa Allah. Ndipo Allah akumva kukambirana kwanu; ndithu Allah Ngwakumva, Ngopenya (chilichonse)"
  58,2,“Amene akufanizira mwa inu (Asilamu) akazi awo (ndi amayi awo) iwo siamayi awo; amayi awo ndiamene adawabereka. Ndithu iwo akunena mawu oipa ndi onama. Koma ndithu Allah ali Wofafaniza (machimo) ndi Wokhululuka (kwa amene walapa)
  58,3,"“Ndipo amene akuwafanizira akazi awo (ndi amayi awo) kenako nkubweza zimene adanena, apereke ufulu kwa kapolo asanakhale malo amodzi (ndi mkaziyo). Amenewa ndi malamulo a Allah kwa inu (amene) mukuchenjezedwa nawo. Ndipo Allah akudziwa zimene mukuchita (zoonekera poyera ndi zosaonekera choncho sungani malamulo amene Allah wakhazikitsa pa inu)"
  58,4,"“Ndipo amene sadapeze (kapolo) asale miyezi iwiri yondondozana asadakhalirane pamodzi (ndi mkaziyo), koma amene sadathe kusala adyetse masikini makumi asanu ndi limodzi . Izi (zalamulidwa) kuti mukhulupirire mwa Allah ndi Mthenga Wake. Amenewo ndiwo malire a Allah; (malamulo okhazikitsidwa ndi Allah choncho musawalumphe). Ndipo chilango chopweteka chili pa osakhulupirira"
  58,5,"“Ndithu amene akutsutsana ndi Allah kudzanso Mthenga Wake, ayalutsidwa monga momwe adayalutsidwira amene adalipo patsogolo pawo; ndithu tavumbulutsa Ayah zolongosola, momveka (pa zololedwa ndi zoletsedwa). Ndipo chilango choyalutsa chili pa osakhulupirira"
  58,6,"“(Kumbuka) tsiku limene Allah adzaukitsa akufa onse ndi kuwafotokozera zimene adachita (pa moyo wa dziko lapansi: zoipa ndi zabwino); Allah adazisunga mozilemba koma iwo adaziiwala. Ndipo Allah ndi mboni wa zonse (palibe chingabisike kwa Iye)"
  58,7,"“Kodi sukudziwa (iwe, womvera wanzeru) kuti Allah akudziwa zakumwamba ndi zam’dziko lapansi? Sipakhala manong’onong’o a (anthu) atatu koma Iye Ngwachinayi wawo (ndi kudziwa kwake kosabisika chilichonse cha kumwamba ndi m’dziko), ngakhale a (anthu) asanu koma Iye Ngwachisanu ndi chimodzi wawo (mkudziwa Kwake), ngakhale ali ochepera kuposera pamenepa kapena ochulukira koma Iye ali nawo paliponse pomwe ati akhale (Allah ali nawo pamodzi mukudziwa Kwake kosabisika chilichonse), kenako adzawafotokozera pa tsiku la chiweruziro zimene adachita; ndithu Allah Ngodziwa chilichonse (mokwanira)"
  58,8,"“Kodi siudaone! Kwa amene aletsedwa kunong’onezana zoipa pakati pawo, kenako akubwereza zimene adaletsedwa? Akunong’onezana za machimo, mtopola ndi kunyoza Mtumiki. Akakudzera akukulonjera (ndi malonje achinyengo) amene Allah sadakulonjerepo nawo ndipo akunena m’mitima mwawo: “Kodi nchifukwa chiyani Allah sakutilanga ndi mawu tikunenawa (ngati iyeyu ndi Mtumikidi wa Allah?” Jahannam ikuwakwanira: adzailowa. Ndipo taonani kuipa malo (awo) wobwerera"
  58,9,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Ngati mukunong’onezana, musamanong’onezane za machimo ndi mtopola ndi kunyoza Mtumiki; koma nong’onezanani za kulungama ndi kuopa Allah ndipo muopeni Allah, kwa Iye nkumene mudzasonkhanitsidwe (ndi kuweruzidwa)"
  58,10,"“Ndithu manong’onong’o oipa amachokera kwa satana kuti adandaulitse amene akhulupirira; koma sangawapweteke nawo chilichonse kupatula Allah atafuna ndipo okhulupirira atsamire kwa Allah Yekha, (asalabadire zonong’onezana zawo)"
  58,11,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Kukapemphedwa kwa inu kuti perekani malo pabwalo (pokhala), perekani malowo (kuti anzanu apeze pokhala; mukatero) Allah akuphanulirani (chifundo Chake pano pa dziko ndi kumwamba). Ndipo kukanenedwa kuti imilirani, muimilire (musanyozere, apatseni ena malo); Allah awakwezera (ulemelero) mwa inu amene akhulupirira ndi amene apatsidwa nzeru. Ndipo Allah akudziwa bwino zimene mukuchita"
  58,12,"E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Mukafuna kuyankhula ndi Mtumiki (s.a.w) tsogozani pa zoyankhula zanuzo, sadaka: kutero ndibwino kwa inu ndiponso ndichoyeretsa (mitima yanu). Koma ngati simudapeze (sadakayo) ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka, Ngwachisoni"
  58,13,“Kodi mwaopa kutsogoza sadaka pakunena naye (Mtumiki)? Ngati simudachite zimenezi basi Allah wakukhululukirani; choncho pempherani Swala moyenera ndipo perekani Zakaat ndiponso mverani Allah pamodzi ndi Mtumiki Wake. Ndipo Allah akudziwa zonse zimene mukuchita
  58,14,“Kodi sukuwaona amene apalana ubwenzi ndi anthu amene Allah wawakwiira; iwo sali mwa inu ndiponso sali mwa iwo. Ndipo akulumbira zabodza uku akudziwa (kuti limeneli ndibodza)
  58,15,"“Allah wawakonzera chilango chaukali, ndithudi nzoipa zimene amachita"
  58,16,"“Kulumbira kwawo adakuchita kukhala chodzitetezera (iwo, ana awo ndi chuma chawo); choncho adatsekereza (anthu) ku njira ya Allah; choncho chilango choyalutsa chili pa iwo"
  58,17,"“Chuma chawo, ngakhale ana awo, sizidzawathandiza konse ku chilango cha Allah. Iwowo ndi anthu a ku Moto m’menemo iwo adzakhala nthawi yaitali"
  58,18,"“(Alikumbukire) tsiku limene Allah adzawaukitsa (ku imfa) onse, adzayamba kulumbira kwa Iye (zabodza) monga akulumbira (zabodza) kwa inu. Ndipo akuganiza kuti apezapo kanthu (pakulumbira kwawo). Dziwani, ndithudi, iwo ndi abodza"
  58,19,"“Satana wawapambana ndipo wawaiwalitsa kukumbukira Allah. Iwowa ndiachipani cha satana. Dziwani kuti chipani cha satana nchotayika, (choonongeka)"
  58,20,"“Ndithudi amene akutsutsana ndi Allah ndi Mthenga Wake, iwowo adzakhala m’gulu la onyozeka"
  58,21,"“Allah adalamula (kuti): “Ndithu ndipambana Ine ndi atumiki Anga.” Ndithu Allah ndiwanyonga zokwana, Wopambana (sapambanidwa ndi aliyense)"
  58,22,"“Supeza anthu okhulupirira mwa Allah ndi tsiku lachimaliziro akukonda amene akutsutsana ndi Allah ndi Mthenga Wake, ngakhale atakhala atate awo, ana awo abale awo ndi akumtundu wawo; kwa iwo (Allah) wazika chikhulupiliro (champhamvu) m’mitima mwawo, ndipo wawalimbikitsa ndi mphamvu zochokera kwa Iye. Ndipo adzawalowetsa m’minda yomwe pansi pake pakuyenda mitsinje; adzakhala m’menemo nthawi yaitali. Allah adzakondwera nawo ndipo (iwonso) adzakondwera Naye. Iwowa ndi chipani cha Allah. Dziwani kuti chipani cha Allah ndichopambana"
  59,1,"“Zonse za kumwamba ndi za pansi zimalemekeza Allah (ndi kumuyeretsa ku khalidwe losayenera ndi ulemelero Wake). Ndipo Iye Ngopambana (salephera kanthu), Ngwaluntha (m’kakonzedwe Kake ndi m’zochita Zake)"
  59,2,"“Iye ndi Amene adatulutsa osakhulupirira ena mwa anthu a buku m’nyumba zawo mkusamusidwa koyamba (pa chilumba cha Arabu). Simunkaganizira kuti angatuluke (m’nyumba zawozo). Ndipo iwo amaganiza kuti malinga awo awateteza kwa Allah. Koma Allah adawalanga kupyolera mmene samayembekezera, ndipo adathira mantha oopsa m’mitima mwawo (potumiza Mtumiki Wake kwa iwo), adagumula nyumba zawo ndi manja awo ndi manja a okhulupirira. Choncho lingalirani (zimenezi) E inu eni nzeru"
  59,3,"“Ndipo kukadapanda kuti Allah adawalembera (pachiyambi) kusamuka (m’nyumba zawo), akadawalanga pa dziko pompano; koma chilango cha Moto chili pa iwo tsiku lachimaliziro"
  59,4,"“Zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti iwo adamtsutsa Allah ndi Mthenga Wake, (kutsutsa kopyola muyeso); ndipo amene akutsutsa Allah (sangapulumuke ku chilango Chake). Ndithu Allah Ndiwolanga mwaukali"
  59,5,"“Sim’dadule mtengo uliwonse wa zipatso za kanjedza, (inu Asilamu), kapena kuusiya uli chiimire ndi thunthu lake koma nchifuniro cha Allah ndi kuti awayalutse otuluka m’malamulo Ake"
  59,6,"“Ndipo chuma chimene wapereka Allah kwa Mtumiki Wake chochokera kwa iwo (Bani Nadhiri), chimenecho inu simudathamangitse mahachi kapena ngamira (pakuchipeza), koma Allah amapereka mphamvu kwa atumiki Ake zogonjetsera amene wamfuna. Ndipo Allah ali ndi Mphamvu (pa) chilichonse"
  59,7,"“Chuma chimene Allah wachipereka kwa mtumiki Wake kuchokera kwa anthu am’midzi (yapafupi ndi mzinda wa Madina) chimenecho ncha Allah, ndi Mtumiki, ndi abale a mtumiki ndi amasiye, ndi masikini, ndiponso apaulendo; kuti chisakhale chongozungulira pakati pa olemera okha mwa inu. Ndipo chimene wakupatsani Mtumiki, chilandireni; ndipo chimene Wakuletsani chisiyeni. Muopeni Allah (potsatira malamulo Ake). Ndithu Allah Ngwaukali polanga"
  59,8,“(Chiperekedwe) kwa osauka osamuka omwe adatulutsidwa m’nyumba zawo ndi (kusiya) chuma chawo chifukwa chofuna zabwino za Allah ndi chikondi (Chake) ndi kupulumutsa (chipembedzo cha) Allah ndi Mthenga Wake (pogwiritsira ntchito matupi awo ndi chuma chawo); iwowa ndi (Asilamu) owona
  59,9,"“Koma amene adakhala kale mu mzinda uwu (wa Madina) ndi kukhulupirira akukonda amene adasamukira kwa iwo. Ndipo sakupeza vuto m’mitima mwawo pa zimene anzawo apatsidwa, ndipo akutsogoza zofuna za anzawo pa zawo, ngakhale iwo akuzifunitsitsa. Ndipo amene atetezedwa (ndi Allah) ku umbombo wa mitima yawo, amenewo ndiwo opambana"
  59,10,"“Ndipo (okhulupirira) amene adadza pambuyo (pa Amuhajirina ndi Answari) akunena kuti: “Mbuye wathu tikhululukireni ndi anzathu amene adatitsogolera pa chikhulupiliro, ndipo musaike m’mitima mwathu njiru ndi chidani kwa amene adakhulupirira. E Mbuye wathu! Inu ndinu Wodekha, Wachisoni chosatha.”"
  59,11,"“Kodi wawaona amene achita uchiphamaso? Amene akunena kwa anzawo amene sadakhulupirire pakati pa anthu a mabuku: “Ndithu ngati (mukakamizidwa) kutuluka mu mzinda wa Madina, ndithudi tidzatuluka nanu pamodzi ndipo sitingamvere aliyense za inu mpaka muyaya; ngati mutamenyedwa nkhondo (ndi Asilamu) tidzakuthandizani. Koma Allah akuikira umboni kuti iwo ndionama (pa zimene alonjeza)"
  59,12,"“Ngati atatulutsidwa, sangatuluke nawo limodzi; ngati atamenyedwa, sangawathandize ndipo ngati atawathandiza atembenuza misana (kuthawa) kenako sapulumutsidwa"
  59,13,“Ndithu inu (Asilamu) mukuopedwa kwambiri m’mitima mwawo kuposa mmene akumuopera Allah. Zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti iwo ndi anthu osazindikira (chilichonse)
  59,14,"“(Ayuda) sangamenyane ndi inu ali pa gulu kupatula m’midzi yotetezedwa ndi malinga, kapena kuseri kwa zipupa. Nkhondo yawo pakati pawo njaukali; ungawaganizire kuti ali pamodzi pomwe mitima yawo njosiyana; zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti iwo ndianthu opanda nzeru"
  59,15,"“Fanizo (la Ayuda a Banu Nadhiri) lili ngati (amene adatsutsa mwa Ayuda a Qainuka) amene awatsogolera (kupeza mavuto) posachedwapa, adalawa chilango (pa dziko lapansi) cha zochita zawo (ndi kuswa mapangano). Ndipo iwo adzalandira chilango (china) chowawa kwambiri, (pa tsiku la chiweruziro)"
  59,16,"“Fanizo la achinyengo (achiphamaso pakuwanyenga Banu Nadhiri kuti amupandukire Mneneri wa Allah) lili ngati satana (ponyenga munthu kusiya chikhulupiliro). Adati kwa Iye: “Mkane (Allah).” Ndipo pamene adamkana, (satana) adati: “Ine sindili ndi iwe; ndithu ine ndikuopa Allah, Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”"
  59,17,"“Choncho mapeto a onse awiriwo, kudali kukalowa ku Moto ndi kukhala m’menemo nthawi yaitali. Iyi ndiyo mphoto ya anthu onyenga (ochenjelera anzawo)"
  59,18,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Muopeni Allah (potsatira malamulo Ake ndi kusiya zimene waletsa) ndipo alingalire munthu aliyense zamawa zimene watsogoza. Ndipo muopeni Allah, ndithu Allah Ngodziwa zimene mukuchita (ndipo adzakulipirani pa zimenezo)"
  59,19,“Ndipo musakhale monga amene aiwala (zoyenera kuchitira) Allah; choncho (naye Allah) wawaiwalitsa mitima yawo (powachotsera kuzindikira zimene zingawathandize). Amenewa ndiwo olakwa kwakukulu (otuluka ku chilamulo cha Allah)
  59,20,"“Sangafanane anthu a ku Moto, (olangidwa), ndi anthu a ku Jannah, (opeza mtendere). Anthu aku Jannah ndiwo opambana"
  59,21,"“Chikhala kuti tidaivumbulutsa Qur’an iyi pamwamba pa phiri, ukadaliona phirilo lili lodzichepetsa ndi kung’ambika chifukwa choopa Allah. Ndipo awa ndi mafanizo omwe tikuwapereka kwa anthu kuti aganizire"
  59,22,"“Iye ndi Allah, Amene palibenso wina wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye, Wodziwa zamseri ndi zooneka. Iye Ngwachifundo chambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  59,23,"“Iye ndi Allah, Amene palibenso wina wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye, Mfumu, Woyera, Mwini mtendere, Wotsimikizira (aneneri Ake mphamvu yochitira zozizwitsa,) Msungi wa chilichonse (yemwe akuona zochita za akapolo Ake;) Wamphamvu zopambana, Mgonjetsi Wotukuka muulemelero; Wamkulukulu. Wayeretsedwa Allah kuzimene akumuphatikiza nazo"
  59,24,"“Iye ndi Allah; Mlengi wa (zinthu, palibe chomfanizira); Muumbi wa chilichonse, Mkonzi wa maonekedwe a zinthu, Ake ndi maina abwino, zonse za kumwamba ndi pansi zikumulemekeza Iye ndi kumyeretsa ku makhalidwe osayenerana ndi ulemelero Wake. Iye Ngopambana ndiponso Wanzeru zakuya"
  60,1,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Musawachite adani Anga ndi adani anu kukhala athandizi anu ndi kumawauza (nkhani zanu) mwa chikondi, pomwe iwo sanakhulupirire choonadi chimene chakudzerani. Adamtulutsa Mtumiki ndi inu nomwe (m’nyumba zanu) chifukwa chakuti mumakhulupirira Allah, Mbuye wanu, (palibe cholakwa chilichonse chimene mudawachitira,) ngati mwatuluka kukachita Jihâd pa njira Yanga ndi kufunafuna chikondi Changa (musapalane nawo ubwenzi). Mukuwatumizira chinsinsi (chanu cha nkhondo) chifukwa cha chikondi (chanu ndi iwo); (musachitenso zimenezi) pomwe Ine ndikudziwa zimene inu mukubisa ndi zimenene mukuzisonyeza (poyera); amene akuchita zimenezi mwa inu, ndiye kuti wataya njira yoongoka"
  60,2,“Akakumana nanu (pankhondo) akukhala adani anu ndipo akukutambasulirani manja ndi malirime awo moipa (pokumenyani ndi kukutukwanani); ndipo akulakalaka mukadakhala osakhulupirira (kuti mufanane nawo)
  60,3,"“Abale anu ngakhale ana anu sadzakuthandizani tsiku la Qiyâma (Allah) adzaweruza (pakati panu), ndipo Allah akuona zimene mukuchita"
  60,4,"“Ndithu inu muli ndi chitsanzo chabwino cha (mtumiki) Ibrahim ndi amene adali naye pamene adawauza anzawo (osakhulupirira kuti): “Ndithu ife tapatukana nanu pamodzi ndi milungu yanu imene mukuipembedza kusiya Allah; takukanani, ndipo chidani ndi kusakondana zaonekera poyera pakati pa inu ndi ife mpaka muyaya, kufikira, mutakhulupirira mwa Allah mmodzi (inunso chitani chimodzimodzi, muwakane abale anu amene ali akafiri), kupatula mawu a Ibrahim pamene adamuuza tate wake (kuti): “Ndithu ndikupempherani chikhululuko. Palibe chimene ndingakutetezereni nacho kwa Allah (ngati mutamuphatikiza Allah ndi zina.”) E Mbuye wathu! Kwa Inu tatsamira. Ndipo kwa Inu tatembenukira ndiponso kobwerera nkwa Inu"
  60,5,"“E Mbuye wathu! Musatichite kukhala mayeso kwa amene sadakhulupirire, tikhululukireni Mbuye wathu! Ndithu Inu, Ndinu Amphamvu zopambana ndiponso Anzeru zakuya"
  60,6,“Ndithu muli nacho inu kwa iwo (Ibrahim ndi omtsatira) chitsanzo chabwino kwa amene akuyembekezera kukumana ndi Allah ndi tsiku lachimaliziro. Ndipo amene anyozere ndithu Allah Ngolemera (ndiponso) Ngotamandika
  60,7,"“Mwina Allah angaike chikondi pakati panu ndi ena mwa amene mumawada (poiongolera mitima yawo kukhulupirira mwa Allah), ndipo Allah Ngokhoza chilichonse ndiponso Allah Ngokhululuka; Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  60,8,“Allah sakukuletsani kuwachitira zabwino ndi chilungamo amene sadakumenyeni ndi kukutulutsani m’nyumba zanu chifukwa cha chipembedzo. Ndithu Allah amakonda achilungamo
  60,9,"“Allah akukuletsani kugwirizana nawo amene adakumenyani chifukwa cha chipembedzo ndi kukutulutsani m’nyumba zanu, ndi amene adathandiza kukutulutsani. Amene ati agwirizane nawo iwowo ndiwo achinyengo"
  60,10,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Akakudzerani okhulupirira aakazi osamuka, ayeseni mayeso (kuti mudziwe chikhulupiliro chawo); Allah ali wodziwa kwambiri za chikhulupiliro chawo; ngati mutawadziwa kuti ndiokhulupirira musawabwezere kwa osakhulupirira. Akaziwo saloledwa kukwatiwa ndi osakhulupirira, iwonso saloledwa kuwakwatira. Abwezereni chiwongo chimene adapereka amuna osakhulupirirawo. Ndipo palibe tchimo kwa inu kuwakwatira, (ngakhale adasiya amuna awo achikafiri (ku Makka) ngati muwapatsa chiwongo chawo. Musakakamire maukwati ndi akazi achikafiri (osakhulupirira amene adatsalira ku Makka). Itanitsani zimene mudapereka kwa akazi anu (achikafiriwo), naonso Akafiri aitanitse zimene adapereka (kwa akazi awo akalowa m’Chisilamu). Limeneli ndi lamulo la Allah limene akulamula pakati panu. Allah ndiwodziwa kwambiri ndiponso Ngwanzeru (poika malamulo)"
  60,11,"“Ndipo ngati mmodzi mwa akazi anu atakuthawani kupita kwa Akafiri, ndipo (mwadzidzidzi) mwakachita nkhondo (ndi kupeza chuma chosiya adani anu), apatseni amene awathawa akazi awo chofanana ndi chimene adapereka (pokwatira). Ndipo muopeni Allah amene inu mukumkhulupirira"
  60,12,"“E iwe Mtumiki! Akakudzera akazi okhulupirira kudzakulonjeza kuti samphatikiza Allah ndi chilichonse ndi kuti saziba, sazichita chiwerewere, sazipha ana awo ndi kuti sazinena bodza lamkunkhuniza, lomwe akulipeka pakati pa manja awo ndi miyendo yawo (pompachika mwana kwa wina amene sali tate wake), ndi kutinso sadzakunyoza pa chinthu chabwino (chimene ukuwaitanira), landira lonjezo lawolo, ndipo apemphere chikhululuko kwa Allah. Ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni"
  60,13,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Musagwirizane ndi anthu amene Allah wawakwiyira. Ndithu iwo ataya mtima wopeza mphoto tsiku lachimaliziro (chifukwa cha machimo awo ochuluka) monga momwe atayira mtima akafiri za kuuka kwa amene ali m’manda
  61,1,“Zonse zakumwamba ndi zapansi zimalemekeza Allah (ndi kumuyeretsa kumakhalidwe osayenera ndi ulemelero Wake). Ndipo Iye Yekha Ngopambana pa chilichonse; Wanzeru zakuya
  61,2,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Bwanji mukunena zimene simuchita
  61,3,“Nzomuipira zedi Allah kunena zinthu zimene simuchita
  61,4,"“Ndithu Allah amakonda amene akumenya nkhondo pa njira Yake (yofalitsa chipembedzo Chake), ali pa mzere (umodzi) uku ali monga chomanga, chomangika mwamphamvu"
  61,5,"“Ndipo kumbuka (iwe Mneneri{s.a.w}) pamene Mûsa adanena kwa anthu ake kuti: “Ndichifukwa ninji mukundivutitsa ine pomwe mukudziwa kuti ine ndine Mtumiki wa Allah kwa inu?” Ndipo pamene adapitiriza kupandukira choonadi, Allah adaipinda mitima yawo (kuti isalandire chiongoko); ndipo Allah saongola anthu otuluka m’chilamulo Chake"
  61,6,"“Ndiponso (kumbuka) pamene adanena (Mtumiki) Isa (Yesu) mwana wa Mariya, kuti: “E inu ana a Israelil! Ndithu ine ndine Mtumiki wa Allah kwa inu, amene ndikuchitira umboni zimene zidadza patsogolo panga za buku la Chipangano chakale (Torah) ndipo ndikuuzani nkhani yabwino ya mthenga amene adzadze pambuyo panga, dzina lake Ahamad (Muhammad{s.a.w}).” Koma pamene adawadzera (Mtumiki wolonjedzedwayo) ndi zisonyezo zowonekera poyera (kuti iye ndi Mtumiki wa Allah). Adati: “Awa ndi matsenga owonekera.”"
  61,7,"“Kodi ndani oipitsitsa kuposa yemwe wapekera Allah bodza, pomwe iye akuitanidwira ku Chisilamu (chipembedzo choona ndi chabwino)? Ndipo Allah saongola anthu achinyengo"
  61,8,“Akufuna kuti azimitse dangalira la Allah ndi pakamwa pawo ndipo Allah Ngokwaniritsa dangalira Lake ngakhale ziwaipire osakhulupirira
  61,9,"“Iye ndi amene adatuma Mtumiki Wake (Muhammad{s.a.w}) ndi chiongoko ndi chipembedzo choona, kuti achiike pamwamba pa zipembedzo zonse, ngakhale kuti ophatikiza Allah ndi mafano zikuwaipira"
  61,10,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Kodi ndikudziwitseni malonda amene angakupulumutseni ku chilango chowawa
  61,11,"“Muzimkhulupirira Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake; ndipo muzichita Jihâd pa njira ya Allah ndi chuma chanu, ndi matupi anu. Zimenezo nzabwino kwa inu ngati muli odziwa"
  61,12,"“Akukhululukirani machimo anu ndipo akulowetsani m’minda momwe mitsinje ikuyenda pansi pake, ndiponso (adzakupatsani) mokhala mwabwino ku minda yamuyaya. Kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu"
  61,13,“Ndizina zomwe mukuzifuna. Thandizo (lonse) lichokera kwa Allah ndi kugonjetsa kumene kuli pafupi; ndipo auze nkhani yabwino okhulupirira
  61,14,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Khalani othangata (kufalitsa chipembedzo cha) Allah (pamene Mtumiki akukuitanani kuti mumthangate) monga momwe adanenera Isa (Yesu) mwana wa Mariya powauza otsatira ake: “Ndani adzandithangata pa ntchito ya Allah (yofalitsa chipembedzo Chake)? Otsatira ake adanena: “Ife ndife othangata (kufalitsa chipembedzo cha) Allah.” Choncho gulu lina la ana a Israyeli lidakhululupirira, ndipo gulu lina silidakhululupirire, tero tidawapatsa mphamvu amene adakhulupirira pa adani awo, ndipo adali opambana"
  62,1,"“Zonse zakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi zikulemekeza Allah; Mfumu, Woyera, Wamphamvu zopambana ndi nzeru zakuya (ndi kumyeretsa ku makhalidwe osayenerana ndi ulemelero Wake)"
  62,2,"“Iye ndiAmene adatumiza kwa Ummiyyina (osadziwa kulemba ndi kuwerenga), Mtumiki wochokera mwa iwo kuti awawerengere ndime Zake ndi kuti awayeretse (ku uchimo ndi kumakhalidwe oipa) ndi kuwaphunzitsa Qur’an ndi mawu anzeru (a mtumiki) ndithu kale adali osokera kowonekera (Mtumiki {s.a.w} asadadze kwa iwo"
  62,3,"“Ndipo (adamtumizanso) kwa ena mwa iwo, omwe sadakumane nawo, ndipo Iye (Allah) Ngopambana (pa chinthu chilichonse ndi Wamphamvu zoposa ndiponso) Ngwanzeru zakuya"
  62,4,“Umenewo ndiwo ubwino wa Allah akuupereka kwa amene wamfuna (mwa akapolo Ake); ndipo Allah yekha ndi Mwini ubwino waukulu
  62,5,"“Fanizo la (Ayuda) amene adawasenzetsa Taurat (pokakamizidwa kuti atsatire zophunzitsa za bukulo, koma osatsatira), ali ngati bulu amene akusenza mabuku akuluakulu anzeru, (koma osathandizika nawo). Taonani kuipa fanizo la anthu amene atsutsa zisonyezo za Allah. Ndipo Allah saongola anthu achinyengo"
  62,6,"“Nena: “E inu Ayuda! Ngati mwadziganizira kuti ndithu ndinu okondedwa a Allah kuposa (mitundu ina ya) anthu, ilakelakeni imfa (kuti mukalowe ku mtendere wa Allah) ngati mukunena zoona"
  62,7,“Ndipo sangailakelake mpang’ono pomwe chifukwa cha (zoipa) zimene manja awo atsogoza! Ndipo Allah akudziwa bwino za (anthu) osalungama
  62,8,"“Nena (kuti): “Ndithu imfa imene mukuithawa (palibe chipeneko) ikumana nanu; kenako muzabwezedwa kwa wodziwa zobisika ndi zooneka; ndipo adzakuuzani zimene mudali kuchita"
  62,9,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Kukaitanidwa ku Swala (pemphero la Ijuma) tsiku la Ijuma, pitani mwachangu kukamtamanda Allah. Ndipo siyani malonda; zimenezo (mwalamulidwazo) nzabwino kwa inu ngati mukudziwa"
  62,10,"“Choncho Swala (ya Ijumayo) ikatha, balalikanani pa dziko, ndipo funani ubwino wa Allah; ndipo mtamandeni Allah kwambiri kuti mupambane (pa dziko lapansi ndi pa tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  62,11,"“Ndipo akaona malonda kapena masewero, akubalalika kunka ku zimenezo ndi kukusiya uli chiimire (ukuchita khutuba ndi anthu ochepa). Nena (kwa iwo): “Zimene zili kwa Allah nzabwino kwa inu kuposa masewero ndi malonda. Ndipo Allah Ngwabwino kwambiri kuposa opatsa onse.”"
  63,1,"“Akakudzera achiphamaso akunena kuti: “Tikuikira umboni kuti ndithu iwe ndiwe Mtumiki wa Allah, ndipo Allah akudziwa kuti iwe ndiwe mtumiki Wake. Ndipo Allah akuikira umboni kuti achiphamaso ngabodza (pa zomwe akunena)"
  63,2,“Kulumbira kwawo (kwa bodza) akuchita kukhala chotetezera (chuma chawo ndi matupi awo). Tero atsekereza (anthu kuyenda) panjira ya Allah. Ndithu nzoipa zedi zimene amachita
  63,3,"“Zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti iwo adakhulupirira (modzionetsera), kenako adakana (mobisa). Choncho mitima yawo idatsekedwa kotero kuti iwo sangathe kuzindikira (chimene chingawapulumutse ku chilango cha Allah)"
  63,4,"“Ndipo ukawaona, akukondweretsa matupi awo; ndipo akayankhula umvetsera zoyankhula zawo (chifukwa chakuthwa kwa malirime awo, pomwe mkati mwawo ndiming’oma yopanda kanthu); iwo ali ngati matsinde a mitengo yomwe yayadzamiritsidwa (ku chipupa); (mwa iwo mulibe moyo). Mkuwe uliwonse (umene akuumva) akuganiza kuti ukulinga iwo, (chifukwa cha kuzindikira chinyengo chawo); iwowa ndiadani; chenjerani nawo. Allah awatembelere! Mwanjira yanji akuchotsedwa (ku choonadi)"
  63,5,"“Kukanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Bwerani, akupemphereni chikhululuko mthenga wa Allah, akutembenuza mitu yawo (monyoza ndi modzitukumula), ndipo uwaona akunyoza uku akudzikweza (osatsatira langizo).”"
  63,6,"“Kwa iwowa nchimodzimodzi kuwapemphera kwako chikhululuko, kapena kusawapemphera. Allah sangawakhululukire (chifukwa cha kuzama kwawo m’kusakhulupirira). Ndithu Allah saongola anthu otuluka m’chilamulo (Chake)"
  63,7,"“Amenewa ndiwo omwe akunena kwa Answari; (Asilamu aku Madina, kuti): “Musawapatse chuma (chanu) amene ali ndi Mtumiki wa Allah kuti abalalikane.” Pomwe nkhokwe zonse (zachuma) za kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi zili m’manja mwa Allah (ndipo amachipereka kwa amene wamfuna); koma achiphamaso sakuzindikira (zimenezo)"
  63,8,"“Akunena kuti: “Ngati tibwerera ku Madina wolemekezeka adzatulutsa wonyozeka m’menemo. “Pomwe ulemelero ngwa Allah ndi Mthenga Wake ndi okhulupirira; koma achinyengo sakudziwa (zimenezo).”"
  63,9,“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Chuma chanu ngakhalenso ana anu zisakutangwanitseni ndi kusiya kukumbukira Allah (ndi kukwaniritsa zimene wakulamulani). Ndipo amene achite zimenezo iwo ndi otaika
  63,10,"“Perekani (mwachangu pa njira ya Allah) zina mwa zomwe takupatsani, isanamfikire mmodzi wa inu imfa (mwadzidzidzi) ndi kuyamba kunena (modandaula): “Mbuye wanga! Bwanji osandichedwetsa nthawi pang’ono kuti ndipereke sadaka (ndi kuti ndikonze zina zimene sindinazikwaniritse) ndi kutinso ndikhale mwa anthu anu abwino.”"
  63,11,"“Ndipo Allah sangauchedwetse mzimu (ngakhale ndi mphindi imodzi) ukaidzera nthawi yake ya imfa; ndipo Allah Ngodziwa zonse zimene mukuchita, (ndipo adzakulipirani pa zimenezo)"
  64,1,“Zonse zakumwamba ndi zam’dziko lapansi zikulemekeza Allah (ndi kumyeretsa ku zinthu zosayenerana ndi ulemelero Wake; ufumu Ngwake ndipo kutamandidwa kwabwino Nkwake. Ndipo Iye ali ndi mphamvu pa chilichonse)
  64,2,“Iye ndiamene adakulengani (nonsenu popanda kuchokera ku chilichonse) choncho mwa inu alipo wosakhulupirira ndiponso mwa inu alipo wokhulupirira. Ndipo Allah Ngopenya zonse zimene mukuchita (ndipo adzakulipirani nazo)
  64,3,“Adalenga thambo ndi nthaka mwachoonadi ndipo adakujambulani majambulidwe abwino; ndipo kobwerera nkwa Iye (pa tsiku lachiweruziro)
  64,4,"“(Allah) akudziwa za kumwamba ndi za m’dziko lapansi, ndiponso akudziwa zimene mukuzibisa ndi zimene mukuzilengeza (zochita ndi zoyankhula); Allah Ngodziwa za m’zifuwa"
  64,5,“Kodi siidakufikeni nkhani ya omwe sadakhulupirire kale? Adalawa (zowawa) za zoipa za zinthu zawo (pa dziko lapansi). Ndipo chilango chowawa chidzakhala pa iwo (tsiku lachimaliziro)
  64,6,"“Zimenezo nchifukwa chakuti atumiki awo amawadzera ndi zozizwitsa koma iwo amanena (mwachipongwe): “Ha! Anthu anzathu (onga ife) angationgole?” Choncho sadakhulupirire (utumiki wawo) ndipo adanyoza (choonadi) potero Allah adawasiya (ndi kupanda chikhulupiliro kwawo) ndipo Allah Ngokwanira ndiponso Ngoyamikidwa"
  64,7,"“Amene sadakhulupirire akumazinamiza kuti sadzaukitsidwa ku imfa. Nena (kwa iwo iwe Mtumiki{s.a.w}): “Sizili choncho pali Mbuye wanga, ndithu mudzaukitsidwa ku imfa, ndipo mudzauzidwa zimene mumachita (pa dziko lapansi). Zimenezo kwa Allah nzosavuta (kuzichita).”"
  64,8,"“Khulupirirani Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake, ndi dangalira limene talivumbulutsa (Qur’an). Ndipo Allah Ngodziwa kwambiri zimene mukuchita"
  64,9,"“(Kumbukirani) tsiku limene adzakusonkhanitsani chifukwa cha tsiku lakusonkhana (zolengedwa zonse), limenelo ndi tsiku lolephera; ndipo amene akhulupirira mwa Allah ndi kuchita zabwino, amfafanizira zoipa zake, ndipo akamulowetsa m’minda momwe pansi pake pakuyenda mitsinje; adzakhala m’menemo muyaya; kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu"
  64,10,"“Koma amene sadakhulupirire natsutsa zozizwitsa Zathu (zimene zidaperekedwa kwa Aneneri Athu;) iwowo ndi anthu a ku Moto; adzakhala mmenemo nthawi yaitali, amenewo ndiwo mabwelero oipa"
  64,11,"“Palibe vuto lililonse lingapezeke pokhapokha Allah atafuna; ndipo amene akhulupirira Allah, (Allah) aongola mtima wake (kuti ukhale wokhutira ndi chiweruzo cha Allah). Ndipo Allah Ngodziwa chinthu chilichonse"
  64,12,"“Choncho mverani Allah ndipo mverani Mtumiki, ngati munyozera (ndi zanu), ndithu udindo wa Mtumiki Wathu ndikufikitsa uthenga omveka"
  64,13,"“Allah, palibe wina wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye. Ndipo kwa Allah Yekha, okhulupirira atsamire"
  64,14,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Ndithu ena mwa akazi anu ndi ana anu ndiadani anu (chifukwa chakuti amakuchotsani kumbali yomvera Allah pofuna kuti mukwaniritse zofuna zawo). Chenjerani nawo. Ngati muwakhululukira ndi kunyalanyaza ndi kubisa zolakwa zawo ndibwino kwambiri, ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  64,15,“Ndithu chuma chanu ndi ana anu ndimayesero (kwa inu); koma kwa Allah kuli malipiro akulu (kwa yemwe wasankha kumvera Allah)
  64,16,"“Choncho muopeni Allah mmene mungathere, mverani (zophunzitsa Zake) ndipo tsatirani (malamulo Ake) komanso perekani zimene wakupatsani zikhala zabwino kwa inu. Dzichitireni nokha zabwino. Ndipo amene watchinjirizidwa ku umbombo wa mtima wake, iwowo ndiwo opambana"
  64,17,"“Ngati mungamkongoze Allah ngongole yabwino aiwonjezera kwa inu (malipiro ake) ndipo akukhululukirani (zolakwa zanu.) Ndipo Allah Ngolandira kuthokoza, Ngoleza"
  64,18,"“Ngodziwa zobisika ndi zoonekera, Ngwamphamvu zopambana, Ngwanzeru zakuya"
  65,1,"“E iwe Mneneri (s.a.w) ngati mufuna kusudzula akazi ukwati, asudzuleni mnyengo yowerengera Edda yawo (kuwerengera Edda kumayambika mkazi akakhala ndi Twahara akachira matenda akumwezi), ndipo werengerani nyengo ya Edda. Ndipo muopeni Allah Mbuye wanu. Ndipo musawatulutse m’nyumba zawo ndiponso asatuluke kupatula akachita tchimo lalikulu loonekera (loyenera chilango, apo atha kutulutsidwa). Ndipo amenewa ndiwo malire a Allah (amene wawakhazikitsa kwa anthu Ake). Ndipo amene apyola malire a Allah wadzichitira yekha zoipa. Sukudziwa (cholinga cha malamulo amenewa) mwina Allah adzadzetsa chinthu pambuyo pake (chosonyeza kuyanjana)"
  65,2,"“Choncho pamene iwo (osiyidwawo) nyengo yawo (Edda) itayandikira kutha, abwelereni mwa ubwino kapena asiyeni mwaubwino (polekelera nyengoyo kuti ithe); ndipo (powabwerera) funani mboni ziwiri zolungama zochokera mwa inu (zimene zichitire umboni kuti inu mukubwererana) ndipo perekani umboni chifukwa choopa Allah. Zimenezo ndizo akulangizidwa nazo amene akhulupirira mwa Allah ndi tsiku lachimaliziro. Ndipo amene akumuopa Allah (potsatira malamulo Ake), amkonzera njira yotulukira (m’mavuto)"
  65,3,"“Ndipo ampatsa rizq kuchokera momwe samayembekezeramo. Ndipo amene akutsamira kwa Allah (pa zinthu zake zonse), ndiye kuti Allah ali wokwana kwa iye (kumkonzera chilichonse), ndithu Allah Ngokwaniritsa cholinga Chake ndi chofuna Chake. Ndithu chinthu chilichonse Allah wachipatsa mlingo wake woyenera (ndipo sichingaupyole)"
  65,4,"“Ndipo Edda ya amene asiya kudwala kumwezi mwa akazi anu chifukwa cha kukula, ngati mukukaika (nthawi ya Edda yawo), Edda yawo ndi miyezi itatu. Ndi omwe sadathe nsinkhu Edda yawo ndi momwemonso. Tsono akazi apakati nthawi yothera Edda yawo ndipomwe abereka. Ndipo amene aopa Allah amfewetsera zinthu zake (kuti zikhale zosavuta)"
  65,5,"“Limenelo ndilamulo la Allah (lomwe) walikhazikitsa kwa inu. Ndipo amene aopa Allah (posunga malamulo ake), amam’fafanizira zoipa zake, ndiponso amamkulitsira malipiro ake"
  65,6,"“Akhazikeni (osiyidwawo) m’mene mukukhala inumo monga momwe kulili kupeza kwanu (ndi mphamvu zanu ngakhale kuti mwawasiya ukwati). Musawavute ndi cholinga chowapana (kuti athawe okha). Ngati ali ndi pakati, apatseni zonse zofunika pa moyo mpaka adzabereke. Ngati akukuyamwitsirani ana anu apatseni malipiro awo mokwanira; gwirizanani pakati panu mwa ubwino ndi mofatsa. Ngati wina apereka mavuto kwa mnzake (ndiye kuti mwanayo) adzamuyamwitsira (mkazi) wina"
  65,7,"“Wopeza bwino apereke malinga ndi kupeza bwino kwake; ndipo amene wachepekedwa rizq lake, apereke (kangachepe) pa zomwe Allah wampatsa. Allah sakakamiza aliyense kupatula zomwe wampatsa. Allah apereka kupeza bwino pambuyo pa masautso"
  65,8,"“Ndipo ndimidzi ingati yomwe idanyoza lamulo la Mbuye wawo ndi Atumiki Ake, ndipo tidawawerenga ndi chiwerengero chokhwima (posanthula zochita zawo zonse). Ndiponso tidawalanga ndi chilango chaukali"
  65,9,“Choncho adalawa kuipa kwa zinthu zawo ndipo mapeto azinthu zawo adali kutayika (kuonongeka kwakukulu)
  65,10,"“Allah wawakonzera iwo chilango chokhwima, choncho muopeni Allah, E inu eni nzeru, amene mwakhulupirira, ndithu Allah wavumbulutsa chikumbutso (cholemekezeka kwa inu)"
  65,11,"“Mtumiki (amene) akukuwerengerani ndime za Allah zolongosola (choonadi ndi chonama) kuti awatulutse mu mdima ndi kuwaika ku dangalira amene wakhulupirira ndi kumachita zabwino. Ndipo amene akhulupirira Allah ndi kumachita zabwino, adzamlowetsa m’minda momwe mitsinje ikuyenda pansi pake; akakhala m’menemo muyaya. Ndithu Allah wamkonzera rizq (dalitso) labwino (Jannah)"
  65,12,"“Allah ndiYemwe adalenga thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri, nthakanso chimodzimodzi. Malamulo Ake akutsika pakati pa izo kuti mudziwe kuti ndithu Allah pachilichonse ndi Wokhoza ndikutinso Allah wachizinga chilichonse m’kuchidziwa"
  66,1,"“E iwe Mneneri (s.a.w)! Nchifukwa ninji ukudziletsa chimene Allah wakuloleza kuchita? Ukufuna kukondweretsa akazi ako (nchifukwa Chake wachita izi?) Koma Allah Ngokhululuka kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  66,2,"“Ndithu Allah wakhazikitsa kamasulidwe kakulumbira kwanu, ndipo Allah ndiye Mtetezi wanu, Iye Ngodziwa kwambiri ndiponso Ngwanzeru zakuya (pa malamulo amene wawakhazikitsa kwa inu)"
  66,3,"Ndipo kumbuka pamene Mneneri (s.a.w) adauza wina mwa akazi ake nkhani mwachinsinsi, choncho (mkaziyo) pamene adaiulula, Allah adamdziwitsa (Mtumiki) za kuululidwa kwa nkhaniyo, (ndipo Mtumiki) adaifotokoza mbali ina ya nkhaniyo, koma mbali ina adaisiya. Pamene adamfotokozera (mkazi wake) zankhaniyo adati: “Ndani wakuuza zimenezi?” (Mtumiki {s.a.w}) adati: “Wandiuza Wodziwa kwambiri ndiponso Wodziwa zazing’ono ndi zazikulu (Amene sichibisika kwa Iye chobisika chilichonse)"
  66,4,"“Ngati awirinu mulapa kwa Allah pazimene mwachita (chitani changu kulapa) chifukwa chakuti mitima yanu yapotoka pang’ono (chifukwa cha nsanje pa zimene Mneneri akufuna zosunga chinsinsi Chake); koma ngati awirinu muthandizana pazimene zingamvutitse, ndithu Allah ndiye Mtetezi wake ndi Jibril (Gabriele) ndiponso okhulupirira abwino; naonso angelo, kuonjezera apa ndiathandizi (ake)"
  66,5,"“Ngati (Mtumiki) akakusudzulani, ndithu Mbuye wake, ampatsa akazi ena mmalo mwa inu, abwino kuposa inu: ogonjera (Allah), okhulupirira (ndi mitima yawo), omvera, olapa, odzichepetsa (pamaso pa Allah) ochita mapemphero (kwambiri), oyenda (pa chikhulupiliro cha Allah kapena ochulukitsa kusala) amene adakwatiwapo kale ndi osakwatiwapo.”"
  66,6,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Dzitchinjirizeni inu ndi mawanja anu ku Moto umene nkhuni zake ndi anthu ndi miyala; oyang’anira ake ndi angelo ouma mtima, amphamvu, sanyoza Allah pa zimene Wawalamula, ndipo amachita (zokhazo) zimene alamulidwa"
  66,7,"“(Adzawauza osakhulupirira pa tsiku la chiweruziro) E inu amene simdakhulupirire! Musadandaule lero, ndithu mukulipidwa pa zimene mumachita (padziko lapansi)"
  66,8,"“E inu amene mwakhulupirira! Lapani kwa Allah; kulapa koona; ndithu Mbuye wanu akufafanizirani zoipa zanu ndi kukakulowetsani m’minda momwe mitsinje ikuyenda pansi pake, tsiku limene Allah sadzayalutsa mneneli ndi amene adakhulupirira pamodzi naye. Dangalira lawo lidzayenda chapatsogolo pawo ndi mbali yakumanja kwawo, uku akunena: “Mbuye wathu! Tikwanitsireni dangalira lathu (mpaka likatifikitse ku Munda wamtendere), ndiponso tikhululukireni ndithu Inu ndi Wokhoza chilichonse.”"
  66,9,"“E iwe Mneneri! Limbana ndi akafiri (osakhulupirira) ndi Amunafikina (Achiphamaso), aumire mtima. Ndipo malo awo ndi ku Jahannam, taonani kuipa kobwerera (kwawo)"
  66,10,"“Allah wapereka fanizo la osakhulupirira monga mkazi wa Nuh ndi mkazi wa Luti. Awiriwa adali pansi pa akapolo Athu awiri abwino, koma adali osakhulupirika kwa amuna awo, (ndipo amuna awo) sadawateteze kalikonse ku chilango cha Allah, ndipo kudanenedwa kwa iwo “Lowani ku Moto pamodzi (ndi ena) olowa.”"
  66,11,"“Ndiponso Allah wapereka fanizo la amene akhulupirira monga mkazi wa Firiauna (Farawo) pamene adanena: “Mbuye wanga! Ndimangireni kwa inu Nyumba mu Jannah, ndipo ndipulumutseni kwa Firiauna ndi zochita zake, ndiponso ndipulumutseni kwa anthu oipa (ndi amtopola.)”"
  66,12,“Ndi (fanizo lina la wokhulupirira monga) Mariya mwana wa Imran amene adasunga umaliseche wake; ndipo tidauzira mmenemo Mzimu Wathu ndipo adavomereza mawu a Mbuye wake (omwe adali zolamula Zake ndi zoletsa Zake) ndi mabuku Ake (amene adavumbulutsidwa kwa Aneneri Ake); ndipo adali mmodzi wa opitiriza kudzichepetsa (ndi kumvera Allah)
  67,1,“۞ Watukuka ndi kudalitsika (Allah) Amene m’manja Mwake muli ufumu (wochita chilichonse pazolengedwa zonse); ndipo Iye ali ndi mphamvu yokwanira pachilichonse
  67,2,“Amene adalenga imfa ndi moyo kuti akuyeseni (mayeso) ndani mwa inu ali wochita zabwino (kwambiri). Ndipo Iye ndiWopambana m’mphamvu (salephera kanthu) ndiponso Wokhululukira (olakwa)
  67,3,"“Amene adalenga thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri mosanjikana (kapena zolingana mkalengedwe kake). Suona kusiyana m’zolenga za Wachifundo chambiri. Bwereza kuyang’ana, kodi ukuona pena pong’ambika"
  67,4,"“Bwerezanso kuyang’ana kachiwiri, kuyang’anako kukubwerera wekha (uku maso) ali olobodoka ndiponso otopa. (Suona polakwika paliponse)"
  67,5,“Ndipo ndithu talikongoletsa thambo loyandikirali ndi nyali (nyenyezi) ndipo tazichita kukhala (mochokera zenje) zolasila asatana. Ndipo tawakonzera (patsiku lachimaliziro) chilango cha Moto woyaka
  67,6,“Ndipo kwa amene sakhulupirira Mbuye wawo ali nacho chilango cha Jahannam; ndipo kuipirenji kobwerera
  67,7,“Akadzaponyedwa m’menemo adzamva mavume ake (oipa) uku ukuwira mwaukali
  67,8,"“Udzayandikira kudukaduka chifukwa cha mkwiyo (kukwiira oipa); nthawi iliyonse gulu (la oipa) likadzaponyedwa m’menemo, Angelo oyang’anira Motowo adzawafunsa (mowadzudzula): “Kodi sadakufikeni mchenjezi (wokuchenjezani za tsikuli?).”"
  67,9,"“Adzayankha “Inde, adatifika mchenjezi koma tidatsutsa, ndipo tidati: ‘Allah sadavumbulutse chilichonse (kwa iwe ngakhale kwa anzako). Koma inu muli m’kusokera kwakukulu.”"
  67,10,"“Ndipo adzanena: “Tikadakhala kuti tidamvera (zimene ankatiuza) kapena kuziganizira mwanzeru sitikadakhala m’gulu la anthu a ku Moto.”"
  67,11,“Choncho adzavomereza machimo awo (koma sipadzakhala chopindula;) tero kuonongeka ndi kukhala kutali (ndi chifundo cha Allah) kuli pa anthu a ku Moto
  67,12,"“Ndithudi amene akumuopa Mbuye wawo pomwe iwo sakumuona, adzapeza chikhululuko pa machimo awo ndi malipiro aakulu (pa zabwino zomwe ankachita)"
  67,13,"“Ndipo bisani mawu anu, kapena aonetseni poyera; (zonsezi nchimodzimodzi kwa Allah) ndithudi Iye Ngodziwa zobisika za m’mitima"
  67,14,“Kodi asadziwe amene adalenga (zinthu zonse)? Pomwe Iye Ngodziwa zinthu zingo’nozing’no kwambiri mmene zilili (ndiponso) Ngodziwa nkhani zonse
  67,15,"“Iye ndi Amene wakupangirani nthaka kuti ikhale yogonjera (pa chilichonse chimene mufuna). Choncho yendani mbali zake zonse; ndipo idyani rizq lake, (limene Allah akukutulutsirani). Ndipo kwa Iye Yekha ndiko kobwerera kwanu (nonse mutapatsidwa moyo wachiwiri)"
  67,16,“Kodi muli m’chitetezo kwa Amene ali kumwamba kuti sangakukwilireni m’nthaka (ndikukudzidzimutsani) pamene nthaka ikugwedezeka molimba
  67,17,“Kapena muli m’chitetezo kwa Amene ali kumwamba kuti sangakutumizireni mphepo yamkuntho ya miyala (ndi kukuonongani ndi miyalayo?) Choncho mdzadziwa mmene lilili chenjezo Langa (pa inu)
  67,18,“Ndithudi amene adalipo kale iwo asanabadwe adakana mithenga yawo. Nanga udali bwanji mkwiyo Wanga pa iwo (pakuwaononga onse)
  67,19,"“Kodi, sadaone mbalame pamwamba pawo mmene zikutambasulira (mapiko ake) ndi kuwafumbata. Palibe amene akuzigwira kuti zisagwe koma (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri; ndithudi Iye pachilichonse Ngopenya"
  67,20,“Kodi ndani amene ali asilikali anu okutetezani kuchilango posakhala (Allah) Wachifimdo chambiri? Ndithudi osakhulupirira ali mkunyengeka (pa zimene akuganizira)
  67,21,"“Kodi ndani uyo amene angakupatseni rizq (limene mungakhalire ndi moyo ndi kupezera mtendere) ngati Iye atatsekereza rizq Lake (kwa inu)? Koma Akafiri akupitiriza kudzikweza kwawo, ndi kudziika kutali ndi choonadi"
  67,22,“Kodi amene akuyenda mozyolika ndi nkhope yake angakhale wolungama kapena amene akuyenda moongoka panjira yosakhota
  67,23,"“Nena: “Iye ndi Amene adakulengani (pomwe simudali kanthu) ndipo adakupatsani makutu, maso ndi mitima, (zimene mukhoza kupeza nazo mtendere). Koma kuyamika kwanu (kwa Yemwe adakupatsani zimenezi) nkochepa kwambiri"
  67,24,"“Nena: “Iye ndi amene adakuchulukitsani pa dziko ndipo kwa Iye (Yekha) ndiko mudzasonkhanitsidwa (kuti adzakuwerengereni ndi kukulipirani)"
  67,25,"“Akunena (monyada osakhulupirira za kuuka): “Ndiliti (lidzakwaniritsidwa) lonjezo ili ngati inu muli owona?”"
  67,26,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki{s.a.w}): “Ndithu kudziwa (kwa izi) nkwa Allah yekha, ndipo ndithudi ine, ndine mchenjezi wowonekera.”"
  67,27,"“Koma akadzaziona (zimene akulonjezedwazo) zili pafupi (ndi iwo), nkhope za amene sadakhulupirire zidzakhumudwa ndikuyaluka kwambiri, ndipo kudzanenedwa (mowadzudzula): “Izi ndi zija mudali kuzipempha (kuti zidze, zadza tsopano)"
  67,28,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki{s.a.w}): “Tandiuzani ngati Allah atandiononga pamodzi ndi amene ndili nawo (monga momwe mukufunira) kapena kutichitira chifundo (ndikutalikitsa nthawi ya moyo wathu). Nanga ndani amene adzawateteza wosakhulupirira ku chilango chowawa?”"
  67,29,"“Nena: “Iye ndiye (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri, takhulupirira mwa Iye ndiponso kwa Iye ndikumene tatsamira. Choncho posachedwapa mudziwa (chilango chikatsika kuti) ndani (m’magulu awiriwa) yemwe ali m’kusokera koonekera.”"
  67,30,"“Nena: “Tandiuzani ngati madzi anuwa ataphwa (kulowelera pansi penipeni); choncho ndani amene angakubweretsereni madzi oyenda (ochokera mkati mwanthaka)"
  68,1,"“Nûn. Ndikulumbilira cholembera (chimene akulembera angelo), ndi zimene amalemba"
  68,2,“Pa chisomo cha Mbuye wako iwe sindiwe wamisala (pokupatsa uneneri)
  68,3,"“Ndipo ndithu udzakhala ndi malipiro akulu osaduka, (onkerankera mtsogolo chifukwa cha mavuto amene ukukumana nawo pofikitsa uthenga)"
  68,4,“Ndipo ndithu uli nawo makhalidwe abwino kwambiri (omwe Allah adakulenga nawo)
  68,5,"“Basi, posachedwapa uona, iwonso aona"
  68,6,“Kuti ndani mwa inu wamisala (iwe kapena iwo)
  68,7,“Ndithu Mbuye wako akum’dziwa bwino amene wasokera panjira yake. Ndiponso akuwadziwa bwino amene ali oongoka
  68,8,"“Choncho, usawamvere otsutsa; (usasiye zimene uli nazo ngakhale sakugwirizana nazo)"
  68,9,“Akufuna kuti ukadakhala wofewa kwa iwo (pa zinthu zina) nawo akadakhala ofewa (kwa iwe)
  68,10,"“Ndipo usamumvere aliyense wochulukitsa kulumbira, woyaluka"
  68,11,"“Wojeda, woyenda ndi ukazitape (ndi cholinga choononga umodzi wawo)"
  68,12,"“Wotsekereza zabwino, wamtopola, wamachimo ambiri"
  68,13,“Wouma mtima; pamwamba pa izi ndi wodzipachika mu mtundu wa ena (pomwe iye sali m’menemo)
  68,14,“Chifukwa choti iye ndi mwini chuma ndi ana (ndi zimene ali kunyadira)
  68,15,"“Zikawerengedwa kwa iye Ayah Zathu amanena: “Izi ndi nthano za akale (ndi zabodza zawo, zopeka).”"
  68,16,“Timuika pamphuno pake chizindikiro (chosasiyana nacho kuti ayaluke nacho pamaso pa anthu)
  68,17,"“Ndithu ife tidawayesa (eni mzinda wa Makka ndi mtendere omwe udali pa iwo, koma adakana monga) momwe tidawayesera eni munda, pamene adalumbira kuti akathyola (zipatso za m’munda wawozo) mbandakucha (kuti osauka asawaone angawapemphe)"
  68,18,"“Ndipo sadapatule (ngakhale wosauka ndi m’modzi yemwe ponena kuti uje timpatse, uje tisampatse, kapena sadanene kuti: “Ngati Allah afuna).”"
  68,19,“Mliri woopsa wochokera kwa Mbuye wako udauzinga (mundawo nthawi yausiku) iwo ali mtulo
  68,20,“Choncho udakhala ngati wokololedwa (chifukwa cha mliri uja)
  68,21,“Tero adaitanizana nthawi ya mbandakucha
  68,22,““Lawilirani kumunda wanu kuja ngati mukufuna kukolola (kuopera kuti angakuoneni osauka).”
  68,23,“Adanyamuka uku akunong’ onezana
  68,24,"“(Akunena kuti): “Asakulowelereni wosauka lero mmenemo.”"
  68,25,“Ndipo adalawilira ali ndi chitsimikizo choti atha kuwamana (osauka)
  68,26,"“Choncho pamene adauona, adanena (uku akunjenjemera): “Ndithu ife tasokera (sikuno ayi, munda wathu uja siuno).”"
  68,27,"““Iyayi, ndiwomwewu; koma tamanidwa zinthu zake.”"
  68,28,"“Wolungama mwa iwo adanena: “Kodi sindinakuuzeni (pamene mudali kulangizana zomana osowa) kuti bwanji osamkumbukira Allah (ndi kusintha cholinga chanu)?”"
  68,29,"“(Iwo) adanena: “Alemekezeke Mbuye wathu ndithu ife tidali achinyengo (chifukwa cha kuipa kwa cholinga chathu).”"
  68,30,“Ndipo adatembenukirana ndikuyamba kudzudzulana
  68,31,"“Adati: “E chionongeko chathu! Ndithu Ife tidapyola malire (m’chinyengo chathu).”"
  68,32,““Mwina Mbuye wathu angatipatse zabwino m’malo mwa munda wathuwu. Ndithu ife tikufunitsitsa kwa Mbuye wathu (chikhululuko Chake).”
  68,33,"“Umo ndi mmene chimakhalira chilango (Changa chomwe ndimachitsitsa pa dziko lapansi kwa amene chamuyenera); koma chilango cha tsiku lachimaliziro nchachikulu zedi, akadakhala akudziwa"
  68,34,“Ndithu oopa Allah adzakhala ndi Minda ya mtendere kwa Mbuye wawo
  68,35,“Kodi tiwachite Asilamu monga ochimwa
  68,36,“Kodi nchiyani chakupezani! Nanga mukuweruza bwanji (maweruzo opanda chilungamo)
  68,37,“Kapena muli ndi buku limene mukuwerenga
  68,38,“Kuti ndithu mulinazo mmenemo zomwe mukudzisankhira
  68,39,“Kapena muli nawo mapangano ndi Ife okafika mpaka tsiku lachimaliziro akuti inu mudzapeza zimene mukudziweruzira
  68,40,“Afunse (iwe Mtumiki) ndani mwa iwo amene ali mtsogoleri (pa malamulo amenewa)
  68,41,“Kapena iwo ali nawo othandidzana nawo (pa mau awa)? Chomwecho atabweretsa othandizana nawo ngati akunena zowona
  68,42,"“(Akumbukire) tsiku la mavuto okhwima, ndipo adzaitanidwa (akafiri) kuti achite sijida (polambira Allah) koma sadzatha"
  68,43,"“Maso awo adzangoti pansi zyoli, manyazi ndi kunyozeka kudzawaphimba; chikhalirecho adali kuitanidwa (pa dziko lapansi) kuti agwetse nkhope pansi pomwe iwo adali ndi moyo wa ngwiro (koma ankakana)"
  68,44,"“Choncho ndisiye, (iwe Mtumiki), ndi amene akukanira nkhani iyi tiwakokera kuchilango pang’onopang’ono pamene iwo sakudziwa (mmene chiti chiwadzere chilangochi)"
  68,45,"“Ndipo ndikuwalekelera (pochedwetsa chilango); ndithudi makonzedwe Anga ngokhwima, (palibe angapulumuke mmenemo)"
  68,46,“Kapena ukuwapempha malipiro (pofikitsa uthenga) kotero kuti iwo akulemedwa ndi kulipira
  68,47,“Kapena ali nazo (nzeru) zobisika kotero kuti iwo akulemba (zimene akuweruzazo)
  68,48,“Choncho pirira ndi lamulo la Mbuye wako (chifukwa chowalekelera ndi kuchedwetsa chipulumutso chako); ndipo usakhale ngati mwini nsomba (Yunusu pa changu ndi mkwiyo kwa anthu ake) pamene adaitana (Mbuye wake) uku ali wodzazidwa ndi mkwiyo (kupempha kuti chidze mwachangu chilango kwa anthu ake)
  68,49,"“Chikadapanda kumfikira chisomo chochokera kwa Mbuye wake (ndi kuvomera kulapa kwake), akadaponyedwa (kuchokera m’mimba mwa chinsomba chija) pagombe (popanda kanthu) ali wodzudzulidwa"
  68,50,“Koma adamsankha Mbuye wake (povomera kulapa kwake) ndipo adamchita kukhala mmodzi wa anthu abwino
  68,51,"“Ndithudi anthu amene sadakhulupirire adayandikira kukuteleretsa ndi kunyogodola kwa maso awo (chifukwa chachidani ndi mkwiyo) pamene adamva chikumbutso (Qur’an), ndipo akunena kuti iyeyo ngwamisala"
  68,52,"“Ndipo ichi sichina, koma (ndi phunziro, ndi nzeru) ndi chikumbutso kwa zolengedwa zonse"
  69,1,“Chakudza cha choonadi (chomwe ndi Qiyâma)
  69,2,“Kodi chakudza cha choonadi nchiyani
  69,3,“Nanga nchiyani chikudziwitse za chakudza cha choonadicho
  69,4,“Asamudu ndi Âdi adatsutsa zakudza kwa Qiyâma (yomwe idzadzidzimutsa zolengedwa mwamphamvu ndi zoopsa zake)
  69,5,"“Tsono Asamudu adaonongedwa ndi phokoso lopyola muyeso, (lamphamvu kwambiri)"
  69,6,"“Ndipo Âdi adaonongedwa ndi chimphepo cha mkuntho, chozizira, champhamvu kwambiri"
  69,7,“Allah adachitumiza kwa iwo pa usiku usanu ndi uwiri ndi masana asanu ndi atatu mosadukiza; kotero ukadawaona ali lambalamba mmenemo ngati mathunthu a mitengo ya kanjedza yopanda kanthu m’kati mwake
  69,8,“Kodi nanga ukumuona wotsala mwa iwo
  69,9,"“Ndipo Firiaun ndi amene adalipo iye asadabadwe, ndi khamu la anthu amidzi yotembenuzidwa (anthu a Luti) adadza ndi machimo (akulu)"
  69,10,“Ndipo (yense wa iwowa) adanyoza Mtumiki wa Mbuye wawo; choncho adawalanga chilango chopitilira muyeso
  69,11,“Ndithu pamene madzi adasefukira mopyola muyeso (mpaka kumeza mapiri nthawi ya chigumula cha Nowa) Ife tidakukwezani mchombo choyandama ndi kuyenda
  69,12,"“Kuti tichichite (chochitikacho chomwe okhulupirira adapulumuka nacho; osakhulupirira adaonongeka nacho) kukhala lingaliro ndi phunziro kwa inu, ndikuti lisunge (nkhaniyi) khutu losunga"
  69,13,"“Choncho likadzaimbidwa lipenga, kuimba kumodzi kokha (zamoyo zonse zidzafa)"
  69,14,“Ndipo nthaka ndi mapiri nkuchotsedwa m’malo mwake ndi kuphwanyidwa kamodzi nkamodzi
  69,15,"“Chomwecho tsiku limenelo, chochitika chidzachitika (imene ili Qiyâma)"
  69,16,“Ndipo thambo lidzasweka choncho ilo tsiku limenelo lidzakhala lofooka (pamene lidali lolimba)
  69,17,"“Ndipo angelo adzakhala m’mphepete mwake, ndipo pamwamba pawo tsiku limenero (angelo) asanu ndi atatu adzasenza Arsh (Mpando wachifumu) ya Mbuye wako"
  69,18,“Tsiku limenelo mudzabweretsedwa ku chiweruzo; sichidzabisika chilichonse chobisika mwa inu
  69,19,"“Tsono amene adzapatsidwa kaundula wake chakudzanja lakumanja kwake adzanena (mokondwa kwa amene ali m’phepete mwake): “Tengani! Werengani kaundula wanga!”"
  69,20,““Ndithudi ine ndidatsimikiza (pa dziko lapansi) kuti ndidzakumana ndi chiwerengero changa.”
  69,21,"“Choncho, iye adzakhala m’moyo wosangalatsa"
  69,22,“M’munda wapamwamba
  69,23,“Zipatso zake zoyandikira pansi (zosavuta kuzithyola)
  69,24,"“(Adzawauza kuti:) “Idyani, ndipo imwani mosangalala pa zimene mudatsogoza mmasiku aja adapita (a pa dziko lapansi).”"
  69,25,"“Ndipo amene adzapatsidwe kaundula wake kudzanja lake lamanzere, adzanena (modandaula): “Kalanga ine! Ndiponi ndikadapanda kupatsidwa kaundula wangayu!”"
  69,26,““Nkusadziwa chiwerengero changa!”
  69,27,““Ha! imfa ija ikadandimaliziratu (ndi kundilekanitsa ine ndi zimenezi).”
  69,28,““Chuma changa sichidandithandize!”
  69,29,““Mphamvu zanga (ndi moyo wanga wathanzi) zandichokera!”
  69,30,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa angelo oyang’anira Jahena): Mgwireni ndipo mnjateni (pomphatikiza manja ndi khosi)"
  69,31,“Kenako mponyeni ku Moto
  69,32,“Kenakonso mulowetseni mtcheni lotalika mikwamba makumi asanu ndi awiri
  69,33,"“Ndithudi, iye sadali kukhulupirira mwa Allah wamkulu"
  69,34,“Sadalinso kulimbikitsa zodyetsa osauka
  69,35,"“Basi, lero kuno alibe bwenzi (lomthandiza)"
  69,36,“Ngakhale chakudya kupatula mafinya (a anthu a ku Moto)
  69,37,“Zomwe palibe angazidye kupatula ochimwa (mwadala)
  69,38,“Choncho ndikulumbilira zimene mukuziona
  69,39,“Ndi zimene simukuziona
  69,40,“Ndithudi iyi (Qur’an) ndiliwu la mthenga wolemekezeka (Jibril)
  69,41,"“Ndipo simawu a mlakatuli, ndi zochepa zimene mukuzikhulupirira"
  69,42,"“Ndiponso simawu a mlosi, ndizochepa zimene mmakumbukira"
  69,43,“(Ichi ndi) chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Mbuye wa zolengedwa
  69,44,“Ndipo (Mneneri) akadatipekera bodza linalake
  69,45,“Tikadamgwira (mwamphamvu) ndimkono wamanja
  69,46,“Ndipo tikadadula mwa iye mtsempha wa moyo (kotero kuti ndikuferatu nthawi yomweyo)
  69,47,“Sipakadapezeka aliyense mwa inu womteteza (kuchilango Chathu)
  69,48,“Ndithu iyi (Qur’an) ndi phunziro labwino kwa owopa (Allah)
  69,49,"“Ndithu Ife, tikudziwa kuti ena mwa inu ndiotsutsa (Qur’an)"
  69,50,“Ndipo ndithu iyi (Qur’an) idzakhala chowadandaulitsa (chachikulu) osakhulupirira (pamene adzaona chilango chawo ndi mtendere wa okhulupirira)
  69,51,“Ndithu iyoyi ndichoonadi Chotsimikizika; (mulibe chikaiko)
  69,52,"“Basi, lemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wamkulu (pitiriza kutamanda dzina Lake)"
  70,1,"“Wopempha adapempha kuti chiwadzere msanga chilango chopezekacho, (m’kupempha kwa chipongwe ndi kotsutsa)"
  70,2,“Kwa okanira palibe angachitsekereze
  70,3,“Chochokera kwa Allah Mwini makwelero
  70,4,“Angelo ndi Jiburil amakwera kwa Iye (Allah) m’tsiku lomwe kutalika kwake kuli ngati zaka zikwi makumi asanu
  70,5,"“Choncho, pirira (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w) kupirira kwabwino"
  70,6,“Ndithu iwo akuliona (tsiku la Qiyâma) kuti lili kutali (silingachitike)
  70,7,“Koma Ife tikuliona kuti lilipafupi (ndilochitika)
  70,8,“Tsiku limene thambo lidzakhala ngati mtovu wosungunuka
  70,9,“Ndipo mapiri adzakhala ngati ubweya (wongouluka wokha)
  70,10,“Ndipo m’bale sadzafunsa za m’bale wake
  70,11,“Ngakhale adzawalole kuti aonane ndi kudziwana pakati pawo (sadzafunsana). Wochimwa adzalakalaka kuti akadaziwombola ku chilango cha tsiku limenelo ndi ana ake
  70,12,"“Ndi mkazi wake, ndi m’bale wake"
  70,13,“Ndi akumtundu wake amene amamsunga
  70,14,"“Ndi (kulipira) zonse za m’dziko, kuti zimpulumutse"
  70,15,"“Iyayi, (siya iwe wamachimo zimene ukulakalakazo)! Ndithu umenewu ndi Moto wa malawi"
  70,16,“Wosupula mwamphamvu khungu
  70,17,“Udzaitana (potchula dzina la aliyense) amene adachitembenuzira msana choona ndi kunyoza
  70,18,“Adasonkhanitsa (chuma) ndi kusunga (m’nkhokwe zake popanda kuperekera chopereka cha Allah)
  70,19,“Ndithu munthu walengedwa kukhala wosapirira
  70,20,“Mavuto akamkhudza amada nkhawa
  70,21,“Koma zabwino zikamkhudza amamana (ena ndi kuiwala mavuto amene adali nawo)
  70,22,"“Kupatula opemphera Swala, (iwo alibe mbiri zoipazi)"
  70,23,“Iwo amene sadukiza mapemphero awo a swala; (sakuwaleka ngakhale zivute chotani)
  70,24,“Ndi amene mchuma chawo muli gawo lodziwika (Zakaat)
  70,25,“La wopempha ndi wosapempha
  70,26,“Ndi amene akuvomereza za tsiku la malipiro (ndi kumalikonzekera)
  70,27,“Ndi iwo amene akuopa chilango chochokera kwa Mbuye wawo
  70,28,“Ndithu chilango cha Mbuye wawo nchosapulumuka nacho (munthu woipa)
  70,29,“Ndiponso iwo amene akusunga umaliseche wawo (posachita chiwerewere)
  70,30,“Kupatula kwa akazi awo ndi amene manja awo akumanja apeza; ndithu pazimenezo iwo sangadzudzulidwe
  70,31,“Koma amene angafune (zina) kusiya zimenezi iwowo ndiwo olumpha malire
  70,32,“Ndi iwo amene amasunga mwaubwino zimene amasungitsidwa ndi zimene alonjeza
  70,33,“Ndi iwo amene amaima molungama popereka umboni wawo
  70,34,“Ndiponso iwo amene amasunga (mwaubwino) mapemphero awo a swala
  70,35,“Amene ali ndi mbiri zimenezi adzakhala m’Minda (yamtendere) ali olemekezedwa
  70,36,“Kodi kuli chiyani kwa amene akana (chikhulupiliro) akuthamangira kwa iwe (maso ali pamtunda)
  70,37,“Atakuzungulira ena chakumanja ena chakumanzere
  70,38,“Kodi akulakalaka aliyense mwa iwo kuti akalowetsedwe ku Munda wamtendere
  70,39,“Asiye (kukhumba kwawo kokalowa ku Munda wamtendere)! Ndithu Ife tidawalenga kuchokera m’zimene akudziwa (madzi opanda pake)
  70,40,“Ndikulumbilira Mbuye wa kuvuma ndi kuzambwe konse ndithu Ndife Wokhoza
  70,41,“Kuwasintha ndi kudzetsa abwino kuposa iwo; Ife palibe (chilichonse) chotipambana
  70,42,“Asiye azingolankhula zopanda pake ndi kumangosewera mpaka adzakumane ndi tsiku lawo limene akulonjezedwa
  70,43,“Tsiku limene adzatuluke m’manda uku akuthamanga (kudza kwa woitana) ngati kuti akuthamangira kumafano awo (amene adali kuwapembedza)
  70,44,"“Maso awo ali zyoli, (osatha kuwakweza); kuyaluka kutawaphimba! Limenelo ndilo tsiku lomwe adali kulonjezedwa (pomwe adali padziko lapansi)"
  71,1,"“Ndithu Ife tidamtuma Nuh kwa anthu ake, (ndikumuuza kuti): “Chenjeza anthu ako chisadawafike chilango chowawa.”"
  71,2,"“Adanena (Nuh): “E inu anthu anga! Ndithu ine ndimchenjezi kwa inu woonekera poyera (wolongosola za uthenga wa Mbuye wanu m’chiyankhulo chimene mukuchidziwa).”"
  71,3,““Mpembedzeni Allah ndipo rnuopeni ndikutinso mundimvere (pazimene ndikukulangizani).”
  71,4,““(Ngati mutero) adzakukhululukirani machimo anu ndi kukutalikitsirani moyo wanu kufikira m’nthawi imene yaikidwa (kuti ndiwo malire a kutalika kwa moyo). Ndithu nthawi ya Allah ikabwera siyichedwetsedwa (ngakhale pang’ono) mukadakhala mukudziwa.”
  71,5,"“Adanena (Nuh): “E Mbuye wanga! Ndithu ine ndaitanira anthu anga (ku chikhulupiliro) usiku ndi usana (popanda kufooka).”"
  71,6,““Kuitana kwanga sikudaonjezere (chilichonse) koma kuthawa basi (kuchikhulupiliro Chanu).”
  71,7,"“Ndipo ine nthawi iliyonse ndikawaitanira (ku chikhulupiliro Chanu) kuti mwakhululukire, akuika zala zawo m’makutu mwawo (kuti asamve uthenga Wanu), ndipo akudziphimba ndi nsalu zawo (kuti asaone nkhope yanga), ndipo akupitiriza kukana kwawo ndi kudzikweza kwakukulu"
  71,8,“Kenaka ine ndawaitanira (kwa Inu) ndi mawu ofuula
  71,9,“Kenakanso (ine ndawaitanira) molengeza poyera ndiponso mwachinsinsi mobisa
  71,10,"“Choncho ndidati (kwa anthu anga): Pemphani kwa Mbuye wanu chikhululuko (pa kukana kwanu ndi kutonza kwanu), ndithu Iye ali Wokhululuka kwambiri"
  71,11,“Akutumizirani mvula yotsika mochuluka
  71,12,"“Ndikukupatsani chuma ndi ana, (zomwe ndi zokongoletsa za dziko lapansi), ndi kukupangirani minda (yokongola) ndi kukupangirani mitsinje (yothilira mbewu zanu ndi kumwetsa ziweto zanu)"
  71,13,“Kodi chifukwa ninji simupereka ulemu kwa Allah (woyenera Umulungu Wake kuti akakuchitireni chifundo ndi kukupulumutsani ku chilango)
  71,14,"“Pomwe Iye adakulengani mnjira zosiyanasiyana; (madzi a umunthu, kenako magazi, kenako magazi ochindikala, kenako mafupa ndipo kenako mnofu)"
  71,15,“Kodi simudaone momwe Allah adalengera thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri mosanjikizana
  71,16,"“Ndi kuyika mwezi mthambomo kukhala kuunika, ndiponso kuyika dzuwa kukhala nyali"
  71,17,“Ndipo Allah adakulengani kuchokera m’nthaka monga mmera
  71,18,“Kenako adzakubwezerani momwemo ndikudzakutulutsaninso (popanda cholepheretsa)
  71,19,“Ndipo Allah wakupangirani nthaka kukhala ngati choyala
  71,20,“Kuti muziyendayenda m’menemo m’njira zazikulu.”
  71,21,"“Adanena Nuh: “Mbuye wanga! Ndithu anthu anga andinyoza (pa zimene ndawalamula kuti akhulupirire Inu ndi kupempha chikhululuko chanu), ndipo (ofooka mwa iwo) amtsatira yemwe chuma chake ndi ana ake sizidzamuonjezera (chilichonse chabwino) koma kutaika (ndi kuonongeka pa tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  71,22,“Ndipo (eni chuma ndi ana) awatchera (otsatira awo) ndale zazikulu (ndi zopyola muyeso kuti asakhulupirire).”
  71,23,"“Ndipo adanena (kwa owatsatira awo): “Musasiye kupembedza milungu yanu; musamusiye Wadda, Suwaa’, Yaghutha, Ya’uqa ndi Nasra” (maina a mafano awo)"
  71,24,“Ndipo ndithu iwo asokeretsa (anthu) ambiri; ndipo musawaonjezere ochita zoipa (china chake) koma kusokera basi.”
  71,25,“Chifukwa cha zochimwa zawo adamizidwa ndi kulowetsedwa ku Moto (waukulu woyaka); sadapeze owapulumutsa ndi kuwateteza m’malo mwa Allah
  71,26,"“Ndipo adanena Nuh (atataya mtima za anthu ake): “Mbuye wanga! Musasiye aliyense mwa osakhulupirira kukhala pa dziko.”"
  71,27,"““Ndithu Inu Mbuye wanga ngati muwasiya (popanda kuwaononga ndi kuwathetsa) asokeretsa akapolo anu (kunjira yolungama). Ndipo sangabereke (ana abwino) koma oipa; osakhulupirira (okhala kutali ndi choonadi, ndiponso onyoza Inu).”"
  71,28,"““Mbuye wanga! Ndikhululukireni ndi makolo anga, ndi aliyense walowa m’nyumba yanga ali okhulupirira ndi okhulupirira amuna ndi okhulupirira akazi. Ndipo musawaonjezere anthu achinyengo chinachake koma kuwaononga basi.”"
  72,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w), kwa anthu ako): “Kwavumbulutsidwa kwa ine kuti gulu la ziwanda lidamvetsera (kuwerenga kwanga kwa Qur’an) ndipo lidanena (kumtundu wawo): ndithu tamvetsera Qur’an yodabwitsa (ikuwerengedwa)"
  72,2,"“Ikuitanira kuchilungamo, ndipo taikhulupirira. Ndipo sitimphatikiza aliyense ndi Mbuye wathu, (pa mapemphero)"
  72,3,“Ndipo ndithu ukulu ndi ulemelero wa Mbuye wathu watukuka; sadadzipangire mkazi kapena mwana
  72,4,“Ndipo ndithu mbuli za mwa ife zakhala zikunenera Allah mawu abodza (okhala kutali ndi choonadi)
  72,5,“Ndipo ndithu ife tinkaganiza kuti anthu ndi ziwanda sangamnenere Allah zabodza (zosayenera ulemelero Wake)
  72,6,"“Ndipo ndithu padali amuna a mu wanthu amapempha chitetezo kwa amuna amziwanda, ndipo adawaonjezera (amuna amziwanda) kupitiriza machimo (awo, kupulikira ndi kuchenjelera anthu)"
  72,7,“Ndipo ndithu iwo amaganiza monga momwe mumaganizira inu kuti Allah sadzaukitsa aliyense
  72,8,“Ndithu ife tidafuna kukafika kumwamba; tidakupeza kutadzala alonda (angelo) amphamvu ndi zenje za moto
  72,9,“Ndithu ife tidali kukhala m’menemo (kale) mokhala momvetsera; (mobera nkhani zakumwamba). Koma amene afune kumvetsera tsopano apeza chenje cha moto chikudikilira (kuti chimgwere iye ndi kumuononga)
  72,10,"“Ndithu ife sitikudziwa chilango chimene akuwafunira a m’dziko (polondera kumwamba, kuletsa kumvetsera nkhani zakumeneko); kapena Mbuye wawo akuwafunira zabwino ndi chilungamo (pa zimenezo)"
  72,11,“Ndithu ena mwa ife ndi abwino koma ena sali choncho. Tili njira zosiyanasiyana
  72,12,"“Ndithu ife tidadziwa kuti Allah sitingathe kumlepheretsa (lamulo Lake pa ife paliponse tingakhale) pa dziko lapansi, ndipo sitingamlepheretsenso pomzemba ndi kuthawira (kumwamba)"
  72,13,“Ndipo ife pamene tachimva chiongoko (Qur’an) tachikhulupirira ndipo amene ati akhulupirire mwa Mbuye wake saopa kumchepetsera (chabwino kapena kumuonjezera machimo ake)
  72,14,"“Ndithu mwa ife alipo Asilamu ndiponso mwa ife alipo opatuka (mu njira ya chilungamo); amene walowa m’Chisilamu, iwowo ndi amene alunjika njira ya choonadi"
  72,15,“Koma opatuka (kunjira ya chilungamo) adzakhala nkhuni za Jahannam.”
  72,16,“Ndithu (anthu ndi ziwanda) akadalungama panjira ya chilungamo tikadawamwetsa madzi ambiri (okwanira nyengo zonse)
  72,17,"“Kuti tiwayese ndi zimenezo (mmene angamyamikire Allah pa mtendere Wake pa iwo). Koma amene anyozera kupembedza Mbuye wake, amlowetsa ku chilango chovuta (chimene sangathe kupirira nacho)"
  72,18,"“Ndithu misikiti ndi ya Allah yekha! Choncho, musapembedze aliyense pamodzi ndi Allah"
  72,19,"“Ndipo ndithu pamene adaima kapolo wa Allah (Muhammad{s.a.w}, pa Swala yake) uku akumpembedza (Allah), ziwanda zidatsala pang’ono kumgwera (chifukwa cha kuchuluka kwawo ndi kumzinga podabwa ndi zimene adaziona ndi kuzimva)"
  72,20,"“Nena: “Ndikumpembedza Mbuye wanga M’modzi (Yekha) ndipo sindingamphatikize ndi aliyense (m’mapemphero Ake).”"
  72,21,"“Nena: “Ine ndilibe udindo wokupatsani mavuto kapena chilungamo (ndi zabwino).”"
  72,22,"“Nena: “Ine palibe anganditeteze ku chilango cha Allah (ngati nditamnyoza) sindingapeze malo (othawira kuchilango Chake) kupatula kwa Iye.”"
  72,23,"““Koma (mphamvu imene ndili nayo) ndikufikitsa uthenga wa Allah umene adanditumizira; ndithu amene anyoza Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake (ndi kupatuka pa chipembedzo cha (Allah) ndithu moto wa Jahannam ndi wake, akakhala m’menemo muyaya.”"
  72,24,"“Mpaka pomwe adzaziona zimene alonjezedwa ndipamene adzadziwa (kuti) kodi ndani mwini mthandizi wofooka ndiponso wochepekedwa mchiwerengero (cha omtsatira, iwo kapena Asilamu).”"
  72,25,"“Nena (kuti): “Sindikudziwa ngati zomwe mukulonjezedwa (za chilango) zili pafupi, kapena Mbuye wanga azitalikitsa.”"
  72,26,"““(Iye) ndi wodziwa zobisika; sazionetsa zobisika Zake kwa aliyense (mzolengedwa Zake),”"
  72,27,““Kupatula Mtumiki (Wake) amene wamuyanja; (iyeyo amamdziwitsa zobisikazo) ndipo ndithu amamuikira alonda kutsogolo kwake ndi kumbuyo kwake (omulonda).”
  72,28,"““Kuti adziwe ngati afikitsa uthenga wa Mbuye wawo, ndipo wawazungulira (podziwa zonse zili kwa iwo) ndipo wadziwa kuchuluka kwa zinthu zonse zimene zilipo; (palibe chobisika kwa Iye).”"
  73,1,“E iwe wadzifunditsa (ndi nsalu)
  73,2,"“Imilira usiku (upemphere), kupatula nthawi yochepa"
  73,3,“Theka lake kapena chepetsa thekalo pang’ono (mpaka ufike chimodzi mwa zigawo zitatu za usiku)
  73,4,“Kapena wonjezapo (mpaka ufike zigawo ziwiri mwa zigawo zitatu za usiku;) ndipo werenga Qur’an mofatsa (lemba ndi lemba)
  73,5,“Ife tikuvumbulutsira iwe (Mneneri) mawu olemera (yomwe ndi Qur’an)
  73,6,"“Ndithu kudzuka usiku ndi kuchita mapemphero kumalowelera (mu mtima) kwambiri, ndipo zoyankhula zake zimakhala zoongoka ndi zolunjika bwino (kuposa mapemphero amasana)"
  73,7,“Ndithu masana uli ndi zochitachita zambiri; (umatanganidwa ndi ntchito yauthenga; dzipatse danga usiku polimbika kupemphera)
  73,8,"“Ndipo tchula dzina la Mbuye wako (Amene adalenga ndi kulera zinthu), ndipo udzipereke kwathunthu kwa Iye"
  73,9,“(Iye ndiye) Mbuye wa kuvuma ndi kuzambwe; palibe wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye. Mchiteni kukhala Mtetezi (wanu pa zinthu zanu zonse)
  73,10,“Ndipo pirira pa zimene akunena. Ndipo apewe (ndi mtima wako); kupewa kwabwino
  73,11,“Ndisiye Ine ndi otsutsa eni kupeza bwino; ndipo alekelere kanthawi kochepa
  73,12,"“Ndithudi, tili ndi mitundumitundu ya unyolo ndi Moto woyaka"
  73,13,“Ndi chakudya chotsamwitsa ndi chilango chowawa
  73,14,“Tsiku limene nthaka ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka; (kugwedezeka kwa mphamvu kotero kuti) mapiri adzakhala ngati mulu wa mchenga woyoyoka
  73,15,“Ndithu Ife takutumizirani Mthenga amene adzakhala mboni yanu (tsiku la chimaliziro; monga momwe tidamtumizira (Mûsa) kukhala Mtumiki kwa Firiauni
  73,16,“Koma Firiauni adamnyoza Mtumikiyo; ndipo tidamulanga chilango chokhwima
  73,17,“Kodi mungadzitchinjirize chotani ngati mukana (chilango cha) tsiku (lomwe) lidzachititsa ana kukhala ndi imvi
  73,18,"“Thambo (pamodzi ndi mphamvu zake ndi kukula kwake), lidzang’ambika (tsiku limenelo) chifukwa cha kuopsa kwa tsikulo, lonjezo la (Allah) lidzakwaniritsidwa (palibe wolipinga)"
  73,19,"“Ndithudi, ma Ayah awa (amene akunena za kuwopsa kwa Qiyâma) ndichikumbutso. Choncho amene akufuna (kuthandizika nawo) ayende panjira ya Mbuye wake (pokwaniritsa malamulo Ake ndi kuleka zoipa)"
  73,20,"“Ndithu Mbuye wako akudziwa kuti iwe ukuima (kupemphera) pafupifupi magawo awiri mwa magawo atatu a usiku kapena theka lake, kape’nanso gawo limodzi mwa magawo atatu a usiku, pamodzi ndi gulu la omwe uli nawo. Ndipo Allah ndi Amene amadziwa bwino muyeso wa (nthawi za) usiku ndi usana, wadziwa kuti simungathe kuwerengera zimenezo, choncho wakukhululukirani. Werengani ndime imene yapepuka yochokera m’Qur’an. Wadziwa kuti ena mwa inu adzakhala odwala; (kudzawavuta kuimilira ndi kuchezera usiku), ndipo ena adzakhala akuyendayenda pa dziko (ndi cholinga cha malonda ndi ntchito) kunka nafunafuna ubwino wa Allah. Ndipo ena adzakhala akumenya nkhondo pa njira ya Allah (ncholinga chotukula mawu Ake), werengani chimene chapepuka chochokera mmenemo (m’Qur’an). Ndipo pitirizani kupemphera Swala, perekani chopereka (chimene chakakamizidwa kwa inu). Ndipo mkongozeni Allah ngongole yabwino. Ndipo chilichonse chabwino chimene mwadzitsogozera mudzachipeza kwa Allah chili chabwino (kuposa zomwe mudazisiya m’mbuyo) ndi malipiro akulu zedi ndipo mpempheni Allah chikhululuko (pa uchimo wanu ndi chikhululuko pakunyozera kwanu kuchita zabwino). Ndithu Allah Ngokhululuka, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  74,1,“E iwe wadziphimba (nsalu)
  74,2,“Imilira ndipo uwachenjeze (anthu za chilango cha Allah)
  74,3,“Ndipo Mbuye wako (Yekha) umkulitse (pomulemekeza)
  74,4,“Ndipo nsalu zako uziyeretse (ndi madzi ku uve)
  74,5,“Ndiponso zoipa (monga mafano ndi zina zonse ) zipewe
  74,6,“Usapatse (anthu) ncholinga choti ulandire zambiri
  74,7,"“Chifukwa cha Mbuye wako, pirira (ku malamulo Ake poleka zomwe waletsa ndi kuchita zimene walamula)"
  74,8,“Ndipo likadzaimbidwa lipenga
  74,9,“Tsiku limenelo lidzakhala tsiku lovuta
  74,10,"“Kwa osakhulupirira, silidzakhala lofewa"
  74,11,“Ndisiye ndiamene ndidamlenga Ndekha
  74,12,“Ndipo ndampatsa chuma chambiri
  74,13,“Ndi ana okhala nawo (paliponse)
  74,14,"“Ndipo ndamkonzera (ulemelero), kumkonzera (kwabwino)"
  74,15,“Kenako ali ndi dyera kuti ndimuonjezere (zina popanda kuthokoza)
  74,16,“Koma sichoncho! Ndithu iye adali kutsutsa zizindikiro Zathu
  74,17,“Ndidzamkakamiza kuchilango chovuta; (kukwera phiri la ku Moto limene sakatha kulikwera)
  74,18,“Iye adalingalira (mu mtima mwake) ndi kukonza bwino (chonena chonyoza Qur’an)
  74,19,“Choncho waonongeka! Adakonza bwanji (poinyoza Qur’an)
  74,20,“Ndiponso waonongeka! Adakonza bwanji (poinyoza Qur’an)
  74,21,“Kenako adayang’anayang’ana (nkhope za anthu)
  74,22,“Kenakonso adachita tsinya ndikukwinya nkhope (kwambiri ndi mkwiyo)
  74,23,“Kenakonso adanyoza choonadi ndi kudzikweza (posachivomereza)
  74,24,"“Adati: “Sichina ichi (Qur’an) koma ndi matsenga amene adalandiridwa (kuchokera kwa amatsenga akale)"
  74,25,“Sichina ichi koma ndi mawu a anthu!”
  74,26,“Posachedwa ndimlowetsa ku ‘Saqara.’
  74,27,“Nanga ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za ‘Saqara?’
  74,28,“(Ndi moto umene) siusiya (mnofu) ndiponso siusiya (fupa)
  74,29,“Wopsereza ndi kudetsa khungu
  74,30,“Kumeneko kuli khumi ndi asanu ndi anayi (alonda oyang’anira Motowo)
  74,31,"“Ndipo sitidaike oyang’anira ku Moto (kukhala anthu) koma angelo; ndipo sitidaike chiwerengero chawo koma ndimayesero kwa amene sadakhulupirire, kuti atsimikize amene adapatsidwa mabuku (zimene Qur’an ikunena za chiwerengero cha angelo a ku Moto) ndiponso kuti chionjezeke chikhulupiliro kwa amene akhulupirira, ndikuti asapeneke amene adapatsidwa mabuku pamodzi ndi okhulupirira. Ndiponso kuti amene m’mitima mwawo muli matenda (matenda achinyengo) komanso osakhulupirira anene: “Kodi Allah akulinganji pa fanizo limeneli?” Momwemo Allah akumulekelera kusokera amene wamfuna, ndipo akumuongola amene wamfuna ndipo palibe amene angadziwe magulu a nkhondo a Mbuye wako kupatula Iye mwini. (Kutchula moto ndi zam’kati mwake) sichina koma ndichenjezo kwa anthu"
  74,32,“Sichoncho; ndikulumbilira mwezi
  74,33,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuchoka
  74,34,“Ndi m’bandakucha pamene kukuyera
  74,35,"“Ndithu uwo, (moto wa Jahannam) ndi chimodzi mwa malodza akulu"
  74,36,“Ndi chenjezo kwa anthu
  74,37,“Kwa yemwe wafuna mwa inu kutsogola (pochita zabwino zokamthandiza tsiku louka kwa akufa) kapena kutsalira (ndi za m’dziko)
  74,38,“Mzimu uliwonse ukakhala chikole ndi zimene udachita
  74,39,“Kupatula akudzanja lamanja (Asilamu amene adadzimasula okha potembenukira kwa Allah)
  74,40,“(Iwo) adzakhala m’minda (yosasimbika kukongola kwake) akufunsana wina ndi mnzake
  74,41,“Za anthu oipa
  74,42,"“(Kuti): “Nchiyani chakulowetsani ku Moto?”"
  74,43,"“Adzanena: “Sitidali m’gulu la omwe adali kupemphera (Swala)"
  74,44,“Ndiponso sitidali kuwadyetsa masikini
  74,45,“Koma tinkangomira (m’zachabe ndi zabodza) pamodzi ndi omira (m’menemo)
  74,46,“Ndiponso tidali kutsutsa za tsiku la malipiro
  74,47,“Mpaka imfa idatifika.”
  74,48,“Choncho siwudzawathandiza uwomboli wa awomboli
  74,49,“Kodi ali ndi chiyani iwo pakuti azinyozera chenjezoli (limene lili Qur’an)
  74,50,“(Akuyenda mothamanga kuti asamve chenjezoli) ngati kuti iwo ndi mbidzi zothawa
  74,51,“(Zimene) zikuthawa mkango
  74,52,"“Ati akufuna aliyense mwa iwo apatsidwe kalata zotambasulidwa (zimene zitsimikize uthenga wa Mneneri Muhammad{s.a.w)"
  74,53,“Sichoncho! Koma kuti iwo sakuopa tsiku lachimaliziro
  74,54,“Sichoncho! Ndithu ichi (Qur’an) ndichikumbutso (chokwanira)
  74,55,“Choncho amene wafuna achikumbukire (amene sakufuna ndizake)
  74,56,"“Ndipo sangakumbukire pokhapokha Allah atafuna. Iye ndiye Amene ali woyenera kumuopa, ndiponso ndiye Mwini kukhululukira (amene akumuopa)"
  75,1,“Ndikulumbilira tsiku lachimaliziro
  75,2,“Ndikulumbiliranso mzimu wodzidzudzula (pa cholakwa chimene wachita. Ndithu mudzaukitsidwa; mafupa anu omwazikana atasonkhanitsidwa)
  75,3,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti Ife (Amene tidamlenga kuchokera popanda chilichonse) sitidzatha kusonkhanitsa mafupa ake (ofumbwa)
  75,4,"“Iyayi, Ife tikhoza (kutisonkhanitsa) ndi kutilongosola bwino timizere takunsonga kwa zala zake. (Mafupa ake ndiye osanena)"
  75,5,“Koma munthu akufuna kuti apitirize kuchimwa (mmasiku akudza) mtsogolo mwake
  75,6,"“Akufunsa (mwa chipongwe): “Kodi lidzakhala liti tsiku la chimaliziro?”"
  75,7,“Pamene maso adzangoti tong’oo (ndi mantha)
  75,8,“Ndi kuchoka kuwala kwa mwezi
  75,9,“Ndipo dzuwa ndi mwezi ndikusonkhanitsidwa
  75,10,"“Munthu adzanena tsiku limenelo: “Nkuti kothawira (chilangochi?)”"
  75,11,"“(Adzauzidwa): “Iyayi, (iwe munthu) palibe pothawira (pako)!”"
  75,12,“Tsiku limenelo kobwerera (anthu) ndi kwa Mbuye wako basi
  75,13,“Tsiku limenelo munthu adzauzidwa zochita zake zimene adazitsogoza ndi zimene adazichedwetsa
  75,14,“Koma munthu adzadzichitira umboni yekha pa mzimu wake
  75,15,“Ngakhale atapereka madandaulo ake (otani kuti apulumuke nawo sadzapulumuka)
  75,16,“Usaigwedezere (Qur’an) lirime lako (pamene ikuvumbulutsidwa) kuti uifulumilire (kuiwerenga ndi kuisunga mu mtima)
  75,17,“Ndithu ndiudindo wathu kuisonkhanitsa (mu mtima mwako) ndi kukhazikitsa kawerengedwe kake (palirime lako)
  75,18,“Choncho pamene tikukuwerengera iwe tsatira kuwerenga kwakeko (uku uli chete)
  75,19,"“Kenako, ndithu ndiudindo Wathu kulongosola (zimene siukumvetsa)"
  75,20,“Iyayi koma mukukonda moyo wa pa dziko
  75,21,“Ndipo mukusiya moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro
  75,22,“Nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zowala
  75,23,“Zili kumuyang’ana Mbuye wawo
  75,24,“Ndipo nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zoziya (zokhwinyata)
  75,25,“Zikuyembekezeka kuti zilandira tsoka lodula msana
  75,26,"“Sichoncho! Pamene mzimu udzafika pa nthitimtima, (pomwe pakumana mafupa am’mapewa)"
  75,27,“Ndipo ndikunenedwa ndani angamchiritse
  75,28,"“Ndipo (iye mwini wake), nkutsimikiza kuti ndithu uku ndikusiyana (ndi dziko lapansi)"
  75,29,“Ndipo miyendo idzasanjikizana; (iyi ndi nthawi yochoka mzimu)
  75,30,“Tsiku limenelo koperekedwa (anthu onse) nkwa Mbuye wako
  75,31,“Ndipo sadakhulupirire komanso sadapemphere Swala (zisanu)
  75,32,“Koma (m’malo mwake) adatsutsa ndi kunyoza
  75,33,“Kenaka adapita kubanja lake (uku akuyenda) monyada
  75,34,“Kuonongeka nkwako (iwe wotsutsa)! Kuonongeka zedi
  75,35,“Ndiponso kuonongeka nkwako! kuonongeka zedi
  75,36,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti angosiidwa chabe? (Sadzaweruzidwa)
  75,37,“Kodi sadali dontho la umuna umene udafwamphukira (m’chiberekero)
  75,38,"“Kenako adakhala nthinthi (ntchintchi) ya magazi, ndipo adamlenga ndi kumlinganiza (monga munthu)"
  75,39,"“Ndipo adalenga kuchokera mmenemo mitundu iwiri: mwamuna ndi mkazi"
  75,40,“Kodi (Iye amene adayambitsa chilengedwe choyambachi) sangathe kuwapatsa moyo akufa
  76,1,“Ndithu munthu idampita nthawi yaitali kwambiri (asanauziridwe mzimu) pomwe sadali chinthu chotchulidwa
  76,2,“Ndithu Ife tamlenga munthu kuchokera ku mbewu ya munthu yosakanikirana (ya mkazi ndi ya mwamuna) kuti timuyese mayeso (ndi malamulo Athu); choncho tidampanga kukhala wakumva ndi wopenya; (amve mawu a Allah ndi kuti aone zisonyezo Zake)
  76,3,"“Ndithu Ife tidamlongosolera njira yoongoka: kukhala wokhulupirira kapena wotsutsa (Zonse zili kwa iye)"
  76,4,“Ndithu Ife okana tawakonzera unyolo (wam’miyendo yawo) ndi magoli (am’manja ndi m’makosi awo) ndi Moto waukali woyaka
  76,5,"“Ndithu ochita zabwino adzamwa vinyo, chosakanizira chake chidzakhala (madzi a) kaafura"
  76,6,“(Kaafura ameneyo) ndikasupe amene adzikamwapo akapolo a Allah ndi kumtulutsa (paliponse pamene afuna) kumtulutsa mofewa
  76,7,"“(Amene) akukwaniritsa zimene adalonjeza (okha kwa Allah), ndiponso akuopa tsiku (lalikulu) limene zoipa zake zidzakhala zofalikira ponseponse"
  76,8,"“Ndipo amadyetsa chakudya masikini, amasiye ndi ogwidwa pa nkhondo, pomwe iwo akuchifunanso"
  76,9,"“Amanena (chamumtima akamapereka chakudyacho): “Tikukudyetsani chifukwa chofuna chikondi cha Allah basi; sitikufuna kwa inu malipiro kapena kuthokoza"
  76,10,“Ndithu ife tikuopa kwa Mbuye wathu tsiku lokhwinyata nkhope ndi mavuto akulu.”
  76,11,“Ndipo Allah adzawateteza mu mavuto a tsiku limenelo ndiponso adzawapatsa mtendere ndi chisangalalo
  76,12,“Ndipo adzawalipira chifukwa cha kupirira kwawo Munda wamtendere ndi nsalu zaveleveti
  76,13,“Atatsamira m’menemo pa makama (amtengo wapatali); sadzamva m’menemo kutentha kwa dzuwa kapena kuzizira
  76,14,“Mithunzi yake ikawayandikira iwo ndipo mikoko yazipatso idzatewa pafupi (moti munthu atha kuthyola ali chigonere)
  76,15,“Ndipo adzakhala akuzunguliridwa (ndi otumikira) uku atatenga zomwera za siliva ndi matambula onyezimira ndiponso olangala
  76,16,"“Zolangala zopangidwa ku siliva, atalinga bwino zakumwazo (malinga ndi kufuna kwawo)"
  76,17,"“Ndipo (anthu abwino) akamwetsedwa kumeneko vinyo, chosakanizira chake chikafanana ndi Zanjabila (chikasu)"
  76,18,“M’menemo muli kasupe wotchedwa Salisabila
  76,19,"“Ndipo azikawazungulira anyamata osasinthika (chilengedwe chawo,) utawaona (chifukwa cha kukongola kwawo ndi kuwala kwa nkhope zawo) ungawaganizire kuti ndi ngale zomwazidwa"
  76,20,“Ndipo ukadzaona kumeneko (ku Jannah) ukaona mtendere ndi ufumu waukulu
  76,21,"“Pamwamba pawo padzakhala nsalu zaveleveti zopyapyala, zobiriwira ndi nsalu zaveleveti zochindikala, akavekedwa m’manja mwawo zibangiri zasiliva; Mbuye wawo akawamwetsa chakumwa china choyera kwambiri"
  76,22,"“(Akawauza kuti:) “Ndithu iyi ndi mphoto yanu ndipo ntchito zanu ndi zolandiridwa.”"
  76,23,"“Ndithu Ife taivumbulutsa kwa iwe Qur’an mwapang’onopang’ono (kuti uisunge bwino, usaiwale)"
  76,24,"“Choncho, pirira ndi lamulo la Mbuye wako ndipo usamvere wamachimo kapena wokanira aliyense mwa iwo"
  76,25,"“Ndipo kumbukira dzina la Mbuye wako; mmawa, ndi madzulo (Swala za Subuhi, Dhuhr ndi Asri)"
  76,26,"“Ndipo usiku mlambire Iye, (Swala ya Maghrib ndi Isha); ndiponso umulemekeze usiku nthawi yaitali (popemphera sunna za tahajjudi)"
  76,27,"“Ndithu awa akukonda moyo wa dziko lapansi, ndipo akulisiya kumbuyo kwao tsiku lovuta"
  76,28,“Ife ndi amene tidawalenga ndipo tidalimbika kalengedwe kawo; ndipo titafuna tingabweretse ena onga iwo (omvera Allah) kulowa m’malo mwawo
  76,29,“Ndithu ichi ndichikumbutso choncho amene afuna atsata njira yopitira kwa Mbuye wake (pomukhulupirira ndi kumumvera)
  76,30,"“Koma simungafune nokha chilichonse pokhapokha atafuna Allah, ndithu Allah ndi Wodziwa zedi, Wanzeru zakuya"
  76,31,“Akumlowetsa amene wamfuna ku chifundo Chake; koma oyipa wawalinganizira chilango chowawa kwambiri
  77,1,“Ndikulumbilira mphepo yomwe ikuomba motsatizana
  77,2,“Ndi mphepo yamkuntho ikamakuntha
  77,3,“Ndi mphepo yobalalitsa mitambo ndi mvula
  77,4,“Ndi ma Ayah osiyanitsa pakati pachoona ndi chonama
  77,5,“Ndi angelo opereka chivumbulutso kwa aneneri
  77,6,“Kuti chichotse madandaulo kapena chikhale chenjezo
  77,7,“Ndithu zimene mukulonjezedwa (kuti chimaliziro chidzakhalapo) zidzachitikadi (popanda chipeneko)
  77,8,“Pamene nyenyezi zidzafafanizidwa (kuwala kwake ndi kuchotsedwa m’malo mwake)
  77,9,“Ndiponso pamene thambo lidzang‘ambidwa
  77,10,“Ndi pamenenso mapiri adzachotsedwa m’malo mwake ndi kuperedwa (kukhala fumbi)
  77,11,"“Ndi pamene atumiki adzasonkhanitsidwa pa nthawi yake, (kuti apereke umboni ku mibadwo yawo)"
  77,12,“Kodi nditsiku lanji azichedwetsera (zinthu zikuluzikulu kuti zidzachitike)
  77,13,“Nditsiku loweruza (pakati pa zolengedwa)
  77,14,“Nchiyani chingakudziwitse za tsiku la chiweruzirolo
  77,15,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (lonjezo Lathu lakuuka ku imfa)
  77,16,"“Kodi sitidawaononge (anthu) akale (chifukwa cha machimo awo, monga anthu a Nuh, Âdi ndi Samudu)"
  77,17,“Kenako titsatiza ena (okana Allah m’kuonongekako monga tidawachitira oyamba)
  77,18,“Chomwecho tiwachitiranso ochimwa
  77,19,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (lonjezo Lathu lakuuka ku imfa)
  77,20,"“Kodi sitidakulengeni kuchokera ku madzi onyozeka, (madzi ambewu ya munthu)"
  77,21,“Kenako tidawaika pamalo okhazikika (kuti chilengedwe chake chikwanire pamenepo)
  77,22,“Mpaka nyengo yodziwika (imene tidaipima kuti mwana abadwe)
  77,23,“Tidaipima nyengoyo; taonani kupima bwino Ife opima
  77,24,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (lonjezo Lathu lakuuka ku imfa)
  77,25,“Kodi sitidaichite nthaka kukhala yofungatira
  77,26,“Amoyo ndi akufa
  77,27,"“Ndipo tidaika m’menemo mapiri ataliatali (olimbitsa nthaka), ndipo takumwetsani madzi okoma"
  77,28,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (lonjezo Lathu lakuuka ku imfa)
  77,29,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa okana tsiku la chimaliziro:) Pitani kuzimene mudali kuzitsutsa zija"
  77,30,“Pitani kumthunzi (wautsi wa ku Moto) wa nthambi zitatu
  77,31,“Simthunzi (wamtendere) ndiponso siwotchinjiriza ku malawi a Moto.”
  77,32,“Ndithu motowo umaponya mphalikira (mbaliwali) zazikulu ngati nyumba
  77,33,“Zonga ngati ngamira zachikasu
  77,34,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (zimenezi)
  77,35,“Ili ndi tsiku lomwe sadzayankhula
  77,36,“Ndipo sadzapatsidwa chilolezo (choyankhulira) kuti apereke madandaulo awo
  77,37,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (za tsiku limenelo)
  77,38,"“(Adzauzidwa kuti): Ili ndi tsiku loweruza (pakati pa abwino ndi oipa takusonkhanitsani inu (otsutsa Muhammad {s.a.w}), ndi akale (otsutsa aneneri akale)"
  77,39,“Ngati muli ndi ndale (yodzipulumutsira ku chilango Changa) ndichiteni ndaleyo
  77,40,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (lonjezo la Allah)
  77,41,“Ndithu oopa (Allah tsiku limenelo) adzakhala mu mthunzi ndi mitsinje
  77,42,“Ndipo adzakhala ndi zipatso zomwe azidzazifuna
  77,43,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa iwo): “Idyani, imwani mokondwa chifukwa cha zabwino zomwe mudali kuchita (mu moyo wa dziko lapansi)"
  77,44,“Ndithu umo ndi mmene Ife timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  77,45,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (mtendere wa Allah)
  77,46,"“Idyani, sangalalani pang’ono m’kanthawi kochepa; ndithu inu ndinu ochimwa (chifukwa chakumphatikiza Allah ndi zolengedwa)"
  77,47,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (mtendere wa Allah)
  77,48,"“Ndipo kukanenedwa kwa iwo: “Weramani, (pembedzani Allah).” sawerengera"
  77,49,“Kuonongeka kwakukulu tsiku limenelo kuli pa otsutsa (malamulo a Allah)
  77,50,“Kodi ndi nkhani iti imene adzaikhulupirira pambuyo pa Iyi (Qur’an)
  78,1,“۞ Kodi akufunsana zachiyani
  78,2,“Za nkhani yayikulu ija
  78,3,“Imene iwo akusiyana (maganizo)
  78,4,“Aleke (zimenezo) adzadziwa posachedwapa
  78,5,"“Ayi, ndithu aleke (zimenezo); posachedwapa adzadziwa zoona zake (pamene chilango chidzawatsikira)"
  78,6,“Kodi sitidachite nthaka kukhala ngati choyala
  78,7,“Ndi mapiri ngati zichiri (zolimbitsa nthaka)
  78,8,“Ndipo takulengani mitundu iwiri (amuna ndi akazi)
  78,9,“Ndipo tidachita tulo tanu kukhala mpumulo (ku mavuto a ntchito)
  78,10,“Ndipo taupanga usiku kukhala ngati chovala (pokuvindikirani ndi mdima wake)
  78,11,“Ndipo tapanga masana kukhala nthawi yopezera zofunika pa moyo
  78,12,“Ndipo tamanga pamwamba panu thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri zolimba
  78,13,“Ndipo tidapanga nyali yowala ndi yotentha kwambiri (dzuwa)
  78,14,"“Ndipo tawatsitsa madzi otsika mwamphamvu kuchokera ku mitambo, ya mvula"
  78,15,"“Kuti titulutse ndi madziwo mbewu ndi m’mera, (chomwe ndi chakudya cha anthu ndi nyama)"
  78,16,“Ndi minda yothothana nthambi za mitengo
  78,17,“Ndithu tsiku la chiweruziro ndinthawi imene idakhazikitsidwa kale
  78,18,“Tsiku limene lipenga (lakuuka) lidzaimbidwa ndipo inu mudzabwera (kubwalo losonkhanirana) muli magulumagulu
  78,19,"“Ndipo thambo lidzatsegulidwa (mbali zonse): choncho lidzakhala makomomakomo"
  78,20,"“Ndipo mapiri adzachotsedwa m’malo mwake, adzakhala ngati zideruderu"
  78,21,“Ndithu moto wa Jahannam ukuwadikilira (oipa)
  78,22,“Mbuto ya opyola malire
  78,23,“Adzakhala m’menemo muyaya
  78,24,"“Sadzalawa m’menemo kuzizira (kowachotsera kutentha), kapena chakumwa (chowachotsera ludzu lawo)"
  78,25,“Kupatula madzi otentha kwambiri ndi mafinya (otuluka mmatupi a anthu a ku Moto)
  78,26,“Kukhala malipiro olingana ndi ntchito zawo
  78,27,“Ndithu iwo sadali kuyembekezera chiwerengero (cha Allah)
  78,28,“Adatsutsa zizindikiro Zathu (zosonyeza kuuka kwa akufa) ndi mtsutso waukulu
  78,29,“Ndipo chinthu chilichonse tachisunga mochilemba
  78,30,"“Basi, lawani (lero chilango Changa); sitikuonjezerani chinthu china koma chilango pamwamba pa chilango"
  78,31,“Ndithu anthu oopa Allah adzakhala ndi malo wopambana
  78,32,“Minda ndi zipatso za mphesa
  78,33,“Ndi mabuthu (anamwali) ofanana misinkhu
  78,34,“Ndi zipanda zodzaza ndi zakumwa
  78,35,“Sakamva m’menemo mawu opanda pake kapena bodza
  78,36,“Amenewa ndi malipiro ochokera kwa Mbuye wako zopereka zokwanira
  78,37,“Mbuye wa kumwamba ndi pansi ndi zimene zili pakati pake; Wachifundo chambiri. Palibe amene adzakhala ndi mphamvu yolankhulana naye (pa tsiku limenero)
  78,38,“Tsiku limene adzaima Jibril ndi angelo pa mzere (ali odzichepetsa); sadzayankhula aliyense mwa iwo kupatula yekhayo amene adzaloledwa ndi (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri (kuyankhula) ndipo adzanena zolondola
  78,39,"“Limenelo ndi tsiku loona, (lopanda chikaiko); choncho amene akufuna adzipezere malo (njira yonkera) kwa Mbuye wake. (Pomugonjera Iye pa moyo uno wadziko lapansi)"
  78,40,"“Ndithu tikukuchenjezani zachilango chomwe chili pafupi kudza; tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana zimene adatsogoza manja ake, ndipo wosakhulupirira adzanena: Kalanga ine! Ndikadakhala dothi, (kuti ndisalangidwe chilango chikundiyembekezachi)"
  79,1,“Ndikulumbilira (angelo) amene amazula mwamphamvu (mizimu ya osakhulupirira)
  79,2,“Ndikulumbiliranso (angelo) amene amachotsa moleza (mizimu ya okhulupirira)
  79,3,“Ndi omwe amasambira (nayo mizimuyo) mu mlengalenga (ponka nayo ku malo ake oyembekezera)
  79,4,“Ndi iwo amene akupikisana pokwaniritsa malamulo a Allah
  79,5,“Ndi iwo (angelo) amene akulongosola malamulo (Ake). (Ndithudi inu anthu mudzauka kwa akufa)
  79,6,"“Patsiku lomwe (lipenga loyamba lidzaimbidwa), dziko lapansi ndi mapiri ake zidzagwedezeka (ndipo aliyense adzafa)"
  79,7,“Ndipo kudzatsatira kuyimba kwa lipenga lachiwiri (kumene kudzaukitsa akufa onse)
  79,8,“Tsiku limenelo mitima idzanjenjemera ndi kuopa
  79,9,“Maso a eni mitimayo adzakhala ozyolika (chifukwa chamadandaulo)
  79,10,"“(Osakhulupirira) akunena: “Kodi nzoona tidzabwezedwa pambuyo pa imfa monga tidalili kale?”"
  79,11,““Pomwe ife titakhala mafupa ofumbwa (tingabwezedwe ndi kuukitsidwa mwa tsopano)?”
  79,12,"“Adanena (mokanira ndi mwachipongwe): “Choncho kubwerera kumeneko ngati kudzakhalepodi kudzakhala kotaika (ndi kopanda phindu kwa ife. Pomwe ife sindife oyenera kutaika).”"
  79,13,“(Musaganize kubwererako nchinthu chovuta). Ndithundithu Kiyamayo ndi nkuwo umodzi
  79,14,“Mwadzidzidzi (zolengedwa zonse) zidzangoona zili pa dziko latsopano (zili zamoyo)
  79,15,“Kodi yakufika (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w) nkhani ya Mûsa
  79,16,“Pamene Mbuye wake adamuitana pa chigwa choyera (chotchedwa) Tuwaa
  79,17,"“(Adamuuza kuti) pita kwa Farawo ndithu iye wapyola malire, (mkudzitukumula kwake ndikupondereza anthu)"
  79,18,"“Choncho ukamuuze kuti: “Kodi ukufuna kudziyeretsa?”"
  79,19,““Ndikuti ndikuongolere kwa Mbuye wako kuti uzimuopa?”
  79,20,“(Basi Mûsa) adamuonetsa (Farawo) chozizwitsa chachikulu
  79,21,“Koma (Farawo) adatsutsa (Mûsa pazimene adadza nazo zija) ndi kunyoza
  79,22,“Kenaka adabwerera uku akulimbika kutsutsana naye (Allah)
  79,23,“Adawasonkhanitsa (afiti) uku akuitana anthu
  79,24,"“Nanena: “Ine ndine mbuye wanu wapamwambamwamba!”"
  79,25,“Pamenepo Allah adamulanga chifukwa cha mawu ake omaliza ndi oyamba
  79,26,“Ndithu pa zimenezi pali phunziro (lalikulu) kwa yemwe akuopa Allah
  79,27,"“Kodi kulengedwa kwanu, (inu osakhulupirira kuti muuke) nkovuta kapena thambo limene adalimanga (posonkhanitsa mbali zake zosiyanasiyana ndikukhala chinthu chimodzi)"
  79,28,“Adatukula nsinkhu wake ndikulikonza bwino (popanda pena pong’ambika kapena posiyana ndi pena)
  79,29,“Ndipo amauvindikira usiku wake ndi mdima ndipo amatulutsa kuwala wake
  79,30,"“Ndipo pambuyo pazimenezo, nthaka adaiyala (kuti ikhale yoyenera kuikhala)"
  79,31,“Adatulutsa m’menemo madzi ake (potulutsa akasupe) ndikumeretsa msipu wake
  79,32,“Ndipo mapiri adawakhazikitsa (ndikuwalimbika)
  79,33,“(Adachita zonsezi) chifukwa chokusangalatsani inu ndi ziweto zanu
  79,34,“Choncho likadzafika tsoka lalikulu (tsiku la Qiyâma)
  79,35,"“Tsiku limenelo munthu adzakumbukira zimene adachita, (zabwino ndi zoipa)"
  79,36,“Ndipo Moto waukali udzawonetsedwa kwa yense openya
  79,37,“Tsono amene adapyola malire (pochita machimo)
  79,38,“Ndikudzisankhira (yekha) moyo wa pa dziko lapansi
  79,39,“Ndithu Jahannam ndiwo malo ake
  79,40,"“Tsono amene akuopa kuti adzaimilira pamaso pa Mbuye wake, nauletsa mtima wake ku zilakolako zoipa"
  79,41,“Ndithu Munda wamtendere ndiwo adzakhale malo ake
  79,42,"“Akukufunsa (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w) za nthawi (ya tsiku lachimaliziro kuti): “Idzakhala liti?”"
  79,43,“Uli ndi mphamvu yanji iwe yofotokozera za tsikulo? (Iwe ulibe kuzindikira za nthawiyo kotero kuti ungaitchule kwa iwo)
  79,44,“Kwa Mbuye wako ndiko kuli mathero ake
  79,45,“Iwe (ntchito yako) ndikuwachenjeza amene akuiopa; (osati kulengeza zanthawi yake)
  79,46,"“Tsiku limene adzaiona adzakhala ngati sadakhale (pa dziko nthawi yayitali), koma ngati madzulo amodzi kapena masana ake (nthawi ya m’mawa)"
  80,1,“Adachita tsinya (Mneneri) ndi kuyang’ana kumbali
  80,2,“Chifukwa chakuti adamdzera wakhungu (kudzamfunsa zokhudzana ndi chipembedzo chake pamene iye adali kuyankhula ndi atsogoleri Achiquraishi)
  80,3,“Nanga chingakudziwitse nchiyani kuti mwina iye angadziyeretse (pomvera ulaliki wako watsopano)
  80,4,"“Kapena akumbukira, ndipo kukumbukirako kumthandiza"
  80,5,“Koma amene wadzikwaniritsa (ndi chuma chake ndi mphamvu zake)
  80,6,“Ameneyo ndi yemwe ukumchitira chidwi
  80,7,“Palibe chilichonse pa iwe ngati sadziyeretsa
  80,8,“Koma amene wakudzera uku akuthamanga (kufuna maphunziro ndi chiongoko)
  80,9,“Ndipo iye akuopa (Allah mu mtima mwake)
  80,10,"“Za iye, iwe sukusamala, (ukuyikira chidwi kwa wina)"
  80,11,“Sichoncho! Ndithudi iyi (Qur’an) ndi chikumbutso (chenjezo)
  80,12,"“Basi, amene wafuna alangizika (ndi Qur’an, ndipo amene sakufuna msiye)"
  80,13,“(Malangizowa akuchokera) mmakalata olemekezeka (kwa Allah)
  80,14,“Apamwamba ndiponso oyeretsedwa (kumbiri iliyonse yopunguka)
  80,15,“Omwe ali m’manja mwa Alembi (Angelo)
  80,16,"“Olemekezeka, omvera"
  80,17,“Waonongeka (watembeleredwa) munthu. Nkotani kusayamika kwake kotereku
  80,18,“Kuchokera mchinthu chanji chimene iye adamulenga
  80,19,"“Kuchokera ku dontho lamadzi (onyozeka) adamulenga, namkonzeratu mkalengedwe kosiyanasiyana"
  80,20,“Kenako adamfewetsera njira (yotulukira m’mimba mwa mai ake)
  80,21,“Ndipo amamchititsa kuti amwalire namukumbula m’manda
  80,22,“Kenako akadzafuna adzamuukitsa (pambuyo pa imfa)
  80,23,“Ayi ndithu (munthu) sanakwaniritsebe zimene adamulamula Mbuye wake (Allah chingakhale wakhala nthawi yaitali pa dziko lapansi)
  80,24,“Alingalire munthu (mmene chilili) chakudya chake
  80,25,“Ndithu Ife timagwetsa mvula yambiri (kuchokera ku mitambo)
  80,26,“Kenako timaing’amba nthaka kuti mmera utuluke
  80,27,“Ndipo timameretsa m’menemo njere (ya chakudya cha anthu ndi zina zimene amasunga mnkhokwe)
  80,28,“Ndi mphesa ndi msipu
  80,29,“Ndi mzitona (wabwino) ndi (zipatso za) kanjedza
  80,30,“Ndi minda yothothana nthambi za mitengo
  80,31,“Ndi zipatso (zodyedwa ndi anthu) ndi msipu (wodyedwa ndi nyama)
  80,32,“(Tazimeretsa zimenezo kuti) zikondweretse inu ndi ziweto zanu
  80,33,“Choncho likadzafika lipenga logonthetsa mkhutu (ndi kuumitsa makosi)
  80,34,“Patsikuli munthu adzathawa m’bale wake
  80,35,“Mayi wake ndi bambo wake
  80,36,“Mkazi wake ndi ana ake
  80,37,"“Munthu aliyense mwa iwo, tsiku limenelo adzakhala ndi zakezake zotangwanika nazo. (Sadzalabadira za anzake)"
  80,38,“Tsiku limenelo nkhope zina zidzakhala zowala
  80,39,“Zosekelera ndi zachimwemwe (chifukwa cha nkhani yabwino ya ku Munda wamtendere)
  80,40,“Ndipo nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zokutidwa ndi fumbi
  80,41,“Mdima udzazikuta
  80,42,“Iwo ndi anthu osakhulupirira oipa (olakwira Allah)
  81,1,“Pamene dzuwa lidzakulungidwe (ndikuchotsedwa kuwala kwake)
  81,2,“Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzathothoke (ndi kuchoka dangalira lake)
  81,3,“Ndi pamene mapiri adzayendetsedwe (kuchoka mmalo mwake)
  81,4,“Ndi pamene ngamira zabere lamiyezi khumi zidzasiidwe (zopanda oziyang’anira)
  81,5,“Ndi pamene nyama za mtchire zidzasonkhanitsidwe pamodzi (kuchokera mmalo osiyanasiyana chifukwa chakuopsa kwakukulu kwa tsikulo)
  81,6,“Ndi pamene nyanja zidzayatsidwe moto
  81,7,“Ndi pamene mizimu idzalumikizidwe (ndi matupi ake)
  81,8,“Ndi pamene mwana wamkazi yemwe adaikidwa m’manda wamoyo adzafunsidwe
  81,9,“Ndi tchimo lanji adaphedwera
  81,10,“Ndi pamene makalata (momwe mudalembedwa zochita za aliyense) adzatambasulidwe ndi kugawidwa (kuti awerengedwe)
  81,11,“Ndi pamene thambo lidzayalulidwe (kuchoka mmalo mwake)
  81,12,“Ndi pamene Jahena idzasonkhezeredwe mwamphamvu
  81,13,“Ndi pamene Jannah idzayandikitsidwe
  81,14,“(Zikadzachitika zimenezi) mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa zimene wabweretsa (zabwino ndi zoipa)
  81,15,“Ndikulumbilira nyenyezi zimene zimabwerera masana ndi kutulukanso usiku
  81,16,“Zomwe zimayenda kenako nkubisika
  81,17,“Ndi usiku pamene ukulowa
  81,18,“Ndi m’mawa kukamacha
  81,19,“Ndithu iyi (Qur’an) ndi liwu la mthenga wa Allah (Jibril) wolemekezeka
  81,20,“Mwini mphamvu ndi mwini ulemelero kwa Mwini Arsh (Mpando wa chifumu)
  81,21,“Womveredwa kumeneko ndiponso wokhulupirika (pachivumbulutso)
  81,22,“Ndipo m’bale wanuyu siwamisala ayi
  81,23,“Ndithu ndikulumbira kuti (iye Mtumiki) (s.a.w) adamuona (Jibril) mchizimezime (chakum’mawa) chooneka bwino
  81,24,“Ndipo sali iye (Mtumiki) waumbombo ndi chivumbulutso (koma amafikitsa zonse ndi kuziphunzitsa kwa anthu)
  81,25,“(Chivumbulutso chomwe chavumbulutsidwachi kwa iye) si mawu a satana wothamangitsidwa (mchifundo cha Allah)
  81,26,“Nanga mukupita kuti
  81,27,“(Qur’ani) iyi sichina koma ndi chikumbutso cha zolengedwa zonse
  81,28,“Kwa yemwe mwa inu akufuna kuyenda mu njira yoongoka
  81,29,“Ndipo simungafune chinthu mwa inu nokha pokhapokha atafuna Allah Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  82,1,“Pamene thambo lidzasweke
  82,2,“Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzayoyoke (ndi kumwazikana)
  82,3,“Pamenenso nyanja zikuluzikulu zidzaphwasulidwe
  82,4,“Ndiponso pamene manda adzafukulidwe (ndikutuluka akufa omwe adali mmenemo)
  82,5,“(Panthawiyo) mzimu uliwonse udzadziwa zimene udatsogoza (zabwino ndi zoipa) ndi zimene udasiya m’mbuyo
  82,6,“E iwe munthu! Nchiani chakunyenga kumsiya Mbuye wako wa ufulu (kufikira pomnyoza)
  82,7,“Amene adalenga iwe nakulinganiza (ziwalo zako) ndi kukulongosola (moyenera)
  82,8,“Ndipo maonekedwe amtundu uliwonse omwe adawafuna adakuveka (popanda chifuniro chako)
  82,9,"“Ayi, sichoncho! Koma inu mukutsutsa za (tsiku) lamalipiro"
  82,10,“Ndithu pa inu alipo okuyang’ anirani
  82,11,"“Olemekezeka, olemba (zochita zanu)"
  82,12,“Akudziwa (zonse) zimene mukuchita (zabwino ndi zoipa)
  82,13,“Ndithudi ochita zabwino adzakhala mu mtendere
  82,14,“Ndipo ndithu amene ali olakwira malamulo a Allah adzakhala ku Moto wopsereza
  82,15,“Adzaulowa tsiku la malipiro
  82,16,“Ndipo iwo kumeneko sadzachokako
  82,17,“Kodi nchiyani chingakudziwitse za tsiku la malipiro
  82,18,“Ndipo nchiyani chingakudziwitse za tsiku lamalipiro
  82,19,“Limeneli ndi tsiku limene mzimu uliwonse sudzakhala ndi mphamvu (yodzetsa mtendere kapena yochotsa chovuta) pa mzimu wina. Ndipo lamulo pa tsiku limeneli ndi la Allah yekha
  83,1,“Kuonongeka koopsa kukawapeza opunguza miyeso ya malonda
  83,2,“Amene amati akamadziyezera zinthu kwa anthu amafuna kulandira miyeso yodzadza
  83,3,“Koma pamene iwo akamawayesera pa muyeso wa mbale kapena wa sikelo amapungula (choyenera kulandira ogulawo)
  83,4,“Kodi amenewa (akupungula miyeso pamalondawo) sakuganiza kuti adzaukitsidwa
  83,5,“Pa tsiku lalikulu (ndiponso loopsa)
  83,6,“Tsiku limene adzaimilira anthu pamaso pa Mbuye wa zolengedwa
  83,7,“Ayi! Ndithu (siyani chinyengo pamalonda ndi kusalabadira kuuka mmanda); zolembedwa za ntchito ya oipa zili mu Sijjin
  83,8,“Nanga nchiyani chitakudziwitse za Sijjin
  83,9,“Ameneyu ndi kaundula wamkulu yemwe walembedwa (mkati mwake ntchito za anthu oipa)
  83,10,“Chilango chaukali tsiku limenelo chili pa otsutsa
  83,11,“Amene akutsutsa za tsiku la malipiro
  83,12,"“Ndipo palibe angalitsutse koma yekhayo wopyola malire (pochita zoipa), wa machimo ambiri"
  83,13,"“Pamene ma Ayah Athu akuwerengedwa kwa iye (onena za tsiku la malipiro ndikuuka mmanda) amanena kuti: “Izi ndi nthano za anthu akale.”"
  83,14,"“Iyayi, sichoncho! Koma yaphimbidwa mitima yawo ndi dzimbiri (la machimo) omwe akhala akukolola"
  83,15,“Ayi ndithu iwo (okanira) tsiku limenelo) adzatchingidwa kwa Mbuye wawo; (sadzamuona)
  83,16,“Pambuyo pake adzalowa ku Moto; (oyaka)
  83,17,“Kenaka adzauzidwa (powaliritsa) “Ichi nchilango chomwe mudali kuchitsutsa (pa dziko lapansi).”
  83,18,"“Zoona, ndithu kaundula wa anthu abwino (ochita ntchito zabwino) ali mu Illiyyun"
  83,19,“Nanga nchiyani chitakudziwitse za Illiyyun
  83,20,“Ameneyu ndi kaundula (wamkulu) yemwe walembedwa (mkati mwake ntchito za anthu abwino)
  83,21,“Amamuyikira umboni (angelo) amene ayandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  83,22,“Ndithu ochita zabwino adzakhala mu mtendere
  83,23,“Atakhala pa mipando ya ulemu uku akuyang’ana (zimene Allah wawapatsa monga mtendere ndi ulemelero)
  83,24,“Udzaona kuwala kwa mtendere pa nkhope zawo
  83,25,“Adzamwetsedwa vinyo (woyeretsedwa) wotsekeredwa ndi zitsekerero zolimba
  83,26,"“Komalizira kwake (kwa vinyoyo) kuzikatuluka fungo la misk; kuti akapeze zimenezi, apikisane opikisana"
  83,27,“Ndipo chosakanizira cha vinyoyo ndi madzi a Tasnim
  83,28,“(Tasnim ameneyo) ndi kasupe amene azikamwa amene ayandikitsidwa (kwa Allah)
  83,29,“Ndithu amene adachita machimo adali kuwaseka (mwachipongwe) okhulupirira (pa dziko lapansi)
  83,30,“(Okhulupirira) akadutsa pafupi ndi iwo ankakodolerana maso (mwachipongwe)
  83,31,“Ndipo akabwerera kwa anzawo amabwerera akusangalala (ndi kunyozedwa kwa okhulupirira)
  83,32,"“Ndipo (nthawi zonse) akawaona Asilamu amanena: “Ndithu awa ndi osokera (chifukwa chomkhulupirira Mtumiki).” (s.a.w)"
  83,33,“Sanatumizidwe (Akafiri) kukhala ayang’aniri kwa okhulupirira (ndikuwaweruza zakulungama ndi kusokera)
  83,34,“Basi lero okhulupirira awaseka osakhulupirira (powabwezera chipongwe chawo chimene ankachita pa dziko lapansi)
  83,35,“Atakhala pa mipando ya ulemu uku akuyang’ana (mtendere umene Allah wawapatsa)
  83,36,“Kodi alipidwa osakhulupirira pa zomwe ankachita zija (pa dziko lapansi)
  84,1,Pamene thambo lidzang’ambike (kusonyeza mapeto ake)
  84,2,“Ndikudzamvera lamulo la Mbuye wake; ndipo lidzayenera kutero
  84,3,“Ndiponso pamene nthaka idzatambasulidwe (pogumuka mapiri ake ndikuchoka zitunda zake)
  84,4,“Ndi kutaya zomwe zidali mkati mwake ndi kukhala yopanda kanthu
  84,5,“Ndikudzamvera lamulo la Mbuye wake; ndipo lidzayenera kutero. (Choncho zikadzachitika zimenezi ndiye kuti munthu adzalandira mphoto ya zochita zake)
  84,6,"“E iwe munthu! Ndithudi iwe ukubwerera kwa Mbuye wako (ndi zochita zako zabwino kapena zoipa), kubwerera kotsimikizika, ndipo iwe ukumana (ndi zotsatira za zochitachita zako)"
  84,7,“Tsono amene adzapatsidwe kaundula wa zochita zake kudzanja la manja
  84,8,"“Basi iye, adzawerengedwa, kuwerengedwa kopepuka"
  84,9,“Ndipo adzabwerera kwa anthu ake (okhulupirira) ali wokondwa
  84,10,“Koma yemwe adzapatsidwe kaundula wa zochita zake chakumanzere kudzera kumbuyo kwa msana wake (chifukwa chomunyoza)
  84,11,"“Basi, iye adzaitana imfa (kuti imufikire; kuti afe apumule, koma siidzamufikira)"
  84,12,“Ndipo adzalowa ku Moto woyaka
  84,13,“Kamba kakuti iye adali wokondwa; (kukondwa kwa machimo) pamodzi ndi anthu ake (osaganizira za mathero ake)
  84,14,"“Ndithudi, amaganiza kuti sadzabwerera (kwa Allah ndiponso sadzawerengedwa)"
  84,15,“Chifukwa ninji (asabwelere)? Ndithu Mbuye wake adali kumuona. (Choncho alipidwa zimene adachita)
  84,16,“Choncho ndikulumbilira kufiira kwa dzuwa (pamene likulowa)
  84,17,“Ndi usiku ndi zimene wasonkhanitsa
  84,18,“Ndi mwezi ukakwanira dangalira (lake)
  84,19,“Ndithudi mudzachoka apa kunka apa (pa moyo uno mpakana umene uli nkudza)
  84,20,"“Kodi nchiyani chikuwaletsa iwo (okanira) kukhulupirira (Allah ndi kuuka kumanda, zisonyezo zake zitaonekera poyera)"
  84,21,"“Ndipo ikawerengedwa kwa iwo Qur’an, sagwetsa pansi nkhope zawo (modzichepetsa)"
  84,22,“Koma amene sadakhulupirire akutsutsa basi (chifukwa cha makani ndi kudzikweza)
  84,23,“Ndipo Allah akudziwa (bwinobwino) zimene akuzisonkhanitsa
  84,24,"“Choncho, auze nkhani yachilango chopweteka"
  84,25,"“Kupatula awo amene akhulupirira ndikuchita ntchito zabwino, kwa iwo kuli malipiro osatha"
  85,1,“Ndikulumbilira thambo lomwe liri ndi Buruj (Nyenyezi zikuluzikulu)
  85,2,“Ndi tsiku lolonjezedwa (kuwerengedwa ndi kulipidwa)
  85,3,"“Ndi woikira umboni, ndi woikiridwa umboni"
  85,4,"“Atembeleredwa eni ngalande zamoto (zomwe adali kuwazunzira okhulupirira Allah, achimuna ndi achikazi)"
  85,5,“(Ngalande) za moto wankhuni (zambiri zomwe adali kuzikoleza ndikuotchera okhulupirira)
  85,6,“Pamene iwo adali chikhalire m’mphepete mwa ngalandezo
  85,7,"“Uku iwo akuyang’ana zomwe amawachitira okhulupirira, (pootchedwa ndi moto)"
  85,8,“Sadaone choipa chilichonse mwa iwo koma chifukwa choti adakhulupirira Allah mwini mphamvu zonse ndiponso mwini kuyamikidwa
  85,9,“Yemwe ufumu wakumwamba ndi pansi ndiWake; ndipo Allah ndi mboni pachilichonse
  85,10,"“Ndithu amene ayesa mayeso okhulupirira achimuna ndi achikazi (pa chipembedzo chawo ndi mazunzo ndi chilango cha moto), pambuyo pake osalapa (pa zimenezi), adzalandira chilango cha Jahena ndiponso chilango cha moto wopsereza"
  85,11,"“Ndithudi amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino, adzakhala ndi Minda yamtendere (momwe) mitsinje ikuyenda pansi pake; kumeneko ndiko kupambana kwakukulu"
  85,12,"“Ndithu kulanga kwa Mbuye wako (kwa anthu achinyengo), ndi kwaukali kwambiri"
  85,13,"“Iye, (Mmodzi yekha) ndi amene adayambitsa zolengedwa ndiponso ndi Yemwe adzazibweze (pambuyo poonongeka)"
  85,14,"“Iye, ndi Wokhululuka (kwa amene walapa kwa Iye), ndiponso Wokonda kwambiri (amene akumkonda ndi kumumvera)"
  85,15,"“Mwini Arsh (Mpando wachifumu), (ndiponso) Wolemekezeka (mmene alili ndi mbiri Zake)"
  85,16,"“Wochita zimene wafuna, (ndipo chimene wafuna sichikanika)"
  85,17,“Kodi yakufika nkhani ya magulu a nkhondo
  85,18,"“Firiaun (Farawo) ndi Samudu, (ndi chilango chimene chidawapeza chifukwa chakulimbikira kwawo pa zinthu zopanda pake)"
  85,19,“Koma amene sadakhulupirire ali mkati motsutsa basi
  85,20,“Koma Allah awazinga mbali zonse
  85,21,“Koma iyi ndi Qur’an yolemekezeka
  85,22,"“Yomwe idachokera mu ubawo (chisileti chachikulu) wotetezedwa (ndi manja alionse, osintha kanthu kapena kuonjezerapo)"
  86,1,“Ndikulumbilira ku mwamba ndi Nyenyezi imene imadza usiku
  86,2,“Chitakudziwitse nchiyani za Nyenyezi yodza usikuyo
  86,3,“Imeneyo ndi nyenyezi yowala kwambiri (mu mdima)
  86,4,“Ndithudi palibe mzimu uliwonse koma uli ndi msungi wake (amene akuuyang’anira ndikulemba zonse zochita zake)
  86,5,"“Aganizire munthu, kodi adalengedwa kuchokera kuchiyani"
  86,6,“Adalengedwa kuchokera ku madzi ofwamphuka
  86,7,“Amatuluka kuchokera pakati pa mafupa a msana (wa mwamuna) ndi chifuwa (cha mkazi)
  86,8,"“Ndithu Iye ndiwakutha, kumbwezeranso (ku moyo pa mbuyo pa imfa)"
  86,9,“Tsiku limene zobisika zonse zidzaonekera poyera
  86,10,“Munthu sadzakhala ndi mphamvu (tsiku limenelo zodzitetezera iye mwini) ndiponso sadzakhala ndi mtetezi
  86,11,“Ndikulumbiliranso mitambo yobweretsabweretsa mvula
  86,12,“Ndi nthaka imene imang’ambika (potulutsa m’mera)
  86,13,“Ndithudi iyi (Qur’an) ndi mawu olekanitsa (Haqq ndi Bâtwil - choona ndi chonama)
  86,14,“Imeneyi sinkhambakamwa
  86,15,“Ndithudi iwo akukonza chiwembu
  86,16,“Nanenso ndikuwakonzera chiwembu (champhamvu kwambiri chimene sangathe kuchipewa)
  86,17,"“Basi, apatse nthawi osakhulupirira apatse nthawi pang’ono, (aona posachedwa)"
  87,1,“Lemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wapamwambamwamba (ndikuliyeretsa ku zinthu zosayenera)
  87,2,“Amene adalenga (chilichonse) ndikuchikonza bwinobwino (mkalengedwe kolingana)
  87,3,“Amene adalamuliratu (chilichonse zochita zake) ndi kuchiongolera
  87,4,“Ndi Yemwenso akumeretsa msipu
  87,5,“Ndipo nausandutsa kukhala wouma ndi wodera
  87,6,“Tikulakatulira (chivumbulutso Chathu) ndipo siuyiwala
  87,7,“Kupatula chimene wafuna Allah (kuti uchiiwale); ndithu Iye amadziwa zoonekera ndi zimene zimabisika
  87,8,“Ndipo tikufewetsera (njira yochitira zinthu) zabwino
  87,9,“Choncho akumbutse (wanthu powalalikira) ngati kukumbutsa kuthandiza
  87,10,“(Palibe chikaiko ulalikiwo) aukumbukira (ndikuthandizidwa nawo) amene akuopa Allah
  87,11,"“Ndipo wamavuto ambiri, (wamakani ndi wokanira), adzitalikitsa ndi ulalikiwo"
  87,12,“Amene adzalowa ku moto waukulu (umene wakonzedwa kuti udzakhale malipiro ake)
  87,13,"“Ndipo sakafa m’menemo (ndikupumula kumazunzo), ndiponso sakakhala ndi moyo (wamtendere)"
  87,14,“Ndithu wapambana amene wadziyeretsa (ku machimo)
  87,15,"“Ndikukumbukira dzina la Mbuye wake (ndi mtima wake, ndi lirime lake) uku akumapemphera"
  87,16,“Koma inu mukukonda kwambiri moyo wa dziko lapansi
  87,17,“Pamene moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro ndiwabwino kwambiri ndiponso wamuyaya
  87,18,"“Ndithu izi (mukuuzidwa m’Qur’an) zilipo m’mabuku oyamba, akale"
  87,19,“Mabuku a Ibrahim ndi Mûsa
  88,1,"“Kodi yakudzera, (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w) nkhani ya Qiyâma (imene idzaphimba anthu ndi zoopsa zake)"
  88,2,"“Nkhope zina tsiku limenelo, zidzakhala zonyozeka"
  88,3,“Zogwira ntchito yotopetsa kwambiri
  88,4,“Zikalowa ku Moto wotentha kwambiri
  88,5,“Zikamwetsedwa mu kasupe wotentha kwabasi
  88,6,“Sadzakhala ndichakudya koma minga
  88,7,“Yosanenepetsa (thupi) ndiponso yosathetsa njala
  88,8,“Nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zosangalala
  88,9,“Zidzakondwera ndi malipiro a zochita zake (za pa dziko lapansi)
  88,10,“M’minda ya pamwamba (Jannah)
  88,11,"“Sizikamva m’menemo mawu oipa, (otukwana ndi kulaula)"
  88,12,“Mmenemo muli kasupe woyenda (mokongola)
  88,13,“Mmenemo muli makama a pamwamba
  88,14,“Ndi zikho zoikidwa bwino (pamaso pawo)
  88,15,“Ndi misamiro yoikidwa bwino m’mizeremizere
  88,16,"“Ndi mphasa (zamtengo wapatali, carpet) zoyalidwa ponseponse"
  88,17,"“Kodi (akunyozera kulingalira zisonyezo za Allah), sakulingalira kungamira idalengedwa motani"
  88,18,“Ndi thambo (limene akuliona nthawi zonse) m’mene lidatukulidwira (kutali popanda mzati)
  88,19,“Ndi mapiri momwe adakhazikitsidwira (molimba)
  88,20,“Ndi nthaka momwe idayalidwira
  88,21,"“Basi, kumbutsa (anthu) ndithu iwe, ndiwe mkumbutsi"
  88,22,“Sindiwe wokakamiza anthu (kuti akhulupirire)
  88,23,“Koma amene anyoza ndi kukanira (ulaliki wako)
  88,24,“Allah amulanga chilango chachikulu zedi
  88,25,“Ndithu kobwerera kwawo ndi kwa Ife basi
  88,26,“Ndipo ndithu kuwerengedwa kwawo kuli kwa Ife
  89,1,“Ndikulumbilira kuyera kwa m’bandakucha; (pamene usiku uthawa)
  89,2,“Ndi masiku khumi (a mwezi wa Dhul-Hijjah omwe ngopatulika kwa Allah)
  89,3,"“Ndi Shaf’i ndi Witri: (nambala yogawika ndi yosagawika)"
  89,4,“Ndi usiku pamene ukupita (chifukwa cha kuyenda kwa dziko kodabwitsa)
  89,5,"“Kodi m’zimene zatchulidwazi simuli kulumbira kokwanira, kwa munthu wa nzeru"
  89,6,“Kodi sudadziwe momwe Mbuye wako adawalangira Âdi (anthu a mneneri Hûd)
  89,7,“Aku Irama; ataliatali ngati zipilala
  89,8,“Omwe onga iwo sadalengedwe m’maiko ena
  89,9,"“Ndi Asamudu, (anthu a mneneri Swaleh) amene adali kudula matanthwe ku chigwa (chotchedwa Wadi Qura ndi kumamanga nyumba zikuluzikulu)"
  89,10,“Komanso Firiauna (Farawo) mwini magulu ankhondo (omwe amalimbikitsa ufumu wake monga momwe zichiri zimalimbikitsira tenti)
  89,11,“Amene adaipitsa m’maiko mopyola malire
  89,12,“Ndipo adachulukitsa m’menemo kuononga (pamwamba pa kuononga)
  89,13,“Choncho Mbuye wako adawathira ndi mitundu ya zilango (zoopsa)
  89,14,“Ndithu Mbuye wako ali tcheru (ndi zochita za anthu. Ndipo akuwasungira kuti adzawalipire)
  89,15,"“Pamene munthu Mbuye wake akumuyesa (mayeso) ndikumulemekeza ndi kumpatsa mtendere (wachuma, ulemelero ndi mphamvu) amanena monyada: Mbuye wanga wandilemekeza (chifukwa zimenezi nzondiyenera ine)"
  89,16,"“Koma akamuyesa mayeso ndi kumchepetsera rizq lake, (chuma) amanena (motaya rntima): Mbuye wanga wandinyoza"
  89,17,"“Sichoncho ayi, (monga momwe mukuganizira) koma inu simuchitira za ufulu ana amasiye"
  89,18,“Ndipo simulimbikitsana za kudyetsa osauka
  89,19,“Ndipo mukudya chuma cha masiye; kudya kosusuka
  89,20,“Ndiponso mukukonda chuma; kukonda kopyola muyeso
  89,21,“Sichoncho! (Siyani machitidwe amenewa); nthaka ikadzapondedwa (ndikuifafaniza)
  89,22,“Ndikubwera Mbuye wako (mmabweredwe omwe akuwadziwa Iye Mwini) ndi angelo ali mmizeremizere
  89,23,"“Ndi kubweretsedwa Jahannam pa tsikulo, basi tsiku limenelo munthu adzakumbukira, koma kukumbuka kumeneko kudzamthandiza chiyani"
  89,24,"“Adzanena: Kalanga ine! Ndikadatsogoza zabwino pa za moyo wanga uno"
  89,25,"“Motero patsikuli, palibe wina amene adzalange monga momwe (Allah) adzalangire"
  89,26,“Ndiponso sanganjate aliyense monga kunjata kwa iye (Allah)
  89,27,“E iwe mzimu wokhazikika (ndi choona)
  89,28,"“Bwerera kwa Mbuye wako uli wokondwera (ndi zomwe wapatsidwa), ndipo uli woyanjidwa (ndi Allah pa zomwe udatsogoza)"
  89,29,“Lowa mgulu la akapolo anga abwino
  89,30,“Ndipo lowa m’munda Wanga (mnyumba ya mtendere wa muyaya)
  90,1,“Ndikulumbilira mzinda uwu (wa Makka)
  90,2,“Ndipo iwe udzatsikira mu mzindawu mwa ufulu (ndi kuuonjezera ulemelero)
  90,3,"“Ndiponso ndikulumbilira chobereka ndi choberekedwa, (kudzera mwa iwo mtundu wa anthu udasungidwa)"
  90,4,“Ndithudi tamulenga munthu mmavuto (kuyambira chiyambi chake mpaka malekezero a moyo wake)
  90,5,“Kodi (munthu wolengedwa ndi mavutoyu) akuganiza kuti palibe amene angamuthe
  90,6,"“Akunena (monyadira kuti): “Ndaononga chuma chambiri (chifukwa choletsa Chisilamu kufala).”"
  90,7,“Kodi akuganiza kuti palibe akumuona
  90,8,“Kodi sitidampangire maso awiri (amene akuyang’anira)
  90,9,“Ndilirime ndi milomo iwiri (zimene akulankhulira)
  90,10,"“Ndipo tamlongosolera njira ziwiri: (yabwino ndi yoipa, ndipo tampatsa mphamvu yosankhira njira imene akufuna)"
  90,11,“Kodi walikwera phiri lovutalo (lomwe lingakamfikitse ku Jannah)
  90,12,“Nanga nchiyani chakudziwitsa za kukwera phiri lovutalo
  90,13,“(Kutero ndiko) kupereka ufulu kwa kapolo
  90,14,“Kapena kuwadyetsa (osowa) pa tsiku la njala
  90,15,“Amasiye achibale
  90,16,“Kapena wosauka wa fumbi lokhalokha (chifukwa cha kuvutika kwambiri)
  90,17,"“Komanso nakhala mmodzi mwa okhulupirira ndikumalangizana za kupirira, ndi kumalangizananso za chifundo"
  90,18,“Otero ndiwo (anthu abwino) a ku dzanja lamanja
  90,19,"“Koma amene sanakhulupirire Ayah Zathu, ndi anthu a kudzanja lamanzere (oipa)"
  90,20,“Moto wozungulira mbali zonse udzakhala pa iwo (ndikuwatsekera makomo)
  91,1,“Ndikulumbilira dzuwa ndi dangalira lake
  91,2,“Ndi mwezi pamene ukulitsatira (dzuwalo ndikulowa mmalo mwake powalitsa dziko dzuwalo litalowa)
  91,3,“Ndi usana pamene ukulisonyeza poyera (kuti lisaphimbidwe)
  91,4,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuliphimba
  91,5,“Ndi thambo ndi (Mwini mphamvu zonse Wamkulu) Yemwe adalimanga ndi kulitukula (mwaluso)
  91,6,"“Ndi nthaka ndi (Mwini mphamvu zonse Wamkulu), Yemwe adaiyala (mbali zonse ndi kuichita kukhala ngati choyala)"
  91,7,“Ndi mzimu ndi Yemwe adawulinganiza (powupatsa mphamvu)
  91,8,“Ndipo adaudziwitsa zoipa zake ndi zabwino zake; (ndi kuwupatsa ufulu ndi mphamvu zochitira zimene ukufuna)
  91,9,“Ndithu wapambana amene wauyeretsa
  91,10,“Ndipo ndithu wataika amene wauononga
  91,11,“Thamud (Samudu) adakanira (Mneneri wawo) chifukwa cha kulumpha malire kwawo
  91,12,“Pamene woipitsitsa wawo adadzipereka (kupha ngamira yozizwitsa)
  91,13,"“Pamenepo Mneneri wa Allah (Swaleh) adawauza: “Isiyeni ngamira ya Allah (idye mdziko la Allah). Musailetse kumwa madzi (pa tsiku lake).”"
  91,14,“Koma adamutsutsa ndikuipha; kwa chifukwa chimenecho Mbuye wawo (Allah) adawaononga chifukwa cha tchimo lawo; adangowafafaniza (onse mnthaka)
  91,15,“Iye saopa zotsatira za chilangochi (chifukwa amenewa ndi malipiro a chilungamo pa zomwe adachita)
  92,1,“Ndikulumbilira usiku pamene ukuphimba (chilichonse)
  92,2,“Ndi usana pamene kukuyera
  92,3,“Ndiponso Yemwe adalenga chachimuna ndi chachikazi
  92,4,“Ndithu zochita zanu nzosiyanasiyana
  92,5,“Tsono yemwe akupereka (pa njira ya Allah) ndikumamuopa (Mbuye wake ndikupewa zoletsedwa)
  92,6,“Ndikumavomereza zinthu zabwino; (komwe kuli kukhulupirira Allah mwanzeru)
  92,7,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku zabwino
  92,8,“Koma uyo achite umbombo ndikuganiza za kuti iye payekha ngokwana
  92,9,“Ndi kumatsutsa zinthu zabwino
  92,10,“Choncho timufewetsera njira yompititsa ku mavuto (a muyaya)
  92,11,“Ndipo chuma chake sichidzamthandiza (chilichonse) akadzagwera ku Moto
  92,12,“Ndithu Ife ndi amene timawalongosolera anthu njira yabwino ndi njira yoipa
  92,13,“Ndipo ndithu moyo womaliza ndi moyo woyamba uli m’manja mwathu
  92,14,"“Basi, ndikukuchenjezani za Moto woyaka mwa mphamvu"
  92,15,“Sakaulowa koma (kafiri) woipitsitsa kwambiri
  92,16,“Yemwe amatsutsa (choona) ndi kunyoza (zisonyezo za Allah)
  92,17,“Koma yemwe akuopa Allah kwambiri akatalikitsidwa ndi Moto
  92,18,“Amene akupereka chuma chake ndi cholinga chodziyeretsa
  92,19,"“Ndipo palibe aliyense kwa iye, amene adamchitira za chifundo zomwe zikulipidwa"
  92,20,“Koma (akuchita zimenezi) kufuna chikondi cha Mbuye wake Wapamwambamwamba
  92,21,“Ndipo posachedwa adzasangalala
  93,1,“Ndikulumbilira mmawa dzuwa litakwera (imene ili nthawi yantchito)
  93,2,“Ndi usiku pamene ukuvindikira
  93,3,“Sadakusiye Mbuye wako (iwe Mneneri) (s.a.w) ndiponso sadakude
  93,4,“Ndithu moyo watsiku lirimkudza ndi wabwino kwa iwe kuposa umoyo woyambawu
  93,5,“Ndithu posachedwapa akupatsa Mbuye wako (zabwino zamdziko lapansi ndi tsiku lachimaliziro) ndipo ukondwera
  93,6,“Kodi sadakupeze uli wa masiye ndipo adakupatsa pokhala pabwino
  93,7,“Ndipo adakupeza uli wosazindikira (Qur’an) nakuongola (pokuzindikiritsa Qur’aniyo ndi malamulo a chipembedzo)
  93,8,“Ndiponso adakupeza uli wosauka nakulemeretsa
  93,9,"“Basi, wamasiye usamchitire nkhanza"
  93,10,“Ndiponso wopempha usamukalipire
  93,11,“Tsono mtendere wa Mbuye wako uwutchule (pothokoza ndi kugwira ntchito zabwino)
  94,1,“Kodi sitidachiphanule chifuwa chako (pokupatsa chiongoko ndi chikhulupiliro ndi nzeru zambiri)
  94,2,“Ndipo takuchotsera mtolo wako (pa ntchito yolalikira pokuthandiza ndi kukufewetsera zinthu zako)
  94,3,“Mtolo umene udalemetsa msana wako
  94,4,“Ndipo takukweza kutchulidwa kwako
  94,5,“Ndipo ndithu pali chovuta palinso zabwino (Zambiri)
  94,6,“Ndithu pali chovuta palinso zabwino (zambiri)
  94,7,"“Basi, ukamaliza ntchito (yolalikira ndi Jihâd) limbikira kupemphera"
  94,8,“Ndipo khala wolakalaka (zabwino zomwe zili) kwa Mbuye wako
  95,1,“Ndikulumbilira mitengo ya Mkuyu ndi Zitona (pansi pa mitengo imeneyi Ibrahim ndi Nuh (Nowa) adapeza uneneri
  95,2,“Ndi phiri la Sinai (pamene Allah adamulankhulira Mûsa)
  95,3,"“Ndiponso mzinda uwu (wolemekezeka) wamtendere; (Makka, womwe adapatsiridwa uneneri Muhammad) (s.a.w)"
  95,4,"“Palibe chikaiko, tamulenga munthu mkalengedwe kabwino, kolingana (ndipo ali ndi mbiri zabwino)"
  95,5,“Pambuyo pake tamubwezera pansi kumposa wa pansi
  95,6,"“Kupatula amene akhulupirira ndikumachita zabwino, adzakhala nawo iwo malipiro osatha"
  95,7,“Tsono nchiyani chakuchititsa kuti ukanire kuuka ndi malipiro pambuyo (poona mphamvu zathu pa chilichonse)
  95,8,“Kodi Allah si Muweruzi wa nzeru kuposa aweruzi onse
  96,1,"“Werenga! (Iwe Mneneri (s.a.w), zomwe zikuvumbulutsidwa) mdzina la Mbuye wako Yemwe adalenga (zolengedwa zonse)"
  96,2,“Adalenga munthu kuchokera ku magazi owundana
  96,3,“Werenga! Ndipo Mbuye wako ndi Wopereka kwambiri
  96,4,“Yemwe waphunzitsa (munthu kulemba) ndi cholembera
  96,5,“Waphunzitsa munthu zinthu (zambiri) zomwe (iye) sadali kuzidziwa
  96,6,“Zoona ndithu koma munthu akupyola malire (podzikweza)
  96,7,“Chifukwa chodziona kuti walemera
  96,8,"“Palibe chikaiko, (iwe Mneneri (s.a.w) kobwerera (onse) nkwa Mbuye wako basi; (adzawaukitsa)"
  96,9,“Kodi wamuona yemwe akuletsa
  96,10,“Kapolo (wa Allah) akamapemphera
  96,11,“Tandiuza ngati ali pachiongoko
  96,12,“Kapena kuti akulamulira zoopa Allah
  96,13,“Tandiuza (za woletsayo) ngati akutsutsa (zimene wadza nazo Mneneri) ndikunyoza (chikhulupiliro ndi ntchito yabwino)
  96,14,“Kodi sakudziwa kuti Allah akuona (machitidwe ake. Ndipo adzamlipira)
  96,15,“Ayi ndithu ngati sasiya timukoka tsitsi lapatsumba (tiligwira mwamphamvu tsumba lake ndikukamponya ku Moto)
  96,16,“Tsumba labodza (ndiponso) lamachimo
  96,17,"“Basi aliitane gulu lakelo, (la amene amakhala nawo pabwalo kuti amthandize pano pa dziko kapena tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  96,18,“Nafe tiitana azabaniya (angelo a ku Moto)
  96,19,"“Ayi ndithu usamumvere (pa zimene akukuletsazo); koma gwetsa nkhope yako pansi, ndipo dziyandikitse kwa Mbuye wako"
  97,1,“Ndithu taivumbulutsa (Qur’an) mu usiku wa Qadr (usiku wolemekezeka)
  97,2,“Ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za usiku wolemekezekawu
  97,3,“Usiku olemekezekawu uli wabwino kuposa miyezi chikwi chimodzi ( yomwe mulibe Laila-tul-Qadr)
  97,4,“Amatsika angelo ndi Jiburil mmenemo mwa chilolezo cha Mbuye wawo kudzalongosola chinthu chilichonse
  97,5,“Mtendere usiku umenewo! (Palibe mavuto ndi zoipa) mpaka m’bandakucha
  98,1,“Amene adakanira (Allah ndi Mthenga Wake) mwa omwe adapatsidwa buku ndi opembedza mafano sadali olekana (ndi umbuli wawo ndi kusalabadira kwawo choona) mpaka pomwe chidawadzera chisonyezo choonekera poyera
  98,2,“(Yemwe ndi) Mtumiki wochokera kwa Allah akuwawerengera makalata oyeretsedwa (ku zonama)
  98,3,“Omwe mkati mwake muli malamulo oongoka (ofotokoza za choona)
  98,4,“Sadalekane omwe adapatsidwa mabuku mpaka pomwe chidawafikira chisonyezo (chosonyeza kuti Muhammad (s.a.w) ndi mthenga wa Allah yemwe adalonjezedwa mmabuku awo
  98,5,“Ndipo sadalamulidwe (china) koma kuti ampembedze Allah (Mmodzi yekha) ndikuyeretsa chipembedzo chake popendekera ku choona (ndi kusiya njira zonama) ndi kuti asunge Swala ndiponso apereke chopereka (cha pachuma chawo); chimenecho (ndicho) chipembedzo choongoka
  98,6,“Ndithu amene sadakhulupirire (Mneneri) (s.a.w) pakati pa anthu a mabuku ndi opembedza mafano adzalowetsedwa ku Jahannam ndikukhala m’menemo nthawi yaitali; iwowo ndiwo zolengedwa zoipa
  98,7,"“Ndithu amene akhulupirira (mwa Allah ndi Mthenga Wake) ndikumachita zabwino, iwo ndiwo zolengedwa zabwino"
  98,8,"“Malipiro awo kwa Mbuye wawo, ndi minda yamuyaya momwe ikuyenda pansi pake mitsinje; adzakhala m’menemo muyaya. Allah adzawayanja nawonso adzamuyanja (chifukwa cha zomwe adzawapatse); zimenezo ndi za yemwe awope Mbuye wake (Allah)"
  99,1,“Likadzagwedezedwa dziko lapansi kugwedezeka kwake kwamphamvu
  99,2,"“Ndipo nthaka idzatulutsa mitolo yake (zinthu zomwe zidali mkati mwake, monga akufa ndi miyala ya mtengo wapatali)"
  99,3,"“Ndipo munthu adzanena (mwa mantha, ndikudabwa nthawi imeneyo). Ha! Yatani nthaka, (kodi Qiyâma yafika)"
  99,4,"“Tsiku limenelo idzanena nkhani zake zonse, (zabwino kapena zoipa)"
  99,5,“Pakuti Mbuye wako adzailamula kutero (kuti igwedezeke ndikunena zimene zinkachitika pamwamba pake)
  99,6,“Tsiku limenelo anthu adzachoka (m’manda) ali m’magulu obalalika kuti akasonyezedwe ntchito zawo (ndikudziwa chiwerengero chawo chimene chili kwa Allah)
  99,7,"“Choncho, amene angachite chabwino cholemera ngati kanjere kakang’ono, adzaona malipiro ake"
  99,8,"“Ndipo amene angachite choipa cholemera ngati kanjere kakang’ono, adzaona malipiro ake. (Allah sachitira chinyengo aliyense)"
  100,1,“Ndikulumbilira akavalo othamanga ali ndi phuma
  100,2,“Ndi otulutsa moto ku zikhotwa (pomenyetsa miyendo m’miyala)
  100,3,“Ndi othira nkhondo adani mmawa (dzuwa lisadatuluke)
  100,4,“Ndi kuulutsa fumbi lambiri (kwa adani) nthawi imeneyo
  100,5,“Ndikulowelera mkatikati mwa adani
  100,6,"“Ndithu munthu ali wokanira Mbuye wake, (sathokoza Allah pa zimene amdalitsa nazo)"
  100,7,“Ndithudi iye pa zimenezi ndi mboni (yodzichitira yekha kupyolera mzochitachita zake)
  100,8,“Ndipo ndithu iye ndiwokonda chuma kwambiri (ndiponso ngwamsulizo)
  100,9,“Kodi sakudziwa zikadzatulutsidwa za m’manda
  100,10,“Ndikudzasonkhanitsidwa ndi kuonekera poyera zomwe zidali m’mitima
  100,11,“Ndithu tsiku limenelo Mbuye wawo adzawadziwa kwambiri (ndikuwalongosolera zonse zochita zawo)
  101,1,“Kugunda kwa phokoso (la Qiyâma)
  101,2,“Kodi kugunda kwa phokosolo ndi chiyani
  101,3,“Ndichiyani chingakudziwitse za kugunda kwa phokoso (la Qiyâma komwe kudzawakomole anthu)
  101,4,“Limenelo ndi tsiku limene anthu adzakhala ngati agulugufe obalalika
  101,5,“Ndipo mapiri adzakhala ngati ubweya womwazidwa (wongouluka uku ndi uku mumlengalenga)
  101,6,“Tsono amene muyeso wake (wa zinthu zabwino) udzalemere (ndikupepuka zoipa)
  101,7,“Ndiye kuti iye adzakhala mu umoyo wosangalatsa (patsiku la chiweruziro)
  101,8,“Ndipo yemwe muyeso wake (wa zinthu zabwino) udzapepuka (ndi kulemera zoipa)
  101,9,“Ndiye kuti mbuto yake ndi ku Hawiya
  101,10,“Kodi ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za Hawiya
  101,11,“Umenewo ndi Moto woyaka mwa ukali
  102,1,“Kwakutangwanitsani kusonkhanitsa (chuma chambiri ndi ana)
  102,2,“Mpakana mwapita kumanda (mwamwalira ndikukalowa m’manda)
  102,3,“Sichoncho! Mudziwa posachedwapa
  102,4,“Ndiponso sichoncho! Mudziwa posachedwapa
  102,5,"“Sichoncho! mukadakhala mukudziwa, kudziwa kwachitsimikizo (sibwenzi mukutangwanika ndi za mdziko)"
  102,6,“Ndithudi mudzauona Moto
  102,7,“Kenako mudzauona ndithu ndi diso lachitsimikizo
  102,8,“Tsono patsikulo ndithudi mudzafunsidwa za mtendere (omwe munapatsidwa)
  103,1,“Ndikuilumbilira nthawi
  103,2,“Ndithu munthu aliyense ndi wotaika (chifukwa chakugonjetsedwa ndi zilakolako zake)
  103,3,"“Kupatula amene akhulupirira (mwa Allah) ndi kumachita zabwino, ndikumalangizana kutsatira choona ndiponso ndi kumalangizana za kupirira (potsatira malamulo a Allah ndi zina za mdziko)"
  104,1,“Kuonongeka koopsa kudzampeza aliyense wojeda ndi wonyoza anthu polozera (ndi maso kapena kuyankhula ndi lirime)
  104,2,“Yemwe wasonkhanitsa chuma ndikumachiwerengera
  104,3,“Akuganiza kuti chuma chakecho chimkhazika (pa dziko) nthawi yaitali (ndikumteteza ku zimene sakuzifuna)
  104,4,"“Sichoncho! (Asiye maganizo amenewo) ndithudi, akaponyedwa ku Moto woononga (chifukwa cha kuipa kwa zochita zake)"
  104,5,“Ndi chiyani chingakudziwitse za Moto woonongawu
  104,6,"“Umenewu ndi Moto wa Allah woyaka (nthawi zonse, woononga chilichonse choponyedwa mmenemo)"
  104,7,“Umene umakwera mpaka ku mtima
  104,8,“Ndithu motowo ukawazinga (ndi kuwatsekera makomo)
  104,9,“Munsanamira za zitalizitali (kotero kuti sakatha kugwedezeka mmenemo kapena kupulumuka)
  105,1,“Kodi sudaone momwe Mbuye wako adawachitira eni njovu
  105,2,“Kodi sadachichite chiwembu chawo kukhala chosokera (chopanda phindu)
  105,3,“Ndipo adawatumizira magulumagulu a mbalame otsatizana. (ndipo adawazungulira mbali zonse)
  105,4,“Zimawagenda ndi miyala ya moto
  105,5,“Choncho adawachita ngati m’mera wodyedwa (ndi nyama ndi kulavulidwa)
  106,1,“Cholinga chakuwachita Maquraish kuti apitirize chizolowezi chawo
  106,2,"“Apitilize chizolowezi chawo choyenda nthawi ya dzinja (kunka ku Yemen) ndi nthawi yachirimwe (kunka ku Sham kukachita malonda, mosatekeseka ndi mopanda mantha)"
  106,3,"“Choncho, amupembedze Mbuye wa Nyumba iyi (Al-Kaaba amene adachititsa kuti athe kuyenda maulendo awiriwo)"
  106,4,"“Yemwe amawadyetsa (nthawi imene Arabu anzawo) ali m’njala, ndipo amawapatsa chitetezo (pomwe anzawo) ali ndi mantha"
  107,1,“Kodi wamuona yemwe akutsutsa za mphoto (ndi chiwerengero cha tsiku lachimaliziro)
  107,2,“Iye ndi yemwe akukankha wamasiye (mwankhanza)
  107,3,“Ndipo salimbikitsa (ena pamodzi ndi iye mwini) kudyetsa osauka
  107,4,“Choncho kuonongeka kuli pa ena mwa opemphera swala (amene ali ndi mbiri izi)
  107,5,“Omwe amachitira mphwayi mapemphero awo
  107,6,“Amenenso (akamachita mapemphero awo) amadzionetsera (kwa anthu mwachipha maso kuti apeze ulemelero ndi kutamandidwa mmitima mwa anthu)
  107,7,"“Ndipo amamana ziwiya (zawo posabwereka anzawo zinthu zofunika pa moyo wa aliyense monga nkhwangwa, mpeni, mtondo ndi zina zotere)"
  108,1,“Ndithu takupatsa zabwino zambiri (zina mwa izo ndi mtsinje wotchedwa Kauthar)
  108,2,"“(Pakuti ndakupatsa zimenezo), pitiriza kupembedza Mbuye wako (moyera mtima) ndipo ipha nsembe yako (chifukwa chakuthokoza Allah pa zimene wakupatsa, monga ulemelero ndikukusankhira zabwino zambiri)"
  108,3,“Ndithu mdani wako ndiye ali wopanda mwawi
  109,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki) (s.a.w): E inu anthu osakhulupirira"
  109,2,“Sindipembedza chimene inu mukuchipembedza (kusiya Allah)
  109,3,“Inunso simumpembedza amene ine ndikumpembedza (yemwe ndi Allah)
  109,4,“Ndiponso ine sindidzapembedza chimene inu mwakhala mukuchipembedza (chifukwa inu ndinu ophatikiza Allah ndi zinthu zina)
  109,5,“Ndipo inu simudzampembedza amene ine ndikumpembedza (yemwe ndi Allah)
  109,6,"“Inu muli ndi chipembedzo chanu (chimene mukuchikhulupirira), inenso ndili ndi chipembedzo changa (chimene Allah wandisankhira)"
  110,1,“Chikafika chipulumutso cha Allah ndi kugonjetsa (mzinda wa Makka kwa iwe ndi okutsatira)
  110,2,“Ndikuwaona anthu akulowa m’chipembedzo cha Allah ali magulumagulu
  110,3,"“Pamenepo lemekeza Mbuye wako ndi kumtamanda ndiponso mpemphe chikhululuko, ndipo ndithu Iye ndiwolandira mochuluka kulapa (kwa anthu Ake)"
  111,1,“Aonongeka manja a Abi Lahab (omwe adali kuwagwiritsa ntchito pozunza Asilamu). Nayenso wawonongeka
  111,2,“Chuma chake ndi ulemelero wake (umene adaupeza) sizidamthandize ku chilango cha Allah
  111,3,“Adzalowa ku Moto wa malawi
  111,4,“Nayenso mkazi wake (adzalowa ku Moto) yemwe adali kusenza nkhuni (za minga pomutchera Mtumiki (s.a.w) komanso amanka nadanitsa pakati pa anthu
  111,5,“Mkhosi mwake mdzamangidwa chingwe chopiringidwa bwino cha mlaza (chomlanga nacho)
  112,1,"“Nena (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w), kwa amene akukufunsa mwachipongwe, mbiri za Mulungu wako): “Iye ndi Allah Mmodzi, (alibe mnzake)"
  112,2,“Allah ndi Wokhala ndi zonse Wodaliridwa ndi zolengedwa Zake
  112,3,“Sadabale (mwana) ndiponso sadaberekedwe
  112,4,“Ndiponso palibe aliyense wofanana ndi Iye.”
  113,1,"“Nena: “Ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye wam’bandakucha"
  113,2,“Kuchokera ku zoipa zimene Iye adazilenga
  113,3,“Ndi ku zoipa za usiku pamene mdima ukulowa mwa mphamvu
  113,4,“Ndi ku zoipa za afiti omwe amauzira mu mfundo
  113,5,“Ndiponso ku zoipa za wansanje pamene akuchita nsanje.”
  114,1,"“Nena: “Ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi Mbuye (Mleri) wa anthu (Yemwe akulinganiza zinthu zawo)"
  114,2,“Mfumu ya anthu ( Imene iri ndi mphamvu yochita chirichonse pa iwo)
  114,3,“Wopembedzedwa wa anthu
  114,4,“Kuzoipa za mnong’onezi (yemwe amathira unong’onezi wake m’mitimaya anthu) yemwenso amabisala (posiya unong’onezi wake ngati mwini mtimawo atankumbukira Allah)
  114,5,“Yemwe amanong’oneza mzifuwa za anthu
  114,6,“Wochokera m’ziwanda ndi mwa anthu.”